%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20Canada%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20Japan%20sought%20an%20update%20from%20India%20on%20the%20export%20bans%20on%20wheat%20and%20broken%20rice%2C%20and%20how%20long%20it%20intends%20to%20continue.%20The%20member%20countries%20called%20for%20transparency%20on%20export%20restrictions%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20current%20food%20security%20crisis%20afflicting%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20that%20we%20understand%20the%20intended%20duration%20of%20the%20measures%20which%20have%20already%20been%20in%20place%20for%2016%20months%20in%20the%20case%20of%20wheat%2C%20and%20a%20year%20in%20the%20case%20of%20broken%20rice%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20member%20states%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20asked%20India%20to%20ensure%20that%20its%20export%20restrictions%20are%20in%20line%20with%20General%20Agreement%20on%20Tariff%20and%20Trade%20(GATT)%20rules%20and%20they%20are%20only%20temporary%20in%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695796202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19161235%2F31764443254_73b92a3ef0_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fwto-member-states-ask-india-how-long-it-intends-to-ban-rice-wheat-exports%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20banned%20the%20export%20of%20broken%20rice%2C%20non-basmati%20rice%2C%20and%20wheat%20to%20control%20domestic%20prices.%20It%20will%20have%20to%20appear%20before%20World%20Trade%20Organization's%20Committee%20of%20Agriculture%20to%20provide%20its%20explanation%20on%20its%20agricultural%20policies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fwto-member-states-ask-india-how-long-it-intends-to-ban-rice-wheat-exports%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Thrashed%2C%20Made%20To%20Eat%20From%20Dustbin'%3A%20House%20Help%20Accuses%20Army%20Ma