h%20of%202014%2C%20on%20hype%20created%20about%20the%20killing%20of%2040%20CRPF%20personnel%20travelling%20from%20Jammu%20to%20Srinagar%20by%20road%20and%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20presumed%20retaliatory%20aerial%20bombing%20of%20Balakot%20in%20northwest%20Pakistan.%20He%20successfully%20projected%20himself%20as%20a%20muscular%20leader%20ready%20to%20teach%20Pakistan%20a%20lesson.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20three-day%20G20%20jamboree%20on%20September%208-10%2C%20where%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20raised%20the%20killing%20of%20Surrey%2C%20British%20Columbia%20Gurdwara%20president%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20also%20identified%20by%20the%20NIA%20as%20the%20chief%20of%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20(KTF)%2C%20by%20two%20unknown%20gunmen%20alleged%20to%20be%20Indian%20agents%2C%20the%20temperature%20of%20the%20Khalistan%20issue%2C%20long%20dead%20and%20buried%2C%20has%20been%20raised%20by%20the%20Indian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20secured%20lip%20support%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98Five%20Eyes%E2%80%99%20intelligence%20grouping%2C%20comprising%20Canada%20itself%20along%20with%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20over%20what%20he%20told%20the%20Canadian%20Parliament%20of%20Indian%20interference%20in%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20internal%20affairs%2C%20threatening%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%20by%20killing%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%20on%20home%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Modi%20went%20much%20further%20within%20hours%20of%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20speech%20in%20his%20Parliament.%20India%20has%20downgraded%20all%20diplomatic%20and%20related%20activities%20in%20Canada%2C%20sending%20shock%20waves%20among%20Punjabis%2C%20specially%20Sikhs%20with%20close%20relatives%20in%20Canada.%20Canada%20has%20the%20second%20largest%20Sikh%20population%20after%20India%20and%20Sikhs%20play%20crucial%20roles%20in%20Canadian%20politics%20and%20government.%20Seven%20Sikh%20MPs%20are%20ministers%2C%20apart%20from%20high-ranking%20government%20officials.%20Most%20Sikhs%20are%20now%20Canadian%20citizens%20and%20with%20close%20relatives%20tending%20their%20farmlands%2C%20they%20need%20to%20travel%20frequently%20to%20Punjab%20and%20back.%20To%20facilitate%20this%2C%20there%20are%20now%20a%20couple%20of%20direct%20flights%20between%20Amritsar%20and%20Toronto.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20when%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20(SAD)%20president%20Sukhbir%20Singh%20Badal%20took%20this%20up%20with%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20there%20was%20near-panic%20among%20Punjabis%2C%20mainly%20Sikhs%20but%20others%20as%20well.%20The%20BJP%20does%20not%20have%20much%20political%20influence%20in%20Punjab.%20If%20and%20when%20it%20has%20won%20parliamentary%20constituencies%2C%20it%20has%20piggybacked%20either%20on%20the%20Akali%20Dal%20or%20Bollywood%20stars%20like%20Vinod%20Khanna.%20The%20last%20time%2C%20when%20they%20had%20no%20worthwhile%20candidate%20for%20their%20Gurdaspur%20seat%2C%20they%20persuaded%20Hema%20Malini%20to%20get%20film%20star%20Sunny%20Deol%2C%20who%20has%20hardly%20any%20political%20interest%2C%20to%20contest.%20And%20the%20BJP%20won%20that%20seat.%20But%20it%20is%20not%20capable%20of%20winning%20any%20seat%20in%20Punjab%20without%20a%20good%20section%20of%20Sikhs%20also%20supporting%20its%20candidate.%20Hyping%20the%20Khalistan%20issue%20will%20most%20certainly%20alienate%20the%20Sikh%20voter%2C%20at%20least%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20going%20by%20how%20Modi%20encashed%20Pulwama-Balakot%20in%20the%20elections%20to%20the%20present%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Khalistan%20looks%20like%20a%20potent%20issue%20which%20the%20ruling%20party%20may%20fully%20encash%2C%20putting%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20on%20the%20back%20foot.%20The%20Congress%20already%20supports%20the%20government%20on%20this%20issue%20and%20once%20Modi%20goes%20to%20town%20about%20the%20threat%20from%20Khalistan%2C%20the%20Opposition%20may%20not%20have%20a%20leg%20to%20stand%20on%20with%20respect%20to%20national%20security.%20It%20happened%20with%20Kargil%20in%201998-99%2C%20then%20in%202019%20with%20Pulwama.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20added%20advantage%20this%20time%20is%20that%20Canada%20is%20too%20far%20away.%20Whereas%20there%20was%20some%20fear%20of%20escalation%20of%20war%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20over%20the%20Pulwama-Balakot%20matter%2C%20Canada%20is%20another%20matter.%20Besides%2C%20the%20four%20other%20members%20of%20the%20Five%20Eyes%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20have%20significant%20trade%20and%20defence%20ties%20with%20India%2C%20would%20not%20allow%20Canada%20to%20go%20beyond%20verbal%20attacks%2C%20which%20Trudeau%20may%20continue%20to%20consolidate%20his%20political%20constituency%2C%20since%20next%20year%20his%20Liberal%20Party%20too%20is%20going%20for%20national%20elections%20and%20Sikh%20votes%20are%20important%20for%20any%20winning%20combination%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20the%20tension%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20is%20the%20killing%20of%20another%20Sikh%2C%20Sukhdool%20Singh%20Gill%20alias%20Sukha%2C%20described%20by%20the%20NIA%20as%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist.%20He%20was%20gunned%20down%20on%20September%2020%20in%20Winnipeg%2C%20Canada%2C%20very%20much%20like%20Nijjar%2C%20by%20%E2%80%9Cunidentified%E2%80%9D%20killers.%20Sukha%20belonged%20to%20a%20prosperous%20farming%20family%20of%20Punjab%20and%20had%20fled%20to%20Canada%20in%202017.%20There%20are%20striking%20similarities%20between%20these%20two%20notable%20killings%20in%20Canada%2C%20which%20otherwise%20has%20a%20very%20low%20crime%20rate.%20Both%20Nijjar%20and%20Sukha%20were%20on%20the%20NIA%20list%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorists.%20Both%20were%20politically%20active%2C%20raising%20issues%20concerning%20Sikhs.%20Both%20were%20gunned%20down%20by%20%E2%80%9Cunidentified%E2%80%9D%20gunmen.%20Will%20it%20fan%20the%20fires%20further%2C%20or%20will%20the%20Canadian%20government%20now%20reduce%20the%20temperature%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFaraz%20Ahmad%20i