0process%20of%20restructuring%20and%20assessing%20demand%20across%20various%20units.%20Around%201%2C000%20people%20were%20already%20serving%20notice%20periods%2C%20and%20another%201%2C000%20have%20not%20completed%20their%20performance%20improvement%20parameters.%20Assessment%20is%20still%20underway.%20About%203%2C000-3%2C500%20may%20be%20impacted%20due%20the%20whole%20exercise%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%2C%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20identified%2C%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20said%20this%20will%20be%20the%20last%20lay%20off%20at%20BYJU's%20payroll%20and%20the%20entire%20exercise%20will%20be%20over%20by%20October%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20final%20phase%20of%20restructuring%20intends%20to%20optimise%20business%20by%20bringing%20together%20multiple%20divisions%20and%20creating%20a%20clear%20accountability-driven%20structure.%20The%203%2C000-3%2C500%C2%A0%20is%20an%20estimate%20and%20not%20the%20target%20of%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%2C%20BYJU's%20spokesperson%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20the%20final%20stages%20of%20a%20business%20restructuring%20exercise%20to%20simplify%20operating%20structures%2C%20reduce%20the%20cost%20base%20and%20better%20cash%20flow%20management.%20BYJU'S%20new%20India%20CEO%20Arjun%20Mohan%20will%20be%20completing%20this%20process%20in%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%20and%20will%20steer%20a%20revamped%20and%20sustainable%20operation%20ahead.%26quot%3B%20The%20sources%20said%20that%20several%20business%20units%20were%20created%20to%20meet%20the%20growth%20requirement%20during%20the%20pandemic%20and%20there%20were%20few%20product%20experiments%20that%20were%20carried%20out%20but%20they%20did%20not%20work%20out%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20now%20simple%20organisation%20structure%20divided%20between%20K12%20education%20and%20other%20competitive%20examinations.%20It%20will%20focus%20on%20consumer%20behaviour%20servi