0accused.%20The%20stringent%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act%20has%20also%20been%20invoked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUjjain%20police%20chief%20Sachin%20Sharma%20said%20a%20special%20team%20has%20been%20formed%20to%20identify%20and%20catch%20the%20culprits%20at%20the%20earliest.%20%26quot%3BThe%20medical%20examination%20has%20confirmed%20rape.%20We%20have%20formed%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20and%20closely%20following%20this.%20We%20appeal%20to%20the%20people%20to%20inform%20police%20if%20they%20get%20any%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20question%20on%20the%20location%20where%20the%20crime%20took%20place%2C%20the%20officer%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20being%20investigated.%20We%20would%20come%20up%20with%20the%20information%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20girl%20was%20not%20able%20to%20tell%20us%20exactly%20where%20she%20is%20from.%20But%20her%20accent%20suggests%20she%20is%20from%20Prayagraj%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20horrifying%20incident%20has%20yet%20again%20brought%20under%20the%20spotlight%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20dismal%20record%20on%20violence%20against%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Maharashtra%20have%20reported%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20cases%20of%20disappearance%20of%20women%20and%20girls%20between%202019%20and%202021.%20Also%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20reported%20most%20incidents%20of%20rapes%20in%20the%20country%20in%202021-%206%2C462%20-%20as%20per%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20data.%20Out%20of%20them%2C%20more%20than%2050%20per%20cent%20were%20crimes%20against%20minors.%20The%20number%20translates%20to%2018%20rapes%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695793380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fj6os0gn8_ujjain-shocker_625x300_27_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2