n%20politicians%20had%20called%20on%20Rota%20to%20step%20down%2C%20and%20Foreign%20Minister%20Melanie%20Joly%20added%20her%20voice%20to%20the%20chorus%20earlier%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20happened%20on%20Friday%20is%20completely%20unacceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20reporters%20at%20parliament.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20an%20embarrassment%20to%20the%20House%20and%20to%20Canadians%2C%20and%20I%20think%20the%20speaker%20should%20listen%20to%20members%20of%20the%20House%20and%20step%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20mistake%20played%20into%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20hands%2C%20given%20its%20claims%20that%20its%20rationale%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Frussias-war-in-ukraine%2Ft-60931789%5C%22%3Efor%20invading%20Ukraine%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20an%20attempt%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdenazify%E2%80%9D%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20furor%20also%20distracted%20from%20Ukrainian%20President%20Zelenskyy%E2%80%99s%20first%20in-person%20trip%20to%20Canada%20since%20the%20war%20began%2C%20scheduled%20to%20coincide%20with%20him%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fun-summit-zelenskyy-lavrov-play-revolving-doors%2Flive-66876336%5C%22%3Eheading%20to%20New%20York%20for%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fukraine-zelenskyy-arrives-in-washington-for-war-talks%2Fa-66886183%5C%22%3Ethen%20on%20to%20the%20White%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOpposition%20Conservatives%20in%20Canada%20slammed%20the%20government%20for%20failing%20to%20properly%20vet%20Hunka%2C%20but%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20government%20responded%20that%20it%20had%20received%20no%20advanced%20warning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcanadas-speaker-quits-after-ukrainian-nazi-veterans-speech%2Fa-66932160%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%3C%2Fem%3E%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695793163000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27104031%2F2.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fcanadas-speaker-quits-after-ukrainian-nazi-veterans-speech%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20speaker%20of%20Canada's%20House%20of%20Commons%20lower%20chamber%2C%20Anthony%20Rota%2C%20came%20under%20fire%20after%20publicly%20praising%20a%20Ukrainian%20World%20War%20II%20veteran%2C%20who%20it%20transpired%20had%20fought%20for%20the%20Nazis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fcanadas-speaker-quits-after-ukrainian-nazi-veterans-speech%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Salman%20Khan%2C%20Katrina%20Kaif%20in%20%E2%80%98Tiger%203%E2%80%99%3A%20India%E2%80%99s%20Yash%20Raj%20Films%20Unveils%20First%20Footage%20From%20Spy%20Universe%20Film%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695792873000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FTiger-3.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235737040%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20Yash%20Raj%20Films%20has%20unveiled%20the%20first%20footage%20from%20%E2%80%9CTiger%203%2C%E2%80%9D%20starring%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20Katrina%20Kaif.%20Directed%20by%20Maneesh%20Sharma%20(%E2%80%9CBand%20Baaja%20Baaraat%E2%80%9D)%2C%20the%20film%20is%20the%20latest%20instalment%20in%20producer%20Aditya%20Chopra%E2%80%99s%20spy%20universe.%20The%20spy%20universe%20kicked%20off%20with%20the%20Tiger%20franchise%2C%20starring%20Salman%20Khan%20and%20Katrina%20Kaif%2C%20beginning%20with%20%E2%80%9CEk%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fasia%2Fsalman-khan-katrina-kaif-tiger-3-1235737040%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fasia%2Fsalman-khan-katrina-kaif-tiger-3-1235737040%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fasia%2Fsalman-khan-katrina-kaif-tiger-3-1235737040%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20The%20Trudeau%20Problem%20in%20Canada%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20tough%20few%20days%20for%20the%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Justin%20Trudeau.%20Nothing%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20is%20going%20right%20for%20him.%20His%20domestic%20popularity%20has%20been%20on%20a%20downward%20spiral%20for%20some%20time%20and%20is%20unlikely%20to%20rebound%20any%20time%20soon%2C%20if%20the%20present%20trends%20are%20anything%20to%20go%20by.%20His%20main%20rival%2C%20Conservative%20Leader%20Pierre%20Poilievre%2C%20is%20gaining%20ground%20with%20recent%20polls%20suggesting%20he%20has%20the%20backing%20of%2040%20per%20cent%20of%20Canadians%20who%20see%20him%20as%20the%20best%20choice%20to%20be%20prime%20minister%2C%20a%205%20percent%20increase%20from%202022%2C%20even%20as%20Trudeau's%20popularity%20remains%20unchanged%20at%2031%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20across-the-board%20dissatisfaction%20with%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20country%20as%20economic%20issues%20predominate%20the%20domestic%20political%20agenda%20and%20Trudeau%20is%20seen%20as%20being%20unable%20to%20get%20a%20grip%20on%20a%20nation%20adrift.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20usually%20in%20times%20like%20these%20that%20political%20leaders%20look%20to%20foreign%20policy%20to%20shore%20up%20their%20credibility.%20But%20despite%20Trudeau%20trying%20hard%2C%20his%20moves%20have%20fallen%20flat%20even%20in%20this%20realm.%20The%20latest%20in%20this%20series%20is%20the%20honouring%20by%20the%20Canadian%20House%20of%20Commons%20of%20a%20Ukrainian%20man%2C%20Yaroslav%20Hunka%2C%20who%20fought%20for%20a%20Nazi%20unit%20in%20the%20Second%20World%20War%2C%20during%20the%20hosting%20of%20an%20address%20by%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky.%20Hunka%20was%20welcomed%20by%20the%20Speaker%20of%20the%20House%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20Ukrainian%20hero%2C%20a%20Canadian%20hero%2C%20and%20we%20%5BCanadian%20Parliament%5D%20thank%20him%20for%20all%20his%20service.%26quot%3B%20This%20has%20caused%20a%20political%20and%20social%20storm%20in%20Canada%20with%20several%20members%20of%20parliament%20calling%20for%20a%20public%20apology%20by%20Trudeau.%20The%20Speaker%20has%20resigned%20but%20Trudeau%20has%20not%20apologized.%20Underlining%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20invite%20Hunka%20had%20been%20made%20by%20the%20Speaker's%20office%20alone%2C%20Trudeau%20has%20merely%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20something%20that%20is%20deeply%20embarrassing%20to%20parliament%20of%20Canada%20and%20by%20extension%20to%20all%20Canadians.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20matter%20has%20not%20remained%20limited%20to%20Canada.%20Calling%20the%20incident%20%26quot%3Boutrageous%2C%26quot%3B%20Russia%20wasted%20no%20time%20in%20arguing%20that%20%26quot%3Bmany%20Western%20countries%2C%20including%20Canada%2C%20have%20raised%20a%20young%20generation%20that%20does%20not%20know%20who%20fought%20whom%20or%20what%20happened%20during%20the%20Second%20World%20War.%20And%20they%20know%20nothing%20about%20the%20threat%20of%20fascism.%26quot%3B%20Moscow%2C%20whose%20targeting%20of%20Ukraine%20was%20based%20on%20its%20claims%20to%20%26quot%3Bdenazify%26quot%3B%20the%20nation%2C%20would%20have%20found%20the%20irony%20too%20difficult%20to%20resist.%20Poland%20too%20has%20called%20for%20an%20apology%20from%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there%20is%20the%20India-Canada%20row%20that%20shows%20no%20signs%20of%20abating.%20Trudeau's%20mishandling%20of%20an%20important%20relationship%20not%20only%20for%20Ottawa%20but%20for%20the%20wider%20West%20has%20played%20right%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20China%20that%20must%20be%20watching%20with%20great%20interest%20the%20unfolding%20of%20this%20saga%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20responsible%20leadership%20and%20platitudinous%20rhetoric.%20India%20has%20pushed%20back%20hard%20against%20%26quot%3Bpolitically%20motivated%26quot%3B%20accusations%20from%20Canada.%20Speaking%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20targeted%20Canada%20when%20he%20emphasized%20that%20the%20international%20community%20should%20not%26quot%3Bcountenance%20that%20political%20convenience%20determines%20responses%20to%20terrorism%2C%20extremism%20and%20violence%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Brespect%20for%20territorial%20integrity%20and%20non-interference%20in%20internal%20affairs%20cannot%20be%20exercises%20in%20cherry-picking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20crisis%20has%20also%20given%20a%20unique%20opportunity%20to%20New%20Delhi%20to%20throw%20the%20spotlight%20on%20Canada's%20own%20troubled%20record%20on%20extremism%20and%20terrorism.%20Since%20the%201980s%2C%20this%20has%20been%20the%20case%20and%20India%20has%20been%20the%20primary%20victim%20of%20Canada's%20hypocrisy%20in%20brushing%20terrorism%20under%20the%20carpet%20in%20the%20name%20of%20human%20rights%20and%20freedom%20of%20expression.%20Where%20India%20has%20managed%20to%20get%20a%20handle%20on%20its%20own%20internal%20security%20situation%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Canada%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20its%20own%20festering%20extremism.%20It%20is%20now%20becoming%20an%20extra%20territorial%20threat%2C%20one%20that%20India%20has%20been%20repeatedly%20asking%20Ottawa%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrudeau's%20inability%20to%20comprehend%20the%20seriousness%20of%20this%20challenge%20has%20led%20to%20the%20present%20predicament.%20He%20has%20had%20no%20compunction%20in%20celebrating%20extra%20territorial%20killings%20by%20the%20US%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Indian%20entreaties%20they%20are%20not%20only%20to%20be%20ignored%20but%20even%20worse%20-%20challenges%20to%20Indian%20sovereignty%20are%20to%20be%20milked%20for%20domestic%20political%20considerations.The%20Indian%20response%20to%20Trudeau's%20accusations%20has%20shown%20that%20New%20Delhi%20is%20in%20no%20mood%20to%20countenance%20this%20posture%20and%20will%20go%20all%20out%20in%20signaling%20to%20Canada%20and%20other%20adversaries%20that%20it%20is%20serious%20about%20tackling%20the%20challenges%20it%20faces.%20There%20is%20a%20reason%20why%20Canada's%20closest%20allies%20have%20been%20circumspect%20about%20falling%20behind%20Ottawa%20in%20targeting%20India.%20It%20is%20also%20interesting%20to%20note%20the%20caution%20that%20Trudeau%20has%20shown%20when%20dealing%20with%20Chinese%20interference%20in%20Canadian%20elections%20and%20the%20alacrity%20with%20which%20he%20has%20targeted%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20bigger%20issues%20at%20stake%20here%20for%20India%20and%20the%20wider%20world.%20Trudeau%20has%20pushed%20India-Canada%20ties%20to%20the%20brink%20and%20it%20is%20highly%20unlikely%20that%20the%20trust%20deficit%20between%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Trudeau%20can%20be%20bridged%20any%20time%20soon.%20But%20the%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister's%20problems%20go%20beyond%20India%20as%20this%20past%20one%20week%20has%20shown%20as%20he%20navigates%2C%20rather%20unsuccessfully%2C%20one%20crisis%20after%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20He%20is%20Vice%20President%20-%20Studies%20and%20Foreign%20Policy%20at%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20Director%20(Honorary)%20of%20the%20Delhi%20School%20of%20Transnational%20Affairs%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695792840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F6g4