italization.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22JIGYASA%20KAKWANI%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Puts%20its%20Concerted%20Strength%20Against%20TV%20Channel%20That%20Ran%20Kirit%20Somaiya%20Sex%20Tape%20Story%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27104908%2Flokshahi-news.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20July%2017%2C%20Marathi%20news%20channel%20%3Cem%3ELokshahi%3C%2Fem%3E%20carried%20a%20primetime%20news%20item%20about%20Kirit%20Somaiya%20%E2%80%93%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20former%20MP%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20trusted%20%E2%80%9Cwhistle%20blower%E2%80%9D.%20The%20news%20was%20based%20on%20a%20purported%20sex%20video%20of%20the%20BJP%20leader.%20The%20anchor%2C%20and%20also%20the%20channel%E2%80%99s%20editor-in-chief%2C%20Kamlesh%20Sutar%20while%20presenting%20the%20content%20of%20the%20highly%20redacted%20video%20asked%3A%20%E2%80%9CIs%20Kirit%20Somaiya%20being%20honey%20trapped%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20Somaiya%E2%80%99s%20supposed%20sexual%20trapping%20soon%20snowballed%2C%20with%20leaders%20from%20the%20opposition%20accusing%20him%20of%20sexual%20misconduct%20and%20extortion%2C%20among%20other%20things.%20Somaiya%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20the%20story%20lying%20down%20and%20soon%20tried%20all%20avenues%20available%20and%20filed%20complaints%20with%20the%20Mumbai%20police%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20and%20the%20Telecom%20Regulatory%20Authority%20of%20India%20(TRAI).%20Last%20week%2C%20he%20also%20moved%20a%20writ%20petition%20before%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20issue%20of%20whether%20a%20politician%E2%80%99s%20sexual%20life%20qualifies%20to%20be%20a%20news%20story%20remains%20contentious%2C%20it%20is%20the%20state%20and%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20swift%20response%20to%20both%20cover%20up%20the%20matter%20and%20teach%20the%20news%20channel%20%E2%80%9Ca%20lesson%E2%80%9D%20that%20raises%20some%20serious%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20video%20was%20aired%2C%20Somaiya%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Can%20aggrieved%20party%E2%80%9D%2C%20along%20with%20six%20other%20BJP%20MLAs%20and%20MPs%20%E2%80%93%20Mihir%20Kotecha%2C%20Yogesh%20Sagar%2C%20Parag%20Shah%2C%20Ram%20Kadam%2C%20Ashok%20Nete%2C%20Anil%20Bonde%20and%20Ramdas%20Tadas%20%E2%80%93%20complained%20to%20the%20I%26amp%3BB%20ministry%20and%20TRAI.%20In%20their%20complaint%2C%20they%20claiming%20that%20the%20news%20editor%20had%20used%20%E2%80%9Cmanipulation%20techniques%E2%80%9D%20to%20tarnish%20Somiaya%E2%80%99s%20public%20image.%20The%20video%2C%20their%20complaints%20claimed%2C%20were%20%E2%80%9Cobjectionable%2C%20misleading%20and%20unauthentic%E2%80%9D.%20It%20no%20more%20remained%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20fight%20against%20the%20channel%3B%20it%20had%20become%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20personal%20fight%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20complaint%2C%20Somaiya%20accused%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20his%20party%2C%20along%20with%20%3Cem%3ELokshahi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmaligning%20his%20image%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20editor%20Kamlesh%20Sutar%20with%20the%20background%20of%20a%20small%20clip%20tried%20to%20create%20a%20false%20image%20and%20portray%20the%20leader%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Csexual%20%3Cem%3Erakhshasa%3C%2Fem%3E%20(monster)%E2%80%9D%2C%20who%20is%20using%20his%20ED%2C%20political%20connections%20to%20exploit%20dozens%20of%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20Somaiya%E2%80%99s%20complaint%20claimed.%20In%20the%20show%2C%20Sutar%20had%20mentioned%20that%20their%20sources%20claim%20that%20there%20are%20multiple%20videos%20running%20to%20several%20hours%20in%20circulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F673932413%2FKirit-Somaiya-s-complaint-to-I-B-ministry%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20Kirit%20Somaiya's%20complaint%20t