2https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F673932687%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-ktki7kpNXibg9242OQsJ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%220.6669133974833457%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22I%26amp%3BB%20ministry's%20order%20on%20Lokshahi%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20fight%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20end%20here%2C%20Sutar%20says.%20%E2%80%9CTRAI%20order%20is%20still%20pending.%20Also%2C%20the%20Delhi%20HC%20order%20was%20an%20interim%20one%20and%20yet%20to%20reach%20its%20finality.%E2%80%9D%20An%20FIR%20against%20Sutar%20stands%20too%2C%20although%20the%20Mumbai%20police%20have%20claimed%20that%20the%20leaked%20video%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Fsex-video-of-bjp-leader-kirit-somaiya-appears-genuine-says-mumbai-police-officer-101690400367712.html%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cgenuine%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20a%20morphed%20one%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Crime%20Branch%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20police%2C%20however%2C%20had%20raided%20the%20%3Cem%3ELokshahi%3C%2Fem%3E%20office%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20confiscated%20the%20pen%20drive%20in%20which%20the%20video%20was%20allegedly%20obtained.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20also%20asked%20to%20reveal%20our%20source%20for%20the%20story.%20But%20we%20plainly%20refused%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sutar%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESutar%2C%20like%20his%20organisation%2C%20continues%20to%20stand%20by%20the%20story.%20He%20says%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnever%20meant%20to%20target%20an%20individual%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20(Somaiya)%20is%20a%20public%20personality%2C%20a%20former%20MP.%20He%20has%20access%20to%20crucial%20documents%20and%20data%20at%20any%20given%20point%20in%20time.%20The%20story%20was%20about%20a%20video%20that%20was%20suspiciously%20shot%20from%20a%20room%20in%20which%20he%20was%20seen%20engaging%20in%20sexual%20activity.%20The%20question%20that%20needs%20to%20hence%20be%20asked%20is%20how%20did%20the%20camera%20end%20up%20in%20his%20private%20space%20and%20who%20is%20behind%20this%20nefarious%20act.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Inter%20Departmental%20Committee%20(IDC)%20of%20the%20I%26amp%3BB%20had%20observed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwhether%20the%20person%20in%20question%20is%20an%20ordinary%20citizen%20or%20a%20political%20figure%2C%20everyone%20has%20a%20private%20life%20that%20deserves%20respect%E2%80%9D.%20Sutar%20points%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdouble%20standard%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20ministry.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20made%20to%20appear%20as%20if%20this%20is%20the%20one-of-its-kind%20video%20that%20is%20ever%20to%20be%20broadcasted%20on%20a%20news%20channel.%E2%80%9D%20Sutar%20recalls%20that%20in%202017%2C%20Patidar%20Anamat%20Andolan%20Samiti%20chief%20Hardik%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20purported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fstate-elections-2017%2Fhardik-patel-sex-tape-gujarat-elections%5C%22%3Esex%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20suddenly%20emerged%20and%20the%20I%26amp%3BB%20ministry%20didn%E2%80%99t%20consider%20it%20to%20be%20a%20breach%20of%20privacy.%20%E2%80%9CSimilarly%2C%20news%20channels%20openly%20aired%20BJP%20leader%20Ramesh%20Jarkiholi%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20sex%20tape%20without%20any%20obstructive%20orders%20from%20the%20I%26amp%3BB%20or%20the%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sutar%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20just%20because%20news%20channels%20have%20been%20airing%20content%20of%20sexual%20acts%2C%20does%20that%20justify%20%3Cem%3ELokshahi%3C%2Fem%3E%20channel%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20put%20out%20Somaiya%E2%80%99s%20video%3F%20Sutar%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20looked%20at%20it%20him%20as%20a%20victim%20here%20and%20if%20you%20watch%20the%20show%2C%20you%20will%20see%20me%20ask%20several%20times%20if%20Somaiya%20was%20being%20trapped%20and%20was%20his%20room%20intentionally%20bugged.%E2%80%9D%20Strangely%2C%20however%2C%20the%20channel%20didn%E2%80%99t%20reach%20out%20to%20Somaiya%20(who%20they%20consider%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvictim%E2%80%9D)%20until%20the%20story%20was%20aired.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20such%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sutar%20claims%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20story%20gets%20easily%20sabotaged.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695792412000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27104908%2Flokshahi-news.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbjp-kirit-somaiya-lokshahi-marathi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20issue%20of%20whether%20a%20politician%E2%80%99s%20sexual%20life%20qualifies%20to%20be%20a%20news%20story%20remains%20contentious%2C%20it%20is%20the%20state%20and%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20swift%20response%20to%20both%20cover%20up%20the%20matter%20and%20teach%20the%20news%20channel%20%E2%80%9Ca%20lesson%E2%80%9D%20that%20raises%20some%20serious%20questions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbjp-kirit-somaiya-lokshahi-marathi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Girl%2C%204%2C%20Comes%20In%20Contact%20With%20Live%20Wire%2C%20Rescued%20By%20Elderly%20Man%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%204-year-old%20girl%20was%20rescued%20by%20an%20elderly%20man%20from%20being%20electrocuted%20after%20she%20came%20in%20contact%20with%20a%20faulty%20wire%20and%20fell%20facedown%20on%20a%20waterlogged%20road%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Varanasi%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20child%20struggled%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20water%2C%20also%20electrified%20because%20of%20the%20live%20wire.%20In%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20chaos%2C%20an%20e-rickshaw%20stopped%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20the%20passengers%20disembarked%20and%20rushed%20to%20the%20child's%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20bystanders%20also%20came%20forward%20to%20help%20her%20only%20to%20be%20repelled%20by%20electric%20shocks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20girl%20continued