C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103978815%2Cimgsize-43222.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fmedical-drama-mumbai-diaries-returns-for-a-second-season-to-start-streaming-from-october-6-see-teaser-inside%2Farticleshow%2F103978880.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103978880.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPremiering%20on%20October%206%2C%20the%20second%20season%20will%20unfold%20with%20the%20doctors%2C%20trainees%2C%20and%20staff%20of%20Bombay%20General%20Hospital%20dealing%20with%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20terror%20attacks%20and%20their%20personal%20struggles%20that%20follow%2C%20juxtaposing%20it%20against%20the%20devastation%20brought%20by%20the%20Mumbai%20floods%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fmedical-drama-mumbai-diaries-returns-for-a-second-season-to-start-streaming-from-october-6-see-teaser-inside%2Farticleshow%2F103978880.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Scientists%20Discover%208th%20Continent%20That%20Had%20Been%20Missing%20For%20375%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20almost%20375%20years%2C%20geoscientists%20have%20discovered%20a%20continent%20that%20had%20been%20hiding%20in%20plain%20sight.%20The%20small%20team%20of%20geologists%20and%20seismologists%20has%20created%20a%20newly%20refined%20map%20of%20Zealandia%20or%20Te%20Riu-a-Maui%2C%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fphys.org%2Fnews%2F2023-09-newly-refined-zealandia-drawn-dredged.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPhys.org%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20researchers%20found%20it%20by%20using%20the%20data%20obtained%20from%20dredged%20rock%20samples%20recovered%20from%20the%20ocean%20floor.%20The%20details%20of%20the%20research%20have%20been%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20Tectonics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Ffuture%2Farticle%2F20210205-the-last-secrets-of-the-worlds-lost-continent%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereport%2C%20Zealandia%20is%20a%20vast%20continent%20of%201.89%20million%20sq%20miles%20(4.9%20million%20sq%20km)%20it%20is%20around%20six%20times%20the%20size%20of%20Madagascar.%20The%20team%20of%20scientists%20informed%20that%20there%20are%20in%20fact%208%20continents-%20and%20the%20latest%20addition%20breaks%20all%20records%2C%20as%20the%20smallest%2C%20thinnest%2C%20and%20youngest%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20continent%20is%2094%20per%20cent%20underwater%2C%20with%20just%20a%20handful%20of%20islands%2C%20similar%20to%20New%20Zealand.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20example%20of%20how%20something%20very%20obvious%20can%20take%20a%20while%20to%20uncover%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Andy%20Tulloch%2C%20a%20geologist%20at%20the%20New%20Zealand%20Crown%20Research%20Institute%20GNS%20Science%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20team%20that%20discovered%20Zealandia%2C%20BBC%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EScientists%20say%20that%20Zealandia%20has%20always%20been%20difficult%20to%20study.%20Scientists%20are%20now%20studying%20collections%20of%20rocks%20and%20sediment%20samples%20brought%20up%20from%20the%20ocean%20bed%2C%20most%20of%20which%20came%20from%20drilling%20sites-others%20came%20from%20the%20shores%20of%20islands%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPhys.org%20reported%20that%20the%20study%20of%20the%20rock%20samples%20showed%20geologic%20patterns%20in%20West%20Antarctica%20that%20hinted%20at%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20subduction%20zone%20near%20the%20Campbell%20Plateau%20off%20the%20west%20coast%20of%20New%20Zealand.%20The%20researchers%20did%20not%20find%20magnetic%20anomalies%20in%20that%20area%2C%20however%2C%20which%20argues%20against%20theories%20surrounding%20a%20