ighlighted%20the%20%26quot%3Borganised%20crime%2C%20related%20to%20secessionist%20forces%2C%20violence%20and%20extremism%26quot%3B%20in%20Canada%2C%20raising%20concerns%20over%20them%20being%20%26quot%3Bvery%20permissive%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20political%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20'Discussion%20at%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20Relations'%20in%20New%20York%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20Canada%20actually%20has%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20organised%20crime%2C%20relating%20to%20the%20secessionist%20forces%2C%20organized%20crime%2C%20violence%20and%20extremism.%20They're%20all%20very%2C%20very%20deeply%20mixed%20up.%20So%20in%20fact%2C%20we%20have%20been%20talking%20about%20specifics%20and%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20stressed%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20provided%20the%20Canadian%20side%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20information%20about%20the%20crime%2C%20and%20there%20has%20been%20a%20large%20number%20of%20extradition%20requests.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20given%20them%20a%20lot%20of%20information%20about%20organized%20crime%20and%20leadership%2C%20which%20operates%20out%20of%20Canada.%20There%20are%20a%20large%20number%20of%20extradition%20requests.%20There%20are%20terrorist%20leaders%2C%20who%20have%20been%20identified%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20EAM%20raised%20concern%20over%20these%20incidents%20of%20threats%20to%20Indian%20diplomats%20and%20attacks%20on%20Indian%20consulates%2C%20stating%20that%20these%20are%20%26quot%3Bvery%20permissive%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20political%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20concern%20is%20that%20it's%20really%20been%20very%20permissive%2C%20because%20of%20political%20reasons.%20So%20we%20have%20a%20situation%20where%20our%20diplomats%20are%20threatened%2C%20our%20consulates%20have%20been%20attacked...A%20lot%20of%20this%20is%20often%20justified%2C%20as%20saying%20that's%20how%20democracies%20work.%20If%20somebody%20gives%20me%20something%20specific%2C%20it%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20restricted%20to%20Canada.%20But%20if%20there's%20any%20incident%20which%20is%20an%20issue%20and%20somebody%20gives%20me%20something%20specific%2C%20as%20a%20government%2C%20I%20would%20look%20at%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERegarding%20PM%20Trudeau's%20allegations%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20assured%20that%20the%20Indian%20side%20will%20take%20action%20if%20the%20Canadian%20side%20provides%20specific%20information%20in%20connection%20with%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Nijjar's%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20told%20the%20Canadians%20that%20this%20is%20not%20the%20government%20of%20India's%20policy.%20Secondly%2C%20we%20said%20if%20you%20have%20something%20specific%20and%20if%20you%20have%20something%20relevant%2C%20let%20us%20know.%20We%20are%20open%20to%20looking%20at%20it...The%20picture%20is%20not%20complete%20without%20the%20context%20in%20a%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Canada%20has%20yet%20to%20provide%20any%20public%20evidence%20to%20support%20the%20claim%20about%20the%20slaying%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarly%20last%20week%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20made%20an%20explosive%20statement%20accusing%20the%20Indian%20government%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20%E2%80%93%20a%20claim%20that%20India%20has%20outrightly%20rejected%2C%20calling%20it%20'absurd'%20and%20'motivated'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20suspended%20its%20visa%20services%20in%20Canada%2C%20following%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20of%20Indian%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmid%20strained%20ties%2C%20India%20issued%20an%20advisory%20for%20its%20citizens%20and%20those%20who%20are%20travelling%20to%20Canada%20to%20exercise%20%26quo