ica%20(WGA)%20called%20off%20its%20nearly%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhollywood-writers-strike%2Fa-66912722%5C%22%3Efive-month%20strike%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20Tuesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20said%20its%20members%20could%20return%20to%20work%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20it%20moves%20to%20ratify%20a%20new%20three-year%20contract%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhollywood%2Ft-37195247%5C%22%3EHollywood%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0studios.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20WGA%20%E2%80%9Cvoted%20unanimously%20to%20lift%20the%20restraining%20order%20and%20end%20the%20strike%20as%20of%2012%3A01%20am%20PT%2F3%3A01%20am%20ET%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20September%2027th%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20writers%20will%20still%20have%20to%20ratify%C2%A0the%20deal%2C%20but%20will%20now%20be%20permitted%20to%20work%20in%20the%20meantime.%20The%20WGA%20said%20its%20members%20have%20until%20October%209%20to%20vote%20on%20the%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20in%20the%20deal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWGA%20leaders%20have%20called%20the%20deal%20%E2%80%9Cexceptional.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20with%20entertainment%20companies%20contained%20many%20of%20the%20WGA%E2%80%99s%20demands%2C%20including%20more%20compensation%20on%20streaming%20content%2C%20increased%20health%20and%20pension%20contributions%2C%20and%20AI%20safeguards.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThose%20safeguards%20mean%20AI%20cannot%20be%20used%20to%20undermine%20a%20writer%E2%80%99s%20credit.%20While%20writers%20can%20choose%20to%20use%20AI%20when%20drafting%20scripts%2C%20a%20company%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20force%20them%20to%20use%20the%20software.%20The%20studios%20also%20must%20disclose%20to%20a%20writer%20if%20any%20materials%20were%20generated%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalk%20shows%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20first%20to%20return%20to%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENightly%20network%20shows%20such%20as%20NBC%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Tonight%20Show%20Starring%20Jimmy%20Fallon%E2%80%9D%20or%20ABC%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CJimmy%20Kimmel%20Live!%E2%80%9D%20are%20expected%20to%C2%A0return%20to%20the%20air%20within%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WGA%20represents%20more%20than%2011%2C000%20screenwriters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EActors%20remain%20on%20strike%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20screenwriters%20can%20return%20to%20work%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Screen%20Actors%20Guild-American%20Federation%20of%20Radio%20and%20Television%20Artists%20(SAG-AFTRA)%20remain%20on%20strike%2C%20with%20no%20talks%20yet%20on%20the%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20a%20hot%20second%2C%20I%20really%20thought%20that%20this%20was%20going%20to%20go%20on%20until%20next%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Marissa%20Cuevas%2C%20an%20actor%20who%20has%20appeared%20on%20the%20TV%20series%20%E2%80%9CKung%20Fu%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Big%20Bang%20Theory.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKnowing%20that%20at%20least%20one%20of%20us%20has%20gotten%20a%20good%20deal%20gives%20a%20lot%20of%20hope%20that%20we%20will%20also%20get%20a%20good%20deal%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20the%20Associated%20Press%20from%20the%20picket%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWriters%20were%20encouraged%20to%20stand%20with%20actors%20on%20the%20picket%20line%20in%20a%20show%20of%20solidarity%2C%20like%20%E2%80%9CMad%20Men%E2%80%9D%20creator%20Matthew%20Weiner%20did%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20never%20have%20had%20the%20leverage%20we%20had%20if%20SAG%20had%20not%20gone%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Weiner%20told%20the%20Associated%20Press.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20very%20brave%20to%20do%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhollywood-screenwriters-union-agrees-to-end-strike%2Fa-66932516%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%3C%2Fem%3E%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695789490000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14124705%2FWriters_Guild_of_America_2023_writers_strike.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fhollywood-screenwriters-union-agrees-to-end-strike%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Writers%20Guild%20of%20America%20has%20reached%20a%20tentative%20deal%20with%20studios%2C%20which%20had%20met%20most%20demands.%20The%20nearly%20five%20month%20strike%20has%20slowed%20down%20film%20and%20television%20production.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fhollywood-screenwriters-union-agrees-to-end-strike%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Charlie%20Chopra%20%26amp%3B%20The%20Mystery%20Of%20Solang%20Valley%20Is%20Watchable%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20whodunit%20that%20may%20appear%20outmoded%20but%20continues%20to%20be%20enduringly%20appealing%20-%20the%20book%20from%20which%20this%20web%20series%20is%20adapted%2C%20Agatha%20Christie's%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Sittaford%20Mystery%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20was%20first%20published%20in%201931%20-%20receives%20a%20lively%2C%20absorbing%20and%20nifty%20makeover%20in%20%3Ci%3ECharlie%20Chopra%20%26amp%3B%20the%20Mystery%20of%20Solang%20Valley%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDirected%20by%20Vishal%20Bhardwaj%20from%20a%20script%20he%20wrote%20with%20Anjum%20Rajabali%20and%20Jyotsna%20Hariharan%2C%20the%20six-episode%20SonyLIV%20series%20centres%20on%20a%20murder%20foretold%20and%20a%20wrongful%20arrest%2C%20which%20forces%20an%20amateur%20sleuth%20to%20swing%20into%20action%20in%20a%20terrain%20where%20danger%20lurks%20at%20every%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ECharlie%20Chopra%20%26amp%3B%20the%20Mystery%20of%20Solang%20Valley%3C%2Fi%3E%20takes%20liberties%2C%20often%20frothily%20so%2C%20with%20the%20source%20novel%20and%20rustles%20up%20situations%20and%20thinks%20up%20character%20quirks%20that%20serve%20not%20only%20to%20significantly%20indigenize%20the%20story%20but%20also%20to%20update%20it%20for%20contemporary%20sensibilities.%20The%20result%20isn't%20instantly%20scintillating%20but%20as%20Charlie%20Chopra's%20investigation%20unfolds%2C%20the%20show%20grows%20on%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBhardwaj%20assembles%20a%20cast%20of%20seasoned%20screen%20performers%20and%20younger%20actors%20who%20do%20their%20bit%20to%20liven%20up%20the%20proceedings%20even%20though%20a%20few%20of%20them%20are%20left%20to%20languish%20on%20the%20fringes%20of%20the%20plot.%20Not%20so%20Wamiqa%20Gabbi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lead%20actress%20is%20delightfully%20full%20of%20beans%2C%20bringing%20the%20young%20detective%20alive%20by%20combining%20the%20curiosity%20of%20a%20wide-eyed%20rookie%20with%20the%20firm%20resolve%20of%20a%20steely%20woman%20in%20search%20of%20the%20truth%20in%20an%20environment%20of%20distrust%20and%20subterfuge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20hill%20station%20stands%20in%20for%20snowy%20Dartmoor%20in%20Charlie%20Chopra%20%26amp%3B%20the%20Mystery%20of%20Solang%20Valley.%20The%20subdued%20colour%20palette%20that%20the%20location%20yields%20(through%20the%20camera%20of%20cinematographer%20Tassaduq%20Hussain)%20lends%20the%20series%20both%20depth%20of%20view%20and%20sustained%20visual%20gloss.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20surface%20sparkles.%20What%20lies%20underneath%20holds%20the%20aces.%20More%20than%20the%20texture%20of%20the%20images%20and%20the%20interplay%20of%20sun%20and%20snow%2C%20light%20and%20shadow%2C%20and%20silences%20and%20sounds%2C%20what%20the%20series%20gets%20absolutely%20right%20is%20the%20tone%20of%20the%20delivery.%20Secrets%20hover%20over%20the%20environs%20and%20the%20homes%20that%20the%20suspects%20inhabit%2C%20but%20the%20air%20of%20dread%20is%20tempered%20with%20doses%20of%20gentle%20humour%2C%20which%20spring%20from%20the%20acute%20angularities%20of%20the%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgatha%20Christie's%20amateur%20sleuth%20Emily%20Trefusis%20turns%20into%20Charulata%20%26quot%3BCharlie%26quot%3B%20Chopra%20(Wamiqa%20Gabbi)%2C%20a%20cocky%20Patiala%20girl%20who%20begins%20investigating%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20retired%20brigadier%20when%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%20Jimmy%20Nautiyal%20(Vivaan%20Shah)%2C%20the%20victim's%20nephew%20and%20a%20start-up%20entrepreneur%20in%20need%20of%20a%20big%20sum%20of%20money%2C%20is%20charged%20with%20homicide%20and%20taken%20into%20police%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20course%20of%20a%20seance%20during%20a%20weekend%20get-together%20in%20the%20Solang%20Valley%20home%20of%20an%20ill-tempered%20psychic%20(Naseeruddin%20Shah)%2C%20the%20spirit%20of%20a%20woman%20long%20dead%2C%20speaking%20through%20a%20girl%20possessed%2C%20claims%20that%20Brigadier%20Meherbaan%20Singh%20Rawat%20(Gulshan%20Grover)%20is%20dead%20in%20his%20Manali%20bungalow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20superannuated%20army%20man%20is%20indeed%20found%20in%20a%20pool%20of%20blood%20by%20his%20best%20friend%2C%20Colonel%20Anand%20Barua%20(Baharul%20Islam)%2C%20who%20risks%20his%20life%20and%20makes%20his%20way%20to%20the%20cottage%20(in%20blizzard-like%20conditions%20and%20poor%20visibility).%20He%20breaks%20into%20the%20house%20with%20the%20brigadier's%20trusted%20long-time%20factotum%20Hanif%20Sheikh%20(Ashique%20Hussain)%20and%20a%20jaded%20police%20inspector%2C%20Narayan%20Joshi%20(Ghanshyam%20Garg).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEverybody%20at%20the%20s%C3%A9ance%20-%20incidentally%2C%20Kenneth%20Branagh's%20best%20Agatha%20Christie%20reworking%20yet%2C%20A%20Haunting%20in%20Venice%2C%20which%20is%20still%20in%20the%20multiplexes%2C%20begins%20with%20a%20similar%20ritual%20congregation%20although%20The%20Hallowe'en%20Party%20and%20the%20Sittaford%20Mystery%20were%20written%20forty%20years%20apart%20-%20is%20a%20suspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEverybody%20stands%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20death%20of%20the%20wealthy%20brigadier%2C%20who%2C%20as%20Charlie's%20investigation%20progresses%2C%20emerges%20as%20a%20man%20with%20more%20than%20his%20share%20of%20skeletons%20in%20the%20cupboard.%20Similarly%2C%20everybody%20around%20the%20deceased%2C%20his%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20has%20something%20to%20hide%20and%20Charlie%20is%20determined%20to%20do%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20find%20the%20real%20culprit%20and%20prove%20Jimmy's%20innocence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Old%20Manali%20Police%20station%20is%20in%20a%20hurry%20to%20bury%20Jimmy%2C%20but%20Charlie%2C%20with%20the%20aid%20of%20pesky%20television%20journalist%20Sitaram%20Bisht%20(Priyanshu%20Painyuli)%2C%20which%20whom%20she%20starts%20off%20on%20the%20wrong%20foot%2C%20probes%20the%20circumstances%20of%20Brigadier%20Rawat's%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20ferrets%20for%20information%2C%20Charlie%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20deal%20with%20-%20a%20ski%20resort%20that%20might%20have%20hit%20a%20dead-end%2C%20a%20clandestine%20marijuana%20business%2C%20an%20insurance%20fraud%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20fugitives%20hiding%20in%20plain%20sight%2C%20a%20schizophrenic%20under%20psychiatric%20treatment%2C%20a%20war%20refugee%20and%20much%20else.%20As%20lies%20and%20half-truths%20stumble%20out%20of%20the%20closet%2C%20the%20girl%20dives%20in%20headlong%2C%20unmindful%20of%20the%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJimmy%20has%20a%20two%20elder%20siblings%2C%20sister%20Saloni%20(Paoli%20Dam)%20and%20brother%20Billu%20(Imaad%20Shah)%2C%20none%20of%20whom%20is%20above%20suspicion.%20Saloni's%20husband%20Manas%20Dabral%20(Chandan%20Roy%20Sanyal)%2C%20a%20writer%20with%20a%20series%20of%20duds%20behind%20him%2C%20and%20a%20host%20of%20other%20relatives%2C%20the%20brigadier's%20younger%20brother%20Mohan%20(Lalit%20Parimoo)%2C%20his%20psychoanalyst-wife%20Janki%20(Neena%20Gupta)%20and%20their%20ailing%20son%20Varun%20(Pulkit%20Makol)%2C%20who%20requires%20an%20expensive%20kidney%20transplant%2C%20are%20also%20on%20Charlie's%20radar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENeither%20is%20that%20all.%20Charlie%20has%20several%20others%20on%20her%20list%20of%20suspects%20-%20a%20semi-classical%20vocalist%20(Lara%20Dutta)%20and%20her%20daughter%20Wasima%20(Bhagyashree%20Tarke)%2C%20the%20mysterious%20Miss%20Bharucha%20(Ratna%20Pathak%20Shah)%2C%20the%20Negis%20(Amitabh%20Bhattacharjee%20and%20Damini%20Basu)%2C%20who%20live%20on%20rent%20in%20a%20cottage%20owned%20by%20the%20brigadier%2C%20and%2C%20to%20be%20sure%2C%20the%20dead%20man's%20Man%20Friday%2C%20Hanif%20Sheikh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FKh9ieUeCSAQ%3Fsi%3DMmp9UuoGnEkETL2Z%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBhardwaj%20retains%20the%20classic%20Agatha%20Christie%20construct%20while%20employing%20stylistic%20flourishes%20that%20put%20his%20stamp%20on%20the%20narrative.%20The%20show%20opens%20with%20a%20muder%2C%20which%20is%20followed%20by%20a%20couple%20of%20more%20deaths%2C%20and%20the%20storyline%20is%20strewn%20with%20red%20herrings%2C%20exactly%20the%20way%20they%20are%20in%20the%20latest%20film%20adaptation%20of%20a%20Hercule%20Poirot%20case%2C%20A%20Haunting%20in%20Venice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20arc%20is%20markedly%20different.%20With%20a%20robust%20title%20track%20composed%20by%20Vishal%20Bhardwaj%20and%20sung%20by%20Sunidhi%20Chauhan%20setting%20the%20tone%20-%20it%20introduces%20Charlie%20Chopra%2C%20her%20address%20and%20her%20penchant%20for%20perplexing%20cases%20-%20the%20protagonist%20takes%20the%20high-spirited%20timbre%20of%20the%20show%20forward%2C%20repeatedly%20turning%20to%20the%20camera%20and%20sharing%20asides%20with%20the%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20distancing%20effect%20has%20an%20underpinning%20of%20delicious%20whimsy%20that%20in%20the%20process%20of%20underscoring%20the%20artifice%20at%20play%20in%20the%20adaptation%20also%20creates%20for%20the%20audience%20a%20sense%20of%20familiarity%20with%2C%20and%20empathy%20for%2C%20the%20winsome%20Charlie%20Chopra%2C%20a%20girl%20who%20is%20herself%20always%20only%20a%20murderous%20attack%20away%20from%20grave%20physical%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20is%20a%20show%20that%20is%20dominated%20by%20Wamiqa%20Gabbi%2C%20a%20few%20of%20the%20other%20actors%20are%20in%20their%20elements%2C%20none%20more%20so%20than%20Priyanshu%20Painyuli.%20If%20there%20are%20a%20few%20weak%20links%20in%20the%20cast%20of%20Charlie%20Chopra%20%26amp%3B%20the%20Mystery%20of%20Solang%20Valley%2C%20it%20is%20primarily%20because%20the%20overcrowded%20show%20is%20inevitably%20unable%20to%20accord%20equal%20importance%20to%20all%20the%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20supporting%20actors%2C%20Neena%20Gupta%20and%20Ratna%20Pathak%20Shah%20have%20their%20moments%2C%20but%20one%20is%20left%20wishing%20that%20Lara%20Dutta%20and%20Paoli%20Dam%20had%20more%20to%20do.%20But%2C%20in%20the%20ultimate%20analysis%2C%20what%20the%20show%20lacks%20is%20far%20outweighed%20by%20what%20it%20contains.%20Watchable%20all%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695789420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fd8frk9b8_-charlie-chopra_625x300_27_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fcharlie-chopra-the-mystery-of-solang-valley-review-agatha-christie-adaptation-is-watchable-all-the-way-3-stars-4427382%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Charlie%20Chopra%20%26amp%3B%20The%20Mystery%20Of%20Solang%20Valley%20Review%3A%20In%20what%20is%20a%20show%20that%20is%20dominated%20by%20Wamiqa%20Gabbi%2C%20a%20few%20of%20the%20other%20actors%20are%20in%20their%20elements%2C%20none%20more%20so%20than%20Priyanshu%20Painyuli.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fcharlie-chopra-the-mystery-of-solang-valley-review-agatha-christie-adaptation-is-watchable-all-the-way-3-stars-4427382%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%2