-its-owners%2F%23gs.5nbztb%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3EStackedHomes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20others%20who%20recently%20sold%20their%204-room%20BTO%20flats%20in%20the%20same%20part%20of%20Singapore%20have%20made%20profits%20of%20over%2070%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBy%20paying%20for%20their%20new%20house%20in%20cash%2C%20they%20no%20longer%20need%20to%20service%20a%20mortgage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Singapore%2C%20apartments%20developed%20by%20the%20Housing%20Development%20Board%2C%20or%20HDB%2C%20must%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hdb.gov.sg%2Fresidential%2Fselling-a-flat%2Feligibility%5C%22%3Eoccupied%20for%20a%20minimum%20number%20of%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20they%20can%20be%20sold%20on%20the%20open%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20minimum%20occupation%20period%20ends%2C%20some%20of%20those%20living%20in%20BTOs%20will%20take%20the%20chance%20to%20flip%20their%20homes%2C%20make%20a%20profit%2C%20and%20buy%20a%20bigger%20place%2C%20Toh%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20who%20was%20working%20in%20finance%2C%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20the%20couple's%20apartment%20block.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650026b34717fd0019fc849c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20exterior%20of%20the%20couple's%20apartment%20block.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20having%20a%20bigger%20house%2C%20or%20a%20bigger%20car%20doesn't%20necessarily%20translate%20to%20a%20better%20quality%20of%20life%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Toh%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20us%2C%20we%20downsized%20to%20free%20up%20the%20obligations%20to%20pay%20every%20month.%20Then%20we%20can%20have%20the%20additional%20funds%20to%20go%20and%20do%20what%20we%20want.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20they%20are%20planning%20to%20take%20a%20long%2