sn't%20exactly%20in%20the%20most%20well-kept%20condition%2C%20Toh%20said.%20Some%20of%20the%20wall%20tiles%20were%20cracked%2C%20and%20the%20window%20grilles%20were%20falling%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20about%20the%20look%20and%20feel%20of%20the%20space%20was%20outdated%2C%20and%20walking%20into%20the%20home%20felt%20like%20stepping%20into%20the%20past%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20put%20the%20age%20of%20their%20home%20into%20perspective%2C%20the%20first%20HDB%20apartment%20blocks%20in%20Singapore%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.roots.gov.sg%2Fen%2Fplaces%2Fplaces-landing%2FPlaces%2Flandmarks%2Fmy-queenstown-heritage-trail%2Fthe-first-hdb-blocks-the-hdb-terraces%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBlocks%252045%252C%252048%2520%2526%252049%2520Stirling%2Cwork%2520on%2520in%2520the%25201950s.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompleted%20in%201960%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20only%2018%20years%20earlier%20than%20their%20apartment%20block.%20In%20other%20older%20housing%20estates%20like%20theirs%2C%20the%20government%20even%20ends%20up%20buying%20back%20the%20properties%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hdb.gov.sg%2Fresidential%2Fliving-in-an-hdb-flat%2Fsers-and-upgrading-programmes%2Fsers%5C%22%3Eto%20demolish%20them%20and%20redevelop%20the%20area.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20before%20photo%20of%20the%20couple's%20kitchen%20and%20living%20room%2C%20as%20viewed%20from%20the%20kitchen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6507f16ecd637c0019c6a623%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20before%20photo%20of%20the%20couple's%20kitchen%20and%20living%20room%2C%20as%20viewed%20from%20the%20kitchen.%3Cp%3ETobby%20Toh%20and%20Goh%20Kaiyi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAppearance%20aside%2C%20one%20thing%20the%20couple%20was%20sold%20on%20was%20the%20location%3A%20The%20apartment%20was%20loc