20get%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20students%20may%20start%20avoiding%20Canada%20for%20higher%20education%20after%20New%20Delhi%20issued%20a%20safety%20advisory%20on%20the%20country%20for%20%26quot%3Banti-India%26quot%3B%20activities.%20This%20could%20affect%20a%20sector%20that%20brings%20in%20about%20C%2422%20billion%20(%2416.3%20billion)%20annually%20in%20revenues%20for%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20nations%20have%20already%20expelled%20senior%20diplomats%20from%20the%20other%20side%20in%20a%20tit-for-tat%20escalation.%20Canada%20plans%20to%20reduce%20embassy%20staff%20as%20security%20threats%20rise%20in%20the%20South%20Asian%20country%20while%20New%20Delhi%20stopped%20issuing%20visas%20to%20Canadian%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20charts%20looking%20at%20what's%20at%20stake%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EImmigration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndians%20make%20up%20nearly%20a%20fifth%20of%20immigrants%20to%20Canada%2C%20the%20highest%20share%20from%20a%20single%20place%20of%20birth%20since%201971%2C%20according%20to%20government%20data.%20However%2C%20remittances%20from%20Canada%20were%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20the%20total%20flowing%20into%20India%20and%20this%20is%20in%20part%20due%20to%20immigrants%20permanently%20settling%20down%20in%20Canada%20and%20bringing%20over%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EImmigration%20accounts%20for%2090%25%20of%20Canada's%20labor%20force%20growth%20as%20there%20is%20fast-aging%20working%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20sizable%20number%20of%20Indian%20immigrants%20to%20Canada%20are%20Sikhs%20from%20Punjab%20state%20in%20India.%20Sikhs%20account%20for%201.7%25%20of%20India's%20population%20and%20Canada%20has%20the%20highest%20numbers%20of%20Sikhs%20outside%20of%20the%20South%20Asian%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigher%20Education%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndians%20account%20for%20the%20most%20number%20of%20international%20students%20doing%20their%20higher%20education%20in%20Canada.%20In%202022%2C%20they%20made%20up%20over%2028%25%20of%20the%20total%20foreign%20students%2C%20according%20to%20local%20media%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHigher%20education%20is%20a%20significant%20sector%20contributing%20to%20more%20than%2015%25%20of%20Canada's%20services%20exports%20annually.%20The%20latest%20available%20data%20by%20Global%20Affairs%20Canada%20shows%20that%20international%20students%20alone%20contributed%201.3%25%20to%20Canada's%20gross%20domestic%20product%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrade%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrade%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20stood%20at%20%248.16%20billion%20in%202022-23%2C%20dwarfing%20in%20comparison%20to%20%24128.7%20billion%20in%20India's%20bilateral%20trade%20with%20the%20US.%20However%2C%20India%20depends%20almost%20entirely%20on%20imports%20for%20its%20potash%20needs%2C%20and%20buys%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20the%20crop%20nutrient%20from%20Canada%2C%20the%20world's%20biggest%20exporter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESupplies%20from%20Canada%20have%20become%20increasingly%20important%20as%20sanctions%20have%20disrupted%20trade%20and%20expansion%20plans%20for%20Russia%20and%20Belarus.%20The%20current%20frostiness%20may%20impact%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia's%20major%20exports%20to%20Canada%20include%20pharmaceuticals%2C%20iron%20and%20steel%20products.%20The%20nations%20were%20negotiating%20an%20early-stage%20trade%20deal%20before%20the%20talks%20were%20put%20on%20pause%20by%20Canada%20ahead%20of%20the%20Group%20of%2020%20leaders%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Indian%20officials%20said%20it%20was%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20developments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20no%20bilateral%20meetings%20at%20G-20%20in%20a%20sign%20of%20developing%20tensions%20but%20both%20leaders%20had%20a%20sideline%20conversation.%20It%20later%20emerged%20that%20Trudeau%20brought%20up%20the%20allegations%20on%20the%20Sikh's%20murder%2C%20which%20Modi%20had%20responded%20with%20criticism%20on%20Canada%20becoming%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20separatist%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EForeign%20Investment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20attracted%20foreign%20direct%20investment%20equity%20inflows%20of%20%243.60%20billion%20from%20Canada%20between%20April%202000%20and%20June%202023%2C%20according%20to%20government%20data.%20It's%20just%20a%20share%20of%200.56%25%20of%20the%20total%20FDI%20flows%20into%20India%20and%20compares%20with%20%2461.26%20billion%20from%20the%20US%20during%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20official%20in%20India%20has%20said%20there's%20no%20immediate%20impact%20on%20investments%20but%20analysts%20now%20fear%20the%20row%20may%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bchilling%20effect%26quot%3B%20on%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20big-ticket%20deals%20include%20Sun%20Life%20Financial%20Inc.'s%20joint%20venture%20with%20India's%20Aditya%20Birla%20Group%20while%20CPP%20Investment%20Board%20has%20invested%20%2421%20billion%20in%20India%20as%20of%20about%20a%20year%20ago.%20One%20of%20CPPIB's%20key%20investments%20is%20a%202.7%25%20stake%20in%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20foreign%20portfolio%20investment%2C%20commitments%20from%20Canada%20rose%201.72%20trillion%20rupees%20in%20July%20this%20year%20from%201.57%20trillion%20rupees%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695787380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F122o7v0g_modi-trudeau-afp_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-clash-with-canada-threatens-to-hurt-trade-investment-4427311%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canada-India%20ties%20have%20deteriorated%20since%20Prime%20Min