0history%20in%20a%20single%20inning.%20They%20went%20past%20Afghanistan's%20record%20of%2022%20sixes%20that%20helped%20them%20make%20278%2F3%20back%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20two%20of%20the%20most%20interesting%20records%20are%20them%20smashing%20the%20fastest%20fifty%20and%20century%20in%20T20I%20cricket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDipendra%20Singh%20Airee%2C%20the%20Nepal%20all-rounder%20reached%20his%20half-century%20in%20just%20nine%20balls%2C%20going%20past%20Indian%20legend%20Yuvraj%20Singh's%20record%20of%20a%2012-ball%20fifty%20against%20England%20in%20the%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%202007%2C%20a%20match%20which%20saw%20him%20smash%20Stuart%20Broad%20for%20six%20sixes%20in%20an%20over.%20Airee%20ended%20with%2052*%20in%20just%2010%20balls%2C%20with%20eight%20of%20them%20smashed%20out%20of%20the%20park%20for%20a%20six.%20His%20strike%20rate%20of%20520%20is%20also%20the%20best%20in%20a%20T20I%20innings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKushal%20Malla%20also%20went%20past%20T20I%20giants%20like%20India's%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20South%20Africa's%20David%20Miller%20to%20hit%20the%20fastest%20T20I%20century%20ever%2C%20in%20just%2034%20balls.%20Malla%20ended%20with%20137%20in%2050%20balls%2C%20with%20eight%20fours%20and%2012%20sixes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Rohit%20and%20Miller%20have%2035-ball%20centuries%20to%20their%20names%2C%20but%20Malla%20has%20now%20shattered%20these%20records%20by%20smashing%20a%20helpless%20Mongolia%20bowling%20attack%20all%20over%20the%20park.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Mongolia%20needs%20315%20to%20win.%20India's%20men's%20cricket%20campaign%20will%20start%20on%20October%203%20in%20the%20quarterfinals.%20The%20title%20clash%20will%20be%20played%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695787380000%2C%22visual