llywood%20will%20remain%20a%20long%20way%20from%20normal%20service%2C%20with%20actors%20--%20represented%20by%20the%20SAG-AFTRA%20union%20--%20still%20refusing%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20resolution%20to%20that%20stoppage%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20a%20minimum%20of%20several%20more%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20hundreds%20of%20film%20and%20television%20shoots%20backed%20up%2C%20it%20could%20still%20then%20take%20months%20for%20Hollywood%20to%20clear%20the%20logistical%20logjam%20and%20get%20fully%20back%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EActors%20were%20on%20the%20picket%20lines%20Tuesday%20outside%20Netflix%2C%20being%20joined%20by%20members%20of%20the%20WGA%20who%20were%20there%20in%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20strike%20is%20over.%20But%20the%20battle%20goes%20on%20until%20the%20actors%20get%20their%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20WGA%20member%20Vinnie%20Wilhelm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20not%20have%20gotten%20the%20deal%20that%20we%20have%20gotten%20if%20it%20weren't%20for%20the%20support%20of%20the%20actors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695784500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fbe92hnco_writers-hollywood-strike_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafter-5-months-hollywood-writers-body-agrees-to-end-strike-4427229%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20leaders%20of%20the%20Writers%20Guild%20of%20America%20on%20Tuesday%20called%20off%20a%20monthslong%20strike%20that%20has%20paralyzed%20Hollywood%2C%20accepting%20a%20pay%20deal%20hammered%20out%20with%20production%20studios.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafter-5-months-hollywood-writers-body-agrees-to-end-strike-4