0with%20the%20problems%20of%20caste%20census%2C%20implementing%20sub-categorisation%20of%2027%25%20quota%20based%20on%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20Rohini%20Commission%2C%20Maratha%20reservation%20and%20the%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20aggressive%20stance%20on%20the%20exclusion%20of%20defined%20quotas%20for%20OBC%20women%20within%20the%2033%25%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies.%20Jats%2C%20a%20traditionally%20landed%2C%20agrarian%20community%2C%20are%20found%20in%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20They%20are%20electorally%20significant%20and%20politically%20organised%20in%20Haryana%2C%20western%20UP%2C%20NCT%20Delhi%20and%20Rajasthan.%20Protests%20for%20Jat%20reservation%20have%20turned%20violent%20in%20the%20past%2C%20especially%20in%20Haryana%2C%20which%20borders%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Explainer%3A%20Why%20the%20Maratha%20Quota%20Agitation%20Has%20Put%20Successive%20Maharashtra%20Governments%20in%20a%20Bind%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fexplainer-why-the-maratha-quota-agitation-has-put-successive-maharashtra-governments-in-a-bind%5C%22%3EExplainer%3A%20Why%20the%20Maratha%20Quota%20Agitation%20Has%20Put%20Successive%20Maharashtra%20Governments%20in%20a%20Bind%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENaresh%20Tikait%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Kisan%20Union%2C%20who%20was%20one%20of%20the%20speakers%20at%20Sunday%E2%80%99s%20event%20in%20Meerut%2C%20said%20reservation%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cright%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Jats.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20made%20immense%20contributions%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20development%20and%20independence%20movement.%20This%20%3Cem%3Ebaradari%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20also%20contributed%20a%20lot%20in%20sports%20as%20well%20as%20politics%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Tikait.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJat%20groups%20do%20not%20agree%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20in%202015%20to%20strike%20down%20a%20last-ditch%20notification%20by%20the%20Congress-led%20UPA%20government%20in%202014%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20to%20grant%20OBC%20status%20to%20the%20Jat%20community%20at%20the%20central%20level.%20The%20Jats%20already%20enjoy%20OBC%20reservation%20at%20the%20state-level%20in%20states%20such%20as%20Rajasthan%2C%20UP%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Bihar.%20Jats%20of%20Gujarat%20and%20Rajasthan%20(excluding%20Bharatpur%20and%20Dholpur%20districts)%20are%20in%20the%20Central%20List%20of%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%2C%20while%20striking%20down%20the%20Jat%20reservation%2C%20had%20said%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20perception%20of%20a%20self-proclaimed%20socially%20backward%20class%20of%20citizens%20or%20even%20the%20perception%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98advanced%20classes%E2%80%99%20as%20to%20the%20social%20status%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98less%20fortunates%E2%80%99%20cannot%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20constitutionally%20permissible%20yardstick%20for%20determination%20of%20backwardness%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChaudhary%20Yudhvir%20Singh%2C%20national%20general%20secretary%20of%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Jat%20Mahasabha%2C%20however%2C%20does%20not%20agree%20with%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20communities%20parallel%20to%20us%20and%20those%20even%20below%20us%20in%20the%20qualifying%20criteria%20were%20included%20in%20the%20OBC%20list%20as%20part%20of%20a%20political%20conspiracy.%20We%20deserve%20reservation.%20We%20qualify%20on%20the%20indicators%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27111246%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-27-at-11.10.05-AM-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27111246%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-27-at-11.10.05-AM-1.jpeg%201170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27111246%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-27-at-11.10.05-AM-1-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27111246%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-27-at-11.10.05-AM-1-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-677081%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22658%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Jat%20Mahasabha%20meeting%20in%20Meerut%20on%20September%2024.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20eight%20years%20after%20the%20apex%20court%20quashed%20the%20UPA%20government%E2%80%99s%20notification%2C%20Singh%20feels%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20government%20has%20done%20little%20to%20grant%20reservation%20to%20the%20community%20even%20though%20it%20has%20enjoyed%20back-to-back%20majorities%20and%20even%20cornered%20the%20Jat%20vote%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%202012%20Muzaffarnagar%20communal%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20does%20not%20look%20like%20the%20government%20intends%20to%20give%20us%20reservation.%20They%20are%20pursuing%20the%20politics%20of%20non-Jat%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20used%20Jats%20in%202013%20(Muzaffarnagar%20violence)%20and%20captured%20power%20in%20the%20country.%20In%20Haryana%2C%20they%20installed%20a%20non-Jat%20chief%20minister%20(Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar)%20to%20pit%20Jats%20vs%20non-Jats.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Meerut%20gathering%2C%20attending%20by%20several%20heads%20of%20Jat%20%3Cem%3Ekhaps%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Singh%20said%20it%20was%20a%20myth%20that%20the%20community%20was%20affluent.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20affluent%20and%20poor%20people%20in%20every%20baradari.%20We%20are%20not%20demanding%20quota%20for%20every%20Jat%2C%20only%20for%20those%20below%20the%20creamy%20layer%20of%20the%20OBC%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20for%20Jat%20reservation%20in%20Central%20jobs%20and%20admission%20in%20centrally-run%20educational%20institutes%20is%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20old.%20In%20March%202014%2C%20the%20UPA%20government%20in%20its%20last%20cabinet%20meeting%20approved%20OBC%20reservation%20for%20the%20Jats%2C%20rejecting%20the%20advice%20tendered%20to%20it%20by%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Backward%20Classes%20(NCBC)%20which%20had%20stated%20that%20community%20did%20not%20fulfil%20the%20criteria%20for%20inclusion%20in%20the%20Central%20List%20of%20OBCs.%20The%20NCBC%20had%20observed%20that%20merely%20belonging%20to%20an%20agricultural%20community%20could%20not%20confer%20backward%20status%20on%20the%20Jats%2C%20which%20it%20concluded%20were%20neither%20socially%20nor%20educationally%20backward%20and%20were%20adequately%20represented%20in%20armed%20forces%2C%20government%20services%20and%20educational%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22EWS%20Quota%3A%20Why%20Poverty%20Alone%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Be%20a%20Basis%20for%20Reservation%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fews-quota-poverty-reservation%5C%22%3EEWS%20Quota%3A%20Why%20Poverty%20Alone%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Be%20a%20Basis%20for%20Reservation%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UPA%20government%2C%20in%20its%20attempt%20to%20win%20over%20the%20community%2C%20ignored%20the%20NCBC%E2%80%99s%20advice%20by%20saying%20that%20it%20did%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20adequately%20take%20into%20account%20the%20ground%20realities%E2%80%9D.%20Through%20a%20notification%20in%20March%202014%2C%20it%20granted%20OBC%20reservation%20to%20Jats%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20NCT%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Bharatpur%20and%20Dholpur%20districts.%20The%20notification%20was%20challenged%20in%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20which%20struck%20it%20down%2C%20observing%20that%20the%20view%20taken%20by%20the%20NCBC%20was%20%E2%80%9Cadequately%20supported%20by%20good%20and%20acceptable%20reasons%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Cinclusion%20of%20the%20politically%20organized%20classes%20(such%20as%20Jats)%20in%20the%20list%20of%20backward%20classes%20mainly%2C%20if%20not%20solely%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20that%20on%20same%20parameters%20other%20groups%20who%20have%20fared%20better%20have%20been%20so%20included%20cannot%20be%20affirmed%E2%80%9D%2C%20ruled%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Meerut%20meeting%2C%20Singh%20also%20appealed%20Jats%20to%20keep%20their%20youth%20away%20from%20the%20slogans%20of%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%9D%20and%20instead%20stick%20to%20using%20%E2%80%9CRam%20Ram%E2%80%9D%20while%20greeting%20each%20other%20as%20per%20their%20culture.%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Shri%20Ram%20is%20the%20language%20of%20a%20motivated%20party%20worker.%20Ram%20Ram%20is%20our%20culture.%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20is%20spread%20by%20the%20RSS%20as%20part%20of%20its%20agenda%20to%20create%20enmity%20in%20the%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Singh.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20using%20Ram%20Ram%20since%20birth%E2%80%A6at%20every%20event%2C%20in%20weddings%2C%20while%20greeting%20passersby.%20Is%20there%20a%20bigger%20Ram%20%3Cem%3Ebhakt%3C%2Fem%3E%20than%20us%3F%20Today%2C%20they%20are%20asking%20us%20for%20certificates%20of%20Hindu%20%5Breligion%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%20was%20perhaps%20alluding%20to%20the%20penetration%20of%20the%20BJP%20into%20the%20Jat%20regions%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20and%20the%20dismantling%20of%20the%20age-old%20Jat%20traditions%20of%20opposing%20Brahmanical%20supremacy%20and%20embracing%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20view%20of%20Hindu%20unity.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20success%20in%20western%20UP%2C%20in%20particular%20in%20the%20Jat%20belt%2C%20in%20the%202014%2C%202017%20and%202019%20elections%20has%20prevented%20the%20Opposition%20from%20reclaiming%20their%20narrative.%20Before%20the%202017%2C%202019%20and%202022%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20top%20leadership%20held%20several%20meetings%20with%20Jat%20leaders%20and%20elders%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20community%20electorally%20in%20UP%2C%20and%20keep%20them%20away%20from%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%2C%20which%20had%20been%20their%20traditional%20political%20party%20for%20decades%20before%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20riots%20ruptured%20old%20social%20coalitions%20in%20the%20region.%20Jat%20leaders%20said%20the%20BJP%20led%20by%20Amit%20Shah%20even%20promised%20to%20expedite%20their%20demand%20of%20reservation%20once%20voted%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20differentiated%20between%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20and%20Ram%20Ram%20to%20show%20that%20Jats%20are%20not%20communal.%20That%20Jats%20are%20secular.%20No%20one%20uses%20Ram%20Ram%20more%20than%20us.%20It%20is%20our%20culture.%20It%20indicates%20harmony.%20We%20want%20to%20save%20our%20youth%20from%20this%20aggressive%20chant%20(Jai%20Shri%20Ram)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20well%20over%20a%20month%20left%20for%20the%20New%20Delhi%20meeting%20in%20November%2C%20Jat%20groups%20are%20mobilising%20a%20strategy%20to%20make%20their%20reservation%20an%20election%20issue.%20Jats%20from%20across%20the%20country%20will%20be%20in%20attendance%20on%20November%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20more%20than%20nine%20years%20they%20have%20made%20fools%20out%20of%20us.%20If%20we%20do%20not%20get%20the%20reservation%20before%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20we%20will%20protest%20at%20every%20booth%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shera%20Jat%2C%20UP%20organisation%20secretary%20of%20the%20youth%20wing%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Jat%20Mahasabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695783554000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27111154%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-27-at-11.10.05-AM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fafter-maharashtra-jat-bodies-demand-for-reservation-creates-trouble-for-bjp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Jat%20Mahasabha%2C%20which%20organised%20a%20discussion%20as%20part%20of%20its%20UP%20state-level%20executive%20meeting%2C%20announced%20that%20they%20would%20hold%20a%20bigger%20gathering%20of%20Jats%20to%20push%20for%20OBC%20reservation%2C%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20November%2020.%20The%20reignition%20of%20the%20long-standing%20Jat%20reservation%20demand%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20state%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20could%20pose%20new%20questions%20to%20the%20Modi%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fafter-maharashtra-jat-bodies-demand-for-reservation-creates-trouble-for-bjp%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Maharashtra%2C%20Jat%20Bodies'%20Demand%20for%20Reservation%20Creates%20Trouble%20for%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27082647%2F484827_552962561410114_711841006_n.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Already%20facing%20a%20difficult%20political%20situation%20in%20Maharashtra%20with%20Marathas%20intensifying%20their%20demand%20for%20reservation%2C%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20could%20face%20a%20fresh%20challenge%20in%20North%20Indian%20states%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20renewed%20stir%20by%20the%20dominant%20Jat%20community%20for%20inclusion%20in%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2024%2C%20several%20Jat%20community%20and%20farmer%20leaders%20gathered%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Meerut%20district%20to%20discuss%20the%20issue%20of%20OBC%20reservation.%20The%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Jat%20Mahasabha%2C%20which%20organised%20the%20discussion%20as%20part%20of%20its%20state-level%20executive%20meeting%2C%20announced%20that%20they%20would%20hold%20a%20bigger%20gathering%20of%20Jats%20to%20push%20for%20OBC%20reservation%2C%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20November%2020.%20The%20re-ignition%20of%20the%20long-standing%20Jat%20reservation%20demand%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20state%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20this%20year%20could%20pose%20new%20questions%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20already%20faced%20with%20the%20prospects%20of%20dealing%20with%20the%20problems%20of%20caste%20census%2C%20implementing%20sub-categorisation%20of%2027%25%20quota%20based%20on%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20Rohini%20Commission%2C%20Maratha%20reservation%20and%20the%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20aggressive%20stance%20on%20the%20exclusion%20of%20defined%20quotas%20for%20OBC%20women%20within%20the%2033%25%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies.%20Jats%2C%20a%20traditionally%20landed%2C%20agrarian%20community%2C%20are%20found%20in%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20They%20are%20electorally%20significant%20and%20politically%20organised%20in%20Haryana%2C%20western%20UP%2C%20NCT%20Delhi%20and%20Rajasthan.%20Protests%20for%20Jat%20reservation%20have%20turned%20violent%20in%20the%20past%2C%20especially%20in%20Haryana%2C%20which%20borders%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Explainer%3A%20Why%20the%20Maratha%20Quota%20Agitation%20Has%20Put%20Successive%20Maharashtra%20Governments%20in%20a%20Bind%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fexplainer-why-the-maratha-quota-agitation-has-put-successive-maharashtra-governments-in-a-bind%5C%22%3EExplainer%3A%20Why%20the%20Maratha%20Quota%20Agitation%20Has%20Put%20Successive%20Maharashtra%20Governments%20in%20a%20Bind%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENaresh%20Tikait%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Kisan%20Union%2C%20who%20was%20one%20of%20the%20speakers%20at%20Sunday%E2%80%99s%20event%20in%20Meerut%2C%20said%20reservation%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cright%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Jats.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20made%20immense%20contributions%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20development%20and%20independence%20movement.%20This%20%3Cem%3Ebaradari%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20also%20contributed%20a%20lot%20in%20sports%20as%20well%20as%20politics%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Tikait.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJat%20groups%20do%20not%20agree%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20in%202015%20to%20strike%20down%20a%20last-ditch%20notification%20by%20the%20Congress-led%20UPA%20government%20in%202014%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20to%20grant%20OBC%20status%20to%20the%20Jat%20community%20at%20the%20central%20level.%20The%20Jats%20already%20enjoy%20OBC%20reservation%20at%20the%20state-level%20in%20states%20such%20as%20Rajasthan%2C%20UP%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Bihar.%20Jats%20of%20Gujarat%20and%20Rajasthan%20(excluding%20Bharatpur%20and%20Dholpur%20districts)%20are%20in%20the%20Central%20List%20of%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%2C%20while%20striking%20down%20the%20Jat%20reservation%2C%20had%20said%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20perception%20of%20a%20self-proclaimed%20socially%20backward%20class%20of%20citizens%20or%20even%20the%20perception%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98advanced%20classes%E2%80%99%20as%20to%20the%20social%20status%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98less%20fortunates%E2%80%99%20cannot%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20constitutionally%20permissible%20yardstick%20for%20determination%20of%20backwardness%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChaudhary%20Yudhvir%20Singh%2C%20national%20general%20secretary%20of%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Jat%20Mahasabha%2C%20however%2C%20does%20not%20agree%20with%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20communities%20parallel%20to%20us%20and%20those%20even%20below%20us%20in%20the%20qualifying%20criteria%20were%20included%20in%20the%20OBC%20list%20as%20part%20of%20a%20political%20conspiracy.%20We%20deserve%20reservation.%20We%20qualify%20on%20the%20indicators%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20eight%20years%20after%20the%20apex%20court%20quashed%20the%20UPA%20government%E2%80%99s%20notification%2C%20Singh%20feels%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20government%20has%20done%20little%20to%20grant%20reservation%20to%20the%20community%20even%20though%20it%20has%20enjoyed%20back-to-back%20majorities%20and%20even%20cornered%20the%20Jat%20vote%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%202012%20Muzaffarnagar%20communal%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20does%20not%20look%20like%20the%20government%20intends%20to%20give%20us%20reservation.%20They%20are%20pursuing%20the%20politics%20of%20non-Jat%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20used%20Jats%20in%202013%20(Muzaffarnagar%20violence)%20and%20captured%20power%20in%20the%20country.%20In%20Haryana%2C%20they%20installed%20a%20non-Jat%20chief%20minister%20(Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar)%20to%20pit%20Jats%20vs%20non-Jats.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Meerut%20gathering%2C%20attending%20by%20several%20heads%20of%20Jat%20%3Cem%3Ekhaps%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Singh%20said%20it%20was%20a%20myth%20that%20the%20community%20was%20affluent.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20affluent%20and%20poor%20people%20in%20every%20baradari.%20We%20are%20not%20demanding%20quota%20for%20every%20Jat%2C%20only%20for%20those%20below%20the%20creamy%20layer%20of%20the%20OBC%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20for%20Jat%20reservation%20in%20Central%20jobs%20and%20admission%20in%20centrally-run%20educational%20institutes%20is%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20old.%20In%20March%202014%2C%20the%20UPA%20government%20in%20its%20last%20cabinet%20meeting%20approved%20OBC%20reservation%20for%20the%20Jats%2C%20rejecting%20the%20advice%20tendered%20to%20it%20by%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Backward%20Classes%20(NCBC)%20which%20had%20stated%20that%20community%20did%20not%20fulfil%20the%20criteria%20for%20inclusion%20in%20the%20Central%20List%20of%20OBCs.%20The%20NCBC%20had%20observed%20that%20merely%20belonging%20to%20an%20agricultural%20community%20could%20not%20confer%20backward%20status%20on%20the%20Jats%2C%20which%20it%20concluded%20were%20neither%20socially%20nor%20educationally%20backward%20and%20were%20adequately%20represented%20in%20armed%20forces%2C%20government%20services%20and%20educational%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22EWS%20Quota%3A%20Why%20Poverty%20Alone%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Be%20a%20Basis%20for%20Reservation%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fews-quota-poverty-reservation%5C%22%3EEWS%20Quota%3A%20Why%20Poverty%20Alone%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Be%20a%20Basis%20for%20Reservation%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UPA%20government%2C%20in%20its%20attempt%20to%20win%20over%20the%20community%2C%20ignored%20the%20NCBC%E2%80%99s%20advice%20by%20saying%20that%20it%20did%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20adequately%20take%20into%20account%20the%20ground%20realities%E2%80%9D.%20Through%20a%20notification%20in%20March%202014%2C%20it%20granted%20OBC%20reservation%20to%20Jats%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20NCT%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Bharatpur%20and%20Dholpur%20districts.%20The%20notification%20was%20challenged%20in%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20which%20struck%20it%20down%2C%20observing%20that%20the%20view%20taken%20by%20the%20NCBC%20was%20%E2%80%9Cadequately%20supported%20by%20good%20and%20acceptable%20reasons%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Cinclusion%20of%20the%20politically%20organized%20classes%20(such%20as%20Jats)%20in%20the%20list%20of%20backward%20classes%20mainly%2C%20if%20not%20solely%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20that%20on%20same%20parameters%20other%20groups%20who%20have%20fared%20better%20have%20been%20so%20included%20cannot%20be%20affirmed%E2%80%9D%2C%20ruled%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Meerut%20meeting%2C%20Singh%20also%20appealed%20Jats%20to%20keep%20their%20youth%20away%20from%20the%20slogans%20of%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%9D%20and%20instead%20stick%20to%20using%20%E2%80%9CRam%20Ram%E2%80%9D%20while%20greeting%20each%20other%20as%20per%20their%20culture.%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Shri%20Ram%20is%20the%20language%20of%20a%20motivated%20party%20worker.%20Ram%20Ram%20is%20our%20culture.%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20is%20spread%20by%20the%20RSS%20as%20part%20of%20its%20agenda%20to%20create%20enmity%20in%20the%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Singh.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20using%20Ram%20Ram%20since%20birth%E2%80%A6at%20every%20event%2C%20in%20weddings%2C%20while%20greeting%20passersby.%20Is%20there%20a%20bigger%20Ram%20%3Cem%3Ebhakt%3C%2Fem%3E%20than%20us%3F%20Today%2C%20they%20are%20asking%20us%20for%20certificates%20of%20Hindu%20%5Breligion%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%20was%20perhaps%20alluding%20to%20the%20penetration%20of%20the%20BJP%20into%20the%20Jat%20regions%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20and%20the%20dismantling%20of%20the%20age-old%20Jat%20traditions%20of%20opposing%20Brahmanical%20supremacy%20and%20embracing%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20view%20of%20Hindu%20unity.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20success%20in%20western%20UP%2C%20in%20particular%20in%20the%20Jat%20belt%2C%20in%20the%202014%2C%202017%20and%202019%20elections%20has%20prevented%20the%20Opposition%20from%20reclaiming%20their%20narrative.%20Before%20the%202017%2C%202019%20and%202022%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20top%20leadership%20held%20several%20meetings%20with%20Jat%20leaders%20and%20elders%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20community%20electorally%20in%20UP%2C%20and%20keep%20them%20away%20from%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%2C%20which%20had%20been%20their%20traditional%20political%20party%20for%20decades%20before%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20riots%20ruptured%20old%20social%20coalitions%20in%20the%20region.%20Jat%20leaders%20said%20the%20BJP%20led%20by%20Amit%20Shah%20even%20promised%20to%20expedite%20their%20demand%20of%20reservation%20once%20voted%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20differentiated%20between%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20and%20Ram%20Ram%20to%20show%20that%20Jats%20are%20not%20communal.%20That%20Jats%20are%20secular.%20No%20one%20uses%20Ram%20Ram%20more%20than%20us.%20It%20is%20our%20culture.%20It%20indicates%20harmony.%20We%20want%20to%20save%20our%20youth%20from%20this%20aggressive%20chant%20(Jai%20Shri%20Ram)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20well%20over%20a%20month%20left%20for%20the%20New%20Delhi%20meeting%20in%20November%2C%20Jat%20groups%20are%20mobilising%20a%20strategy%20to%20make%20their%20reservation%20an%20election%20issue.%20Jats%20from%20across%20the%20country%20will%20be%20in%20attendance%20on%20November%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20more%20than%20nine%20years%20they%20have%20made%20fools%20out%20of%20us.%20If%20we%20do%20not%20get%20the%20reservation%20before%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20we%20will%20protest%20at%20every%20booth%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shera%20Jat%2C%20UP%20organisation%20secretary%20of%20the%20youth%20wing%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Jat%20Mahasabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695783554000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%