ns%20next%20is%20unchartered%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20stunning%20decision%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-new-york-judge-finds-business-2023-9%5C%22%3Ea%20Manhattan%20judge%20found%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20committed%20widespread%2C%20longstanding%20and%20ongoing%20fraud%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0at%20the%20Trump%20Organization%2C%20and%20ordered%20what%20experts%20in%20New%20York%20financial%20crimes%20say%20amounts%20to%20the%20dissolution%20of%20his%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20penalty%2C%20awarded%20on%20behalf%20of%20New%20York%20attorney%20general%20Letitia%20James%2C%20is%20so%20extreme%2C%20that%20Trump%20may%20fight%20James%20and%20the%20judge%20for%20years%20before%20anything%20actually%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20penalty%20is%20so%20rare%2C%20that%20the%20only%20previous%20time%20it's%20been%20attempted%20on%20such%20a%20grand%20scale%20%E2%80%93%20when%20James%20sought%20the%20corporate%20death%20penalty%20in%20her%20three-year-old%2C%20ongoing%20fraud%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20NRA%20%E2%80%93%20has%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20staggering%20judgement%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20John%20Moscow%2C%20a%20former%20financial%20crimes%20prosecutor%20for%20the%20Manhattan%20district%20attorney's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20means%20you%20are%20no%20longer%20a%20company%2C%20and%20the%20judge%20is%20appointing%20someone%20to%20take%20over%20the%20assets%20and%20distribute%20them%20as%20the%20court%20sees%20fit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221038%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22New%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Arthur%20Engoron's%20order%20dissolving%20the%20Trump%20Organization.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651378fe51acc80019f0e52e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22448%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENew%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Arthur%20Engoron's%20order%20dissolving%20the%20Trump%20Organization.%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20Supreme%20Court%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20by%20New%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Arthur%20Engoron%20spends%20more%20some%2035%20pages%20describing%20Trump's%20frauds%2C%20and%20disassembling%20his%20lawyers'%20arguments.%20Then%20it%20yanks%20the%20corporate%20charter%20in%20two%20short%20paragraphs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20paragraph%20orders%20the%20immediate%20cancellation%20of%20any%20%26quot%3Bcertificates%2C%26quot%3B%20meaning%20corporate%20licenses%2C%20that%20are%20held%20by%20Trump%2C%20his%20two%20adult%20sons%2C%20Trump%20Organization%2C%20and%20its%20underlying%20LLCs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20orders%20that%20%26quot%3Bwithin%2010%20days%20of%20the%20date%20of%20this%20order%2C%20the%20parties%20are%20directed%20to%20recommend%20the%20names%20of%20no%20more%20than%20three%20potential%20independent%20receivers%20to%20manage%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20canceled%20LLCs.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20findings%20of%20fraud%20are%20just%20so%20obvious%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Moscow%2C%20senior%20counsel%20at%20Baach%20Kaufmann%20Middlemiss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20has%20alleged%20that%20Trump%20exaggerated%20the%20worth%20of%20his%20assets%20to%20banks%20and%20insurers%20by%20as%20much%20as%20%243.6%20million%20in%20a%20single%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20how%20it%20unfolds%2C%20I%20just%20don't%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20Moscow%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20continues%20to%20own%20his%20buildings%2C%20agreed%20Moscow%20and%20another%20veteran%20Manhattan%20financial%20crimes%20prosecutor%2C%20Diana%20Florence%2C%20now%20also%20in%20private%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlorence%20likens%20it%20to%20losing%20a%20driver's%20license%20%E2%80%93%20it%20doesn't%20change%20that%20you%20own%20the%20car%2C%20but%20it%20changes%20everything%20about%20what%20you%20can%20and%20can't%20do%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20a%20corporate%20charter%2C%20you%20can't%20operate%20as%20a%20corporation.%20You%20can't%20get%20loans%2C%20you%20can't%20apply%20for%20a%20government%20contract.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20comparable%20to%20once%20a%20person%20dies.%20A%20dead%20person%20can't%20sell%20property.%20Only%20the%20executor%20of%20the%20estate%20can%20do%20that%20%E2%80%93%20or%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20receiver%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsually%2C%20when%20a%20corporation%20goes%20away%2C%20it's%20because%20of%20bankruptcy%2C%26quot%3B%20Florence%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20same%20thing%2C%20but%20it's%20called%20a%20judicial%20dissolution%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20something%20that%20is%20almost%20never%20done.%20It's%20a%20big%20mess%2C%20actually%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20the%20receiver%20would%20continue%20to%20collect%20rents%2C%20pay%20taxes%2C%20pay%20the%20bills%20and%20the%20company%20salaries%20until%20the%20assets%20are%20sold%20off%2C%20with%20Trump%2C%20who%20is%20Trump%20Organization's%20sole%20beneficiary%2C%20receiving%20what's%20left%20over%20after%20any%20debts%20and%20liabilities%20are%20met%2C%20Florence%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20debts%20may%20include%20a%20%24250%20million%20judgement%20the%20attorney%20general%20will%20seek%20when%20the%20case%20goes%20to%20trial%20next%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECan%20Trump%20transfer%20everything%20to%20a%20new%2C%20non-New%20York%20corporation%20and%20keep%20running%20things%20from%20out%20of%20state%3F%20Florence%20thinks%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20can't%2C%20because%20he%2C%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20is%20no%20longer%20in%20charge%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20receiver%20will%20be%20in%20charge%2C%20and%20they%20are%20answerable%20to%20the%20court.%20Trump%20can't%20tell%20the%20receiver%20what%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20nothing%20will%20happen%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20It'll%20be%20years%2C%20I%20think%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20the%20court%20has%20its%20way%2C%20and%20the%20ruling%20survives%20the%20inevitable%20appeals%2C%20%26quot%3BTrump%20will%20ultimately%20get%20the%20cash%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20though%20%26quot%3Bhe%20could%20try%20to%20bid%20on%20the%20properties%20like%20anybody%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20for%20Trump%20and%20the%20attorney%20general%20are%20back%20before%20the%20judge%20Wednesday%20for%20a%20final%20pre-trial%20hearing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-fraud-ruling-corporate-death-penalty-for-his-empire-experts-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695777668000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651373121c099d0019ad20d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-fraud-ruling-corporate-death-penalty-for-his-empire-experts-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20judge%20canceled%20Trump%20Organization's%20NY%20charter%2C%20dissolving%20the%20company.%20Two%20veteran%20Manhattan%20financial%20crimes%20prosecutors%20describe%20what's%20next.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22litaliano%40insider.com%20(Laura%20Italiano)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-fraud-ruling-corporate-death-penalty-for-his-empire-experts-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Canadian%20envoy%20raises%20concerns%20about%20foreign%20interference%20and%20rules%20at%20UN%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695777184000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103974014%2Cimgsize-21712.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcanadian-envoy-ra