0the%20remaining%20great%20whites%20who%20survived%20moved%20east%20to%20avoid%20trouble.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20great%20white%20sharks%20were%20turning%20up%20dead%20on%20South%20Africa's%20False%20Bay%20and%20Gansbaai%20shores%20missing%20something%20crucial%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-viral-orcas-only-ate-liver-great-white-shark-hunt-2022-8%5C%22%3Etheir%20livers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKiller%20whales%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-orcas-kill-great-white-shark-eat-liver-south-africa-2022-7%5C%22%3Eextracting%20the%20sharks'%20livers%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20chilling%20precision%2C%20killing%20them%20in%20the%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20the%20sharks%20stopped%20washing%20ashore.%20They%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Forca-attacks-caused-great-white-sharks-flee-cape-town-experts-2020-11%5C%22%3Estopped%20swimming%20near%20those%20shores%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20their%20most%20well-known%20South%20African%20habitats%20%E2%80%94%20altogether.%20They%20were%20just%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20mysterious%20mass%20disappearance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20decline%20of%20white%20sharks%20was%20so%20dramatic%2C%20so%20fast%2C%20so%20unheard%20of%20that%20lots%20of%20theories%20began%20to%20circulate%2C%26quot%3B%20Michelle%20Jewell%2C%20an%20ecologist%20at%20Michigan%20State%20University%20Museum%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhakaimagazine.com%2Fnews%2Fsouth-africas-missing-sharks-have-been-found%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dreprint%26utm_source%3DPopSci%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHakai%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20worried%20that%20overfishing%20of%20both%20the%20food%20the%20sharks%20eat%20and%20the%20sharks%20themselves%20may%20have%20killed%20off%20large%20swaths%20of%20the%20population.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20it%20turns%20out%20that%20the%20sharks%20didn't%20die%20off%2C%20they%20were%20just%20hiding%20out%20in%20a%20new%20part%20of%20town%2C%20trying%20to%20avoid%20trouble%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS1470160X23008622%23bb0160%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20journal%20Ecological%20Indicators'%20October%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhere%20great%20white%20sharks%20fled%20for%20their%20lives%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20following%20reports%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustralia-diver-killed-by-a-great-white-shark-provoked-incident-2023-4%5C%22%3Ehuman-shark%20incidents%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20scientists%20determined%20that%20the%20South%20African%20shark%20populations%20had%20shifted%20east%2C%20to%20places%20like%20Algoa%20Bay%20and%20the%20KwaZulu-Natal%20coastline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20predators%20have%20a%20huge%20influence%20on%20the%20movement%20and%20habitat%20use%20of%20their%20prey%2C%20so%20this%20isn't%20really%20surprising%2C%26quot%3B%20Jewell%20told%20Hakai%20Magazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224019%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20Styrofoam%20shark%20propped%20on%20top%20of%20a%20tourism%20shack.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651330091c099d0019ad14af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223014%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20tourism%20industry%20in%20Gaansbi%2C%20South%20Africa%20relied%20on%20the%20large%20population%20of%20great%20white%20sharks%20found%20in%20the%20area.%3Cp%3EDan%20Kitwood%20%2F%20Staff%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20Through%20a%20process%20of%20elimination%2C%20the%20scientists%20looked%20at%20the%20leading%20possible%20explanations%20including%20prey%20decline%20in%20the%20region%20where%20the%20sharks%20disappeared%20to%20rapid%20reproduction%20in%20the%20areas%20where%20a%20large%20number%20of%20new%20shark%20sightings%20were%20reported.%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20scientists%20concluded%20that%20the%20most%20likely%20explanation%20is%20that%20the%20great%20whites%20fled%20to%20avoid%20continued%20killer%20whale%20attacks.%20Their%20conclusion%20is%20supported%20by%20white%20shark%20behavior%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20the%20study%20detailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dad8754e7e6b18258f06e8a3f0e776254353ee5a0974c4aa6b4ebae8f25db0569%26postID%3D65132360eedfeb62d8a8db21%26postSlug%3Dgreat-white-sharks-liver-eating-killer-whales-2023-9%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fs41598-019-39356-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20North%20America%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20at%20the%20Southeast%20Farallon%20Islands%20great%20white%20sharks%20have%20been%20recorded%20fleeing%20from%20hunting%20areas%20after%20killer%20whales%20showed%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20many%20people%20think%20of%20the%20great%20white%20as%20an%20apex%20predator%2C%20this%20study%20is%20a%20prime%20example%20of%20the%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThere's%20always%20a%20bigger%20fish.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20indirect%20effect%20of%20predation%20(or%20the%20fear%20of%20predation)%20profoundly%20influences%20animal%20behavior%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreat-white-sharks-liver-eating-killer-whales-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695769825000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651331571c099d0019ad14fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreat-white-sharks-liver-eating-killer-whales-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Great%20white%20sharks%20disappeared%20from%20their%20natural%20habitat%20in%20South%20Africa