a%20business%20in%20New%20York%20state%20again.%20She%20also%20wants%20to%20ban%20Trump%20and%20the%20Trump%20organization%20from%20borrowing%20from%20a%20New%20York%20bank%20or%20purchasing%20real%20estate%20in%20the%20state%20for%20five%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20boot%2C%20the%20judge%20ordered%20that%20Trump%20attorneys%20Michael%20Madaio%2C%20Clifford%20S.%20Robert%2C%20Michael%20Farina%2C%20Christopher%20Kise%2C%20and%20Armen%20Morian%20pay%20penalties%20of%20%247%2C500%20each%20in%20the%20next%2030%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sanctions%2C%20requested%20by%20the%20attorney%20general%2C%20are%20%26quot%3Bthe%20only%20way%20to%20impress%20upon%20defendants'%20attorneys%20the%20consequences%20of%20engaging%20in%20repetitive%2C%20frivolous%20motion%20practice%20after%20this%20Court%2C%20affirmed%20by%20the%20Appellate%20Division%2C%20expressly%20warned%20them%20against%20doing%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEngoron%20saved%20some%20of%20his%20harshest%20words%20for%20Trump's%20claim%20that%20no%20banks%20were%20victimized%2C%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bdisclaimers%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20official%20banking%20statements%20somehow%20render%20him%20fraud%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20claims%20%26quot%3Binvoke%20the%20time-loop%20in%20the%20film%20'Groundhog%20Day%2C'%26quot%3B%20Engoron%20wrote%2C%20in%20a%20scorching%20latest%20chapter%20to%20the%20state's%20lawsuit%20against%20Trump%2C%20his%20two%20adult%20sons%2C%20two%20of%20his%20senior%20managers%2C%20and%20Trump%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20another%20point%20in%20the%2035-page%20ruling%2C%20the%20judge%20referenced%20%26quot%3BDefendants'%20inscrutable%20persistence%26quot%3B%20in%20repeatedly%20claiming%20that%20the%20attorney%20general%2C%20Letitia%20James%20has%20no%20power%20to%20sue%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInfants%2C%20legally-declared%20incompetents%2C%20and%20persons%20under%20certain%20legal%20disabilities%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20sue%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20New%20York%20Attorney%20General%20is%20none%20of%20the%20above.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23991850-nyag-v-trump-summary-judgement-sanctions-decision-20230926%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERead%20the%20judge's%20decision%20declining%20to%20streamline%20Trump's%20business%20fraud%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEngoron%2C%20who%20will%20preside%20over%20the%20non-jury%20trial%2C%20has%20insisted%20on%20opening%20statements%20starting%20promptly%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-ny-ag-fraud-trial-judge-warns-lawyers-delay-sanctions-2023-2%5C%22%3EMonday%2C%20October%202%2C%20%26quot%3Bcome%20hell%20or%20high%20water.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20side%20threw%20that%20timing%20into%20question%20two%20weeks%20ago%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-appellate-judge-grants-interim-delay-ny-business-fraud-trial-2023-9%5C%22%3Easking%20a%20Manhattan-based%C2%A0%20appellate%20panel%20to%20consider%20Trump's%20bid%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20toss%20at%20least%20part%20of%20the%20AG's%20case%20on%20statute-of-limitations%20and%20other%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20can't%20start%20until%20that%20five-judge%20ruling%2C%20expected%20to%20come%20in%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20legal%20team%20has%20argued%20that%20real-estate%20appraisals%20are%20subjective%2C%20and%20that%20Deutsche%20Bank%20in%20particular%2C%20far%20for%20being%20victimized%2C%20actually%20profited%20from%20the%20disputed%20loans%2C%20arguments%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-top-5-defenses-massive-ny-fraud-case-2023-9%5C%22%3ETrump%20himself%20has%20continued%20to%20make%2C%20including%2C%20in%20a%20deposition.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20defenses%20Donald%20Trump%20attempts%20to%20articulate%20in%20his%2