that%20terrorism%20and%20extremism%20cannot%20be%20fought%20as%20per%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20convenience%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20respect%20for%20territorial%20integrity%20cannot%20be%20exercise%20in%20%E2%80%9Ccherry-picking%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20speech%20at%20the%20UNGA%20plenary%2C%20the%20minister%20chose%20to%20avoid%20directly%20contesting%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20allegations%2C%20seeking%20refuge%20instead%20in%20boiler%20plate%20observations%20about%20terrorism%20and%20double%20standards%20%E2%80%93%20comments%20that%20India%20makes%20every%20year.%20When%20the%20MEA%20realised%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Findia%2Fterritorial-integrity-cant-be-cherry-picked-jaishankars-fiery-message-to-pakistan-china-at-unga-8593100.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esome%20TV%20channels%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20were%20reporting%20that%20Jaishankar%E2%80%99s%20speech%20was%20aimed%20at%20Pakistan%20and%20China%2C%20senior%20officials%20rushed%20to%20convey%20that%20the%20minister%E2%80%99s%20target%20was%20in%20fact%20Canada%20and%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeginning%20his%20speech%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENamaste%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20Jaishankar%20stated%20that%20only%20a%20few%20countries%20shape%20the%20agenda%20and%20define%20norms%20of%20the%20international%20systems%2C%20despite%20advocacy%20of%20a%20rules-based%20order%20and%20talk%20of%20respect%20of%20UN%20Charter.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20cannot%20go%20on%20indefinitely.%20Nor%20will%20it%20continue%20to%20go%20unchallenged%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CA%20fair%2C%20equitable%20and%20democratic%20order%20will%20surely%20emerge%2C%20once%20we%20all%20put%20our%20minds%20to%20it.%20And%20for%20a%20start%2C%20that%20means%20ensuring%20that%20rule%20makers%20do%20not%20subjugate%20rule%20takers.%20After%20all%2C%20rules%20will%20work%20only%20when%20they%20apply%20equally%20to%20all.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJaishankar%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpower%20of%20markets%20should%20not%20be%20utilized%20to%20steer%20food%20and%20energy%20from%20the%20needy%20to%20the%20wealthy%E2%80%9D%20and%20neither%20should%20the%20international%20community%20allow%20%E2%80%9Can%20injustice%20like%20vaccine%20apartheid%20to%20recur%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20Indian%20minister%20stated%20that%20should%20there%20be%20tolerance%20for%20double%20standards%20in%20combatting%20terrorism.%20%E2%80%9CNor%20must%20we%20countenance%20that%20political%20convenience%20determines%20responses%20to%20terrorism%2C%20extremism%20and%20violence.%20Similarly%2C%20respect%20for%20territorial%20integrity%20and%20non-interference%20in%20internal%20affairs%20cannot%20be%20exercises%20in%20cherry-picking%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOur%20Statement%20at%20the%20General%20Debate%20of%20the%2078th%20session%C2%A0of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FUNGA%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23UNGA%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FyY3kdVf45p%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FyY3kdVf45p%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Dr.%20S.%20Jaishankar%20(%40DrSJaishankar)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrSJaishankar%2Fstatus%2F1706656151637795231%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Funga-jaishankar-potshots-china%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20year%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Jaishankar%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98politicisation%E2%80%99%20of%20UNSC%E2%80%99s%201267%20sanctions%20committee%20in%20the%20context%20of%20counter-terrorism%20challenges.%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20politicise%20the%20UNSC%201267%20Sanctions%20regime%2C%20sometimes%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20defending%20proclaimed%20terrorists%2C%20do%20so%20at%20their%20own%20peril.%20Believe%20me%2C%20they%20advance%20neither%20their%20own%20interests%20nor%20indeed%20their%20reputation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20September%202022%2C%20ten%20days%20after%20China%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fun-china-blocks-proposal-by-india-us-to-blacklist-pakistan-based-26-11-let-handler%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eput%20a%20hold%20on%20the%20proposal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20impose%20sanctions%20on%20Lashkar-e-Toiba%20supremo%20Sajjad%20Mir.%20Then%20too%2C%20China%20was%20not%20mentioned%20by%20name.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20Jaishankar%E2%80%99s%20speech%20on%20Tuesday%20took%20place%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20allegations%2C%20it%20would%20be%20correct%20to%20assume%20that%20he%20is%20referring%20to%20the%20matter%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eeven%20though%20he%20has%20repeatedly%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20double%20standards%20in%20fighting%20terrorism%20several%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20Canada%20expelled%20an%20Indian%20diplomat%2C%20India%20did%20the%20same%20to%20a%20Canadian%20official%20in%20a%20tit-for-tat%20measure.%20India%20has%20also%20suspended%20visa%20operations%20for%20Canadian%20nationals%20and%20asked%20the%20Canadian%20high%20commission%20to%20downsize.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20through%20its%20spokesperson%2C%20has%2C%20so%20far%2C%20given%20two%20press%20releases%20and%20one%20briefing%20that%20dealt%20with%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20allegations.%20India%20had%20dismissed%20the%20accusations%20and%20asserted%20that%20the%20main%20issue%20was%20that%20Canada%20had%20refused%20to%20take%20action%20to%20stop%20the%20activities%20of%20Khalistani%20groups.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20all%20the%20foreign%20ministers%20of%20the%20five-eyes%20countries%20have%20spoken%20publicly%20over%20the%20past%20week%2C%20indicating%20that%20India%20should%20join%20the%20investigation%20and%20called%20for%20accountability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUS%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20asserted%20that%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%9Ctransnational%20repression%E2%80%9D%20was%20unacceptable%2C%20highlighting%20that%20Washington%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccollaborating%E2%80%9D%20with%20Canada.%20Australian%20foreign%20minister%20Penny%20Wong%20said%20that%20she%20had%20raised%20the%20%E2%80%9Cserious%E2%80%9D%20allegations%20with%20the%20Indian%20side.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20the%20US%20and%20Australia%20have%20repeatedly%20asked%20India%20to%20join%20the%20investigation.%20The%20MEA%20spokesperson%20had%20pointed%20out%20India%20was%20willing%20to%20look%20at%20%E2%80%9Cspecific%20information%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20that%20nothing%20had%20been%20shared%20so%20far.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUK%20foreign%20secretary%20James%20Cleverly%20carefully%20phrased%20his%20concerns%2C%20but%20acknowledged%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20allegations.%20Even%20the%20smallest%20member%20of%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20alliance%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20had%20its%20foreign%20minister%20Nanaia%20Mahuta%20express%20her%20unease.%20She%20stated%20that%20if%20the%20reports%20proved%20accurate%2C%20it%20would%20raise%20%E2%80%9Cserious%20concerns%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20the%20UNGA%20plenary%2C%20their%20Indian%20counterpart%2C%20Jaishankar%2C%20had%20not%20made%20any%20statement%2C%20even%20indirectly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20noted%2C%20Jaishankar%E2%80%99s%20silence%20for%20a%20week%20during%20the%20latest%20diplomatic%20crisis%20was%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20striking%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esince%20he%20is%20known%20for%20robustly%20defending%20against%20foreign%20criticism%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20all%20his%20counterparts%20had%20made%20public%20remarks%20urging%20India%20to%20take%20the%20allegations%20seriously.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fin-indias-diplomatic-standoff-with-canada-jaishankars-silence-stands-out%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20also%20pointed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20out%20that%20Jaishankar%20would%20have%20two%20opportunities%20to%20address%20the%20questions%20%E2%80%93%20one%20during%20the%20UNGA%20plenary%20and%20again%20when%20he%20goes%20to%20Washington%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20envoy%20to%20Canada%20has%20already%20stated%20that%20input%20from%20the%20Five%20Eyes%20countries%20had%20informed%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20made%20in%20parliament%20on%20September%2018.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20public%20response%20from%20India%20to%20the%20remarks%20by%20the%20US%20envoy%20to%20Canada.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%2C%20the%20Canadian%20permanent%20representative%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20Bob%20Rae%20also%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20diplomatic%20fracas%20with%20India%20by%20name.%20However%2C%20he%20pointedly%20noted%20that%20one%20%E2%80%9Ccannot%20bend%20the%20rules%20of%20state-to-state%20relations%20for%20political%20expediency%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20the%20need%20to%20%E2%80%9Cuphold%20the%20values%20of%20free%20and%20democratic%20societies%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20asserted%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20cannot%20bend%20the%20rules%20of%20state-to-state%20relations%20for%20political%20expediency%2C%20because%20we%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20and%20continue%20to%20see%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20democracies%20are%20under%20threat%20through%20various%20means%20of%20foreign%20interference%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Jaishankar%20spoke%20that%20response%20to%20terrorism%20cannot%20be%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20convenience%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Canadian%20diplomat%20said%20that%20rules%20for%20relations%20between%20countries%20cannot%20be%20subverted%20for%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20expediency%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20while%20Rae%20said%20that%20the%20international%20rules-based%20system%20was%20under%20threat%2C%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20norms%20are%20still%20being%20shaped%20by%20a%20small%20club%20and%20the%20rules%20applied%20unevenly%20across%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20truth%20is%2C%20if%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20adhere%20to%20the%20rules%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20agreed%20to%2C%20the%20very%20fabric%20of%20our%20open%20and%20free%20societies%20may%20tear%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20senior%20Canadian%20diplomat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20speech%2C%20Jaishankar%20praised%20India%E2%80%99s%20advocacy%20for%20concerns%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20especially%20as%20chair%20of%20the%20G-20%20summit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20not%20mentioning%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20world%20is%20witnessing%20an%20exceptional%20period%20of%20turmoil.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20it%20is%2C%20structural%20inequities%20and%20uneven%20development%20have%20imposed%20burdens%20on%20the%20Global%20South.%20But%20stresses%20have%20been%20aggravated%20by%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20and%20the%20repercussions%20of%20ongoing%20conflicts%2C%20tensions%20and%20disputes.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20soci