20on%20Tuesday%2C%20September%2026%2C%20denying%20any%20shortage%20of%20medicines%20for%20patients%20suffering%20from%20drug-resistant%20TB%2C%20civil%20society%20groups%20working%20in%20the%20area%20of%20TB%20management%20slammed%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20disregarding%20the%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20real%20struggles%20and%20suffering%E2%80%9D%20of%20people%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECalling%20media%20reports%20%E2%80%98vague%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98ill%E2%80%93informed%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98misleading%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20health%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20drugs%20are%20available%20with%20sufficient%20stocks%20ranging%20six%20months%20and%20above.%E2%80%9D%20The%20full%20statement%20can%20be%20found%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleseDetail.aspx%3FPRID%3D1960787%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20published%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fwill-the-un-high-level-meeting-address-indias-problem-of-tb-drugs-stock-out-situation%5C%22%3Epiece%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20September%2022%2C%202023%2C%20that%20cited%20family%20members%20of%20TB%20patients%20and%20people%20working%20to%20manage%20the%20disease%20in%20six%20states%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20acute%20shortage%20of%20drugs%20had%20hit%20patients%20suffering%20from%20drug-resistant%20TB%20very%20hard.%20The%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20TB%20programme%20head%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20UN%20agency%20was%20aware%20of%20and%20concerned%20about%20the%20situation%20in%20India.%20Two%20doctors%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20also%20expressed%20concern%20%E2%80%93%20saying%20the%20shortage%20could%20have%20irreversible%20consequences%20for%20patients.%20The%20Union%20health%20ministry%20had%20not%20replied%20to%20the%20queries%20sent%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fwill-the-un-high-level-meeting-address-indias-problem-of-tb-drugs-stock-out-situation%5C%22%3EUnprecedented%20TB%20Drugs%20Stock-Out%20in%20India%3A%20Union%20Health%20Minister%20Skips%20UN%20High-Level%20Meet%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResponding%20to%20the%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20denial%2C%20a%20joint%20statement%20from%20five%20civil%20society%20groups%20said%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20TB%20community%20in%20India%20consisting%20of%20TB%20survivors%2C%20TB%20Advocates%2C%20CCM%20members%20representing%20the%20TB%20affected%20community%2C%20Clinicians%20treating%20TB%20Patients%20and%20TB%20Champions%20are%20very%20concerned%20with%20the%20notice%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20(MoHFW)today%20saying%20that%20the%20TB%20Drugs%20stock%20out%20situation%20is%20a%20myth%20and%20a%20media%20hype.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20organisations%20said%20that%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cup%20until%20today%E2%80%9D%20inundated%20with%20%E2%80%9Cdistressing%20appeals%20from%20patients%2C%20relatives%20and%20doctors%20alike%20who%20are%20grappling%20with%20difficulties%20in%20obtaining%20TB%20medications%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20statement%20was%20endorsed%20by%20TB%20Mukth%20Vahini%20%5BBihar%5D%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EARK%20Foundation%20%5BNagaland%5D%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EGlobal%20Coalition%20of%20TB%20Advocates%2C%20a%20global%20body%20of%20civil%20society%20groups%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ERainbow%20TB%20Forum%20%5BTamil%20Nadu%5D%3B%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETouched%20by%20TB%2C%20a%20national%20coalition%20of%20people%20affected%20by%20TB%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ministry%20released%20information%20about%20stocks%20of%20various%20drugs%20available%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20claiming%20that%20they%20would%20last%20six%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20a%20calculation%20done%20by%20a%20civil%20society%20group%20member%2C%20Vaishnavi%20Jayakumar%2C%20using%20the%20data%20from%20the%20tenders%20available%20online%2C%20shows%20that%20one%20drug%20is%20available%20just%20for%20a%20month%2C%20another%20one%20for%20less%20than%20one%20month%2C%20and%20so%20on%20and%20so%20forth.%20Jayakumar%20looked%20at%20the%20tenders%20to%20understand%20the%20yearly%20requirement%20of%20these%20drugs%20and%20thus%20deduced%20the%20monthly%20requirement.%20The%20tenders%20are%20available%20on%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Central%20Medical%20Services%20Society%20(CMSS)%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmss.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20CMSS%20is%20a%20government%20of%20India%20undertaking%20that%20is%20tasked%20with%20procuring%20drugs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FQ4ozq%2F1%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Stocks%20of%20drug-resistant%20TB%20medicines%20in%20Maharashtra%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22350%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FxlP2l%2F1%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Stocks%20of%20drug-resistant%20TB%20medicines%20in%20Maharashtra%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22350%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20calculation%20clearly%20shows%20that%20not%20one%20drug%E2%80%99s%20stock%20will%20last%20for%20six%20months.%20It%20is%20less%20than%20three%20for%20most%20of%20them%20%E2%80%93%20and%20for%20some%2C%20it%20is%20even%20less%20than%20one%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jayakumar%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20She%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20be%20in%20a%20comfortable%20position%2C%20the%20government%20knows%20that%20the%20states%20must%20have%20a%20stock%20for%20three%20months%20at%20the%20very%20least.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20health%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20statement%20said%20that%20data%20on%20drug%20availability%20was%20sourced%20from%20the%20Nikhsay%20Aushadhi%20digital%20platform%20for%20TB%20patients.%20The%20civil%20society%20groups%20said%20that%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20there%20was%20no%20way%20to%20cross-check%20the%20Nikhsay%20Aushadhi%20figures%20and%20asked%20if%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20claims%20were%20true%2C%20why%20then%20was%20there%20such%20a%20critical%20stockout%20situation%20across%20the%20country.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20disheartening%20to%20see%20the%20recent%20communication%20from%20the%20MoHFW%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20disregard%20the%20very%20real%20struggles%20and%20suffering%20endured%20by%20the%20people%20on%20the%20ground.%20Such%20a%20disconnect%20between%20the%20statement%20by%20the%20MoHFW%20and%20the%20lived%20experiences%20of%20TB%20patients%20is%20concerning%20and%20counterproductive%20to%20our%20achieving%20the%20Honorable%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20goal%20of%20eliminating%20TB%20by%202025%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20concludes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695750494000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26231720%2F49700187543_88f11b0ce8_3k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fcivil-society-groups-slam-health-ministry-denial-tb-drugs-shortage%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ministry%20of%20health%20claims%20the%20required%20drugs%20of%20TB%20patie