in%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-internet-shutdowns-hurt-its-vulnerable-communities-digital-india%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Trigger-Happy%20Internet%20Shutdowns%20Hurt%20its%20Poor%20and%20Marginalised%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20comes%20amid%20protests%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ftwo-manipur-students-who-had-gone-missing-in-july-killed-photos-viral-as-internet-restored%5C%22%3Eviral%20photos%20showing%20the%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20two%20Meitei%20students%20%E2%80%93%20Luwangbi%20Linthoingambi%20Hijam%20and%20Phijam%20Hemanjit%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20who%20had%20been%20missing%20for%20over%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20photos%20sparked%20a%20huge%20protest%20by%20students%20in%20the%20capital%20city%2C%20Imphal%2C%20demanding%20justice.%20Students%20took%20to%20the%20streets%2C%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%98Maheiroi%20Hatpa%20Yaningde%2C%E2%80%99%20which%20means%20%E2%80%98We%E2%80%99re%20against%20the%20killing%20of%20students.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20video%2C%20state%20police%20can%20be%20seen%20using%20force%20on%20the%20students%20to%20control%20the%20protest.%20Sources%20said%20many%20of%20the%20protesters%20were%20injured%20as%20the%20police%20lathi-charged%20them%20and%20fired%20tear%20gas%20shells.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPublic%20protest%20in%20Imphal%20after%20more%20than%2040%20students%20were%20injured%20earlier%20in%20the%20day.%20The%20students%20were%20protesting%20against%20the%20killing%20of%20two%20students%20in%20July.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FManipur_Violence%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Manipur_Violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft