s%2Ftamil-nadu%2F2023%2Fsep%2F22%2Fannamalai-please-note-no-news-on-cn-annadurais-apology-in-1956-tnie-dinamani-2617160.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDinamani%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%C2%A0Annadurai%20neither%20retracted%20his%20statement%20nor%20issued%20any%20clarification.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EZero-sum%20game%20for%20Annamalai%20and%20EPS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20was%20a%20command%20performance%2C%20what%20did%20Annamalai%20or%20the%20BJP%20gain%20by%20forcing%20the%20AIADMK%20to%20walk%20out%20of%20the%20alliance%3F%20For%20five%20years%2C%20AIADMK%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20docile%20ally%20of%20the%20BJP%20even%20when%20the%20saffron%20party%20hardly%20had%20any%20presence%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20its%20vote%20share%20was%20slightly%20better%20than%20NOTA%20(None%20of%20the%20above).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAIADMK%20general%20secretary%20Edappadi%20Palalinisamy%20%E2%80%93%20who%20now%20has%20the%20party%20firmly%20under%20his%20control%20after%20forcing%20his%20fellow%20claimant%20O.%20Pannerselvam%20out%20%E2%80%93%20had%20no%20hesitation%20in%20jettisoning%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrue%2C%20it%20was%20Modi%20who%20helped%20him%20during%20the%20turbulence%20in%20the%20AIADMK%20after%20the%20death%20of%20Jayalalithaa%20in%20December%202016%20after%20initially%20backing%20Pannerselvam.%20He%20has%20since%20found%20recognition%20from%20the%20Election%20Commission%20that%20his%20faction%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98real%E2%80%99%20AIADMK.%20He%20has%20got%20the%20party%2C%20its%20flag%2C%20and%20its%20symbol.%20He%20had%20paid%20a%20price%20for%20having%20carried%20the%20BJP%2C%20an%20%E2%80%9Cexcess%20baggage%E2%80%9D%20as%20Jayalalithaa%20used%20to%20call%20national%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25181205%2FF63ynN9aMAAOScB.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25181205%2FF63ynN9aMAAOScB.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25181205%2FF63ynN9aMAAOScB-300x122.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25181205%2FF63ynN9aMAAOScB-1024x415.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-676818%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22486%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAIADMK%20top%20leadership%20meeting%20in%20Chennai%20on%20September%2025%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40AIADMKOfficial%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20AIADMK%20lost%20the%20support%20of%20minorities%20and%20Dalits%20and%20lost%20four%20successive%20ballot%20tests%3A%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20the%202021%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20subsequent%20local%20body%20polls%2C%20and%20the%20local%20Erode%20by-election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEdappadi%2C%20who%20came%20to%20power%20post-Jayalalithaa%20in%202017%2C%20lost%20to%20DMK%E2%80%99s%20Stalin%20in%202021.%20Still%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20win%2066%20seats%20in%20the%20assembly%20to%20emerge%20as%20the%20main%20opposition.%20The%20BJP%2C%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20won%20only%20two%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIts%20performance%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20was%20equally%20dismal.%20The%20DMK-Congress%20front%20swept%20the%20polls%2C%20leaving%20just%20one%20seat%20to%20the%20AIADMK.%20The%20lone%20seat%20was%20won%20by%20O.P.%20Ravindranath%2C%20the%20son%20of%20expelled%20AIADMK%20leader%20Pannerselvam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnnamalai%2C%20a%20former%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%20officer%20who%20took%20over%20as%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20state%20president%20in%20July%202021%2C%20admits%20that%20it%20is%20a%20challenging%20task%20after%20losing%20its%20only%20ally.%20%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20people%20want%20change%20and%20we%20have%20to%20take%20up%20the%20challenge.%E2%80%9D%20He%20did%20not%20explain%20why%20the%20people%20wanted%20change%20at%20the%20state%20level%20but%20wanted%20status%20quo%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%2C%20however%2C%20said%20it%20is%20for%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20central%20leadership%20to%20take%20a%20call%20on%20the%20alliance%2C%20and%20it%20would%20be%20taken%20before%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20zero-sum%20game%20for%20both%20Annamalai%20and%20Edappadi.%20Edappadi%20has%20little%20interest%20at%20the%20national%20level.%20Even%20in%202019%2C%20though%20formally%20aligned%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%20focused%20on%20over%2030%20assembly%20seats%20in%20the%20elections%20necessitated%20by%20expulsions%20of%20rebel%20AIADMK%20MLAs%20and%20won%20just%20about%20enough%20to%20get%20a%20working%20majority%20to%20rule%20until%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20DMK%2C%20which%20is%20a%20constituent%20party%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20will%20take%20on%20the%20BJP%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20made%20sense%20for%20Annamali%20to%20sharpen%20his%20attack%20on%20chief%20minister%20Stalin%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20latter%20facing%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20and%20family%20rule.%20By%20painting%20the%20entire%20Dravidian%20rule%20of%20the%20last%20five%20decades%20with%20the%20same%20brush%2C%20Annamalai%20has%20once%20again%20proved%20that%20he%20is%20a%20novice%20in%20the%20Dravidian%20political%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20trying%20to%20compete%20with%20the%20AIADMK%20for%20opposition%20space%20instead%20of%20putting%20up%20a%20united%20front%2C%20he%20has%20shot%20himself%20in%20the%20foot.%20Modi%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20see%20the%20DMK%2C%20and%20more%20particularly%20its%20ally%20Congress%2C%20as%20the%20main%20threat.%20Edappadi%20and%20AIADMK%20can%20be%20brought%20around%20before%20the%202024%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20already%20lost%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20only%20state%20in%20which%20it%20has%20a%20strong%20presence%20in%20the%20south.%20It%20has%20never%20had%20a%20presence%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Kerala.%20The%20party%20believes%20the%20notional%20loss%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20can%20be%20made%20good%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana.%20That%20is%20why%20Stalin%20called%20the%20AIADMK-BJP%20fight%20%E2%80%9Cstage-managed%E2%80%9D.%20But%2C%20it%20is%20in%20his%20interest%20to%20let%20the%20AIADMK%20remain%20his%20main%20challenger%2C%20as%20it%20will%20otherwise%20give%20the%20BJP%20a%20toehold%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695744466000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26200833%2FThe-Wire-21.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Faiadmk-bjp-split-what-lies-ahead-tamil-nadu%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20did%20Annamalai%20or%20the%20BJP%20gain%20by%20forcing%20the%20AIADMK%20to%20walk%20out%20of%20the%20alliance%3F%20For%20five%20years%2C%20AIADMK%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20docile%20ally%20of%20the%20saffron%20party%2C%20which%20hardly%20had%20any%20presence%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Faiadmk-bjp-split-what-lies-ahead-tamil-nadu%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Has%20Shivraj%E2%80%99s%20Position%20Become%20Like%20Bommai%2C%26nbsp%3BUnder%20Whom%20BJP%20Suffered%20a%20Crushing%20Defeat%20in%20Karnataka%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26210023%2FF6uAo6VbgAAYzDa.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhopal%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Speculations%20have%20been%20rife%20in%20poll-bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20for%20a%20long%20time%20that%20the%20coming%20assembly%20election%20could%20bethe%20four-time%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20swan%20song.%20The%20increasingly%20tightening%20control%20of%20the%20central%20BJP%20leadership%20on%20poll%20preparations%20in%20the%20state%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20marked%20avoidance%20of%20mentioning%20either%20the%20name%20or%20achievements%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20during%20his%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20tours%20further%20lend%20credence%20to%20the%20speculation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20list%20of%2039%20BJP%20candidates%20issued%20by%20the%20party%20on%20Monday%2C%20September%2025%2C%20will%20only%20raise%20more%20doubts%20about%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20fate%20after%20the%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20unprecedented%20move%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20field%20seven%20MPs%20%E2%80%93%20including%20three%20union%20ministers%2C%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20Prahlad%20Singh%20Patel%20and%20Faggan%20Singh%20Kulaste%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20assembly%20election.%20Another%20surprising%20candidate%20for%20the%20election%20is%20BJP%20national%20general%20secretary%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20guns%20are%20seen%20as%20having%20blown%20the%20field%20wide%20open%20for%20the%20race%20to%20be%20chief%20minister%20should%20the%20BJP%20win%2C%20with%20Tomar%2C%20Patel%20and%20Vijayvargiya%20now%20strong%20contenders.%20All%20three%20are%20contemporaries%20of%20Chouhan%2C%20whose%20political%20shenanigans%20over%20the%20past%2018%20years%20ensured%20the%20gradual%20weakening%20of%20their%20clout%20in%20the%20state.%20Now%20they%20are%20back%20in%20the%20reckoning%2C%20possibly%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high-profile%20names%20in%20the%20second%20candidates%E2%80%99%20list%20caught%20the%20chief%20minister%20by%20surprise%2C%20according%20to%20sources%20close%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20MPs%20whose%20names%20were%20announced%20on%20Monday%20were%20informed%20in%20advance%20about%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20decision%20but%20Chouhan%20was%20kept%20in%20the%20dark.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Tomar%2C%20Patel%2C%20Kulaste%20and%20Vijayvargiya%20played%20an%20active%20role%20in%20organising%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Jan%20Ashirwad%20Yatra%2C%20which%20covered%20230%20assembly%20constituencies%20and%20over%2010%2C000%20km.%20With%20the%20central%20leadership%20completely%20taking%20over%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20Yatra%2C%20Chouhan%20was%20eclipsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F10175742%2FScreen-Shot-2021-12-10-at-5.57.17-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221103%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F10175742%2FScreen-Shot-2021-12-10-at-5.57.17-PM.png%201103w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F10175742%2FScreen-Shot-2021-12-10-at-5.57.17-PM-300x169.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F10175742%2FScreen-Shot-2021-12-10-at-5.57.17-PM-1024x576.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-569737%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAgriculture%20minister%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20apparent%20fall%20from%20grace%20has%20triggered%20speculation%20about%20whether%20the%20longest-serving%20BJP%20chief%20minister%20will%20be%20denied%20a%20ticket%20to%20contest%20the%20assembly%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EState%20Congress%20media%20cell%20chief%20K.K.%20Mishra%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20names%20of%20party%20big%20leaders%20have%20been%20announced%2C%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20name%20is%20missing.%20This%20proves%20that%20Chouhan%20has%20weakened%20and%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20heavyweight%20in%20the%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20big%20gamble%20on%20the%20MPs%20is%20being%20viewed%20as%20part%20of%20the%20central%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20desperate%20strategy%20to%20%E2%80%9Cinvisibilise%E2%80%9D%20the%20chief%20minister%20from%20the%20campaign.%20The%20strategy%20seems%20to%20be%20aimed%20at%20downplaying%2C%20if%20not%20erasing%20altogether%2C%20the%20name%20and%20works%20of%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20from%20public%20memory%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20assembly%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECM%20as%20liability%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20actions%20since%20the%20campaigning%20gathered%20momentum%2C%20the%20central%20team%20led%20by%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20betrayed%20the%20impression%20that%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20face%20is%20a%20big%20liability%20for%20the%20party.%20None%20from%20the%20central%20team%20assigned%20to%20supervise%20the%20poll%20campaign%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20is%20talking%20about%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20time%20at%20the%20helm%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20addressed%20an%20election%20rally%20on%20September%2025%20in%20Bhopal%20to%20mark%20the%20culmination%20of%20the%20Jan%20Ashirwad%20Yatra%2C%20did%20not%20deign%20to%20mention%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20name%20nor%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20performance.%20All%20through%20his%20speech%2C%20he%20attacked%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECuriously%20enough%2C%20even%20the%20chief%20minister%20himself%2C%20who%20is%20otherwise%20known%20to%20brag%20about%20his%20achievements%2C%20is%20remarkably%20subdued%20on%20this%20count.%20Instead%2C%20his%20sole%20focus%20is%20on%20announcing%20pre-poll%20bonanzas%20to%20different%20sections.%20He%20seems%20to%20be%20banking%20on%20freebies%2C%20particularly%20the%20ones%20for%20women%20like%20the%20flagship%20Ladli%20Behna%20Yojana.%20He%20has%20intriguingly%20refrained%20from%20responding%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20posers%20on%20issues%20such%20as%20mounting%20debt%20of%20the%20state%20exchequer%2C%20%E2%80%9C50%25%20commission%20ki%20sarkar%20%E2%80%9C%2C%20poor%20social%20indices%2C%20unemployment%20and%20cuts%20in%20allocations%20to%20health%20and%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20instead%20seems%20intent%20on%20outdoing%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20social%20welfare%20promises%20for%20youth%2C%20women%2C%20farmers%20and%20government%20employees.%20Of%20the%2011%20schemes%20that%20the%20Congress%20Vachan%20Patra%20promises%20to%20implement%20if%20voted%20to%20power%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20has%20sought%20to%20offer%20more%20lucrative%20deals%20in%20six%20aspects.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20counter-strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESure%20enough%2C%20the%20BJP%20central%20leadership%20seems%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20harsh%20reality%20that%20the%20beleaguered%20chief%20minister%20finds%20himself%20in.%20The%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20about%20%E2%80%9C50%25%20commission%20ki%20sarkar%E2%80%9D%20had%20begun%20to%20resonate%20with%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20voters%20soon%20after%20the%20Congress%20routed%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9840%25%20sarkara%E2%80%9D%20in%20Karnataka%20in%20May%20this%20year.%20All%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20promises%20on%20social%20welfare%20have%20provoked%20angry%20remarks%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20did%20you%20not%20bother%20about%20us%20all%20these%20years%3F%20Why%20all%20this%20now%2C%20when%20the%20election%20is%20round%20the%20corner%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERealising%20that%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20too%20might%20go%20the%20Karnataka%20way%20if%20Chouhan%20is%20not%20reined%20in%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20took%20command%20of%C2%A0electioneering.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20strategy%20unfolded%20with%20a%20subtle%20hint%20to%20the%20BJP%20cadres%20and%20the%20electorate%20alike%20that%20Chouhan%20will%20not%20be%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate.%20Not%20only%20that%2C%20Chouhan%20was%20denied%20the%20opportunity%20to%20helm%20the%20Jan%20Ashirwad%20Yatra%2C%20a%20privilege%20he%20enjoyed%20while%20canvassing%20for%20the%20previous%20three%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20central%20leadership%20chalked%20out%20five%20such%20chariot-mounted%20journeys%20from%20different%20regions.%20Flagged%20off%20by%20Union%20ministers%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20Rajnath%20Singh%20and%20Nitish%20Gadkari%20between%20September%202%20and%205%20from%20five%20corners%20of%20the%20state%2C%20the%20yatras%20culminated%20on%20September%2025%20in%20Bhopal%20where%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20addressed%20the%20party%20workers%20assembled%20from%20all%20over%20the%20state.%20All%20through%20the%20yatra%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20was%20kept%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26205413%2FF63GU2sWwAA5daO.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26205413%2FF63GU2sWwAA5daO.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26205413%2FF63GU2sWwAA5daO-300x162.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26205413%2FF63GU2sWwAA5daO-1024x551.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-677020%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22646%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20and%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20in%20Bhopal.%20Photo%3A%20%40narendramodi%2F%20X%20(Twitter)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20pitiable%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20plight%20of%20Chouhan%20that%20for%20issuing%20a%20report%20card%20on%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20performance%20over%20the%20last%2018%20years%2C%20Shah%20rushed%20down%20to%20Bhopal%20on%20August%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20longest-serving%20chief%20minister%20looked%20on%20as%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20sang%20paeans%20of%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Csuccess%E2%80%9D%20in%20removing%20the%20%E2%80%98Bimaru%E2%80%99%20(laggard)%20tag%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20However%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cachievements%E2%80%9D%20have%20found%20space%20only%20in%20advertisements%20in%20electronic%2C%20digital%20and%20print%20media%20that%20the%20state%20government%20has%20been%20liberally%20releasing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20same%20achievements%20adorned%20with%20allegedly%20dubious%20statistics%20are%20missing%20in%20the%20election%20speeches%20of%20the%20BJP%20leaders.%20Instead%2C%20the%20BJP%20campaigners%20seem%20to%20prefer%20speaking%20on%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Csins%E2%80%99%20in%20aligning%20with%20the%20forces%20that%20have%20%E2%80%9Cinsulted%20Sanatana%20Dharma%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20releasing%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20report%20card%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20sidestepped%20questions%20on%20whether%20Chouhan%20will%20continue%20in%20the%20post%20if%20the%20BJP%20is%20voted%20to%20power%20again.%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20party%20would%20decide%20on%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20post%20only%20after%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChouhan%E2%80%99s%20position%20has%20become%20akin%20to%20Basavaraj%20Bommai%2C%20under%20whose%20watch%20the%20BJP%20suffered%20a%20crushing%20defeat%20in%20the%20Karnataka%20assembly%20election%20in%20May%20this%20year.%20He%20too%20was%20not%20projected%20as%20chief%20minister.%20Like%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20BJP%20high%20command%20is%20once%20again%20pinning%20its%20hope%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20and%2C%20accordingly%2C%20devising%20strategies%20to%20keep%20a%20sharper%20focus%20on%20national%20issues%2C%20apart%20from%20religious%20polarisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20mood%20was%20also%20evident%20from%20BJP%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%20in%20July%20appointed%20Union%20minister%20Bhupendra%20Yadav%20as%20the%20state%20election%20in-charge%20and%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20as%20the%20co-in-charge%20for%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20A%20week%20later%2C%20on%20July%2015%2C%20the%20party%20appointed%20Union%20minister%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%20as%20convener%20of%20its%20election%20management%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETomar%2C%20who%20has%20been%20president%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20unit%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20is%20considered%20a%20low-profile%20leader%20who%20enjoys%20cordial%20relations%20with%20various%20regional%20satraps.%20He%20is%20a%20lawmaker%20from%20Morena%20in%20the%20Gwalior-Chambal%20region%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20improve%20its%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20active%20supervision%20of%20three%20Union%20ministers%20in%20various%20capacities%20and%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20close%20monitoring%20of%20the%20election%20preparations%20has%20rendered%20the%20state%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20power%20strikingly%20weakened.%20This%20became%20obvious%20when%20the%20party%20on%20August%2023%20released%20its%20first%20list%20of%2039%20candidates%2C%20for%20the%20seats%20it%20had%20lost%20in%20the%202018%20assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20names%20were%20decided%20at%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Central%20Election%20Committee%20(CEC)%20meeting%2C%20chaired%20by%20Nadda%20and%20attended%20by%20Modi%20as%20well%20as%20Union%20ministers%20Rajnath%20Singh%20and%20Shah%2C%20among%20other%20senior%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20candidate%20selection%20was%20said%20to%20be%20based%20on%20a%20survey%20conducted%20by%20the%20central%20leadership.%20The%20chief%20minister%2C%20who%20is%20not%20a%20member%20of%20the%20CEC%2C%20had%20little%2C%20if%20any%2C%20say%20in%20the%20selection%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20the%20first%20list%20evoked%20an%20angry%20response%20in%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20constituencies%2C%20triggering%20protests%20and%20accelerating%20the%20process%20of%20desertion%20from%20the%20BJP%20that%20was%20already%20underway%20since%20May.%20So%20far%2C%2045%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20joined%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisappointing%20feedback%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20central%20leadership%20decided%20not%20to%20buckle%20under%20the%20pressure%20from%20disgruntled%20leaders%2C%20the%20wave%20of%20protests%20led%20the%20high%20command%20to%20conclude%20that%20merely%20sidelining%20the%20chief%20minister%20would%20not%20mollify%20the%20angry%20cadre.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20feedback%20from%20the%20Jan%20Ashirwad%20Yatras%2C%20which%20evoked%20a%20lacklustre%20response%2C%20further%20confirmed%20their%20apprehension%20that%20anti-incumbency%20against%20Chouhan%20is%20deeper%20than%20they%20imagined.%20The%20leadership%2C%20therefore%2C%20contemplated%20a%20more%20drastic%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20field%20the%20seven%20MPs%20%E2%80%93%20including%20the%20three%20Union%20ministers%20%E2%80%93%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20outcome%20of%20stock-taking%20of%20the%20election%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20MP%20from%20Morena%2C%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%20will%20be%20contesting%20the%20Dimani%3B%20Satna%20MP%20Ganesh%20Singh%20will%20contest%20the%20Satna%20assembly%20seat%3B%20Faggan%20Singh%20Kulaste%2C%20the%20Mandla%20MP%2C%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Niwas%3B%20Rakesh%20Singh%20(Jabalpur%20MP)%20from%20Jabalpur%20Paschim%3B%20Prahlad%20Patel%20(Damoh%20MP)%20from%20Narsingpur%3B%20Riti%20Pathak%20(Sidhi)%20from%20Sidhi%3B%20and%20Uday%20Pratap%20Singh%20(Hoshangabad)%20from%20Gadarwara.%20Vijayvargiya%20will%20contest%20the%20Indore-one%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKailash%20Vijayvargiya%20has%20been%20included%20in%20the%20list%20a%20decade%20after%20he%20won%20the%20Mhow%20seat%20in%20his%20native%20Indore%20district%20for%20the%20second%20time%20in%202013.%20His%20inclusion%20has%20ended%20any%20possibility%20of%20his%20son%20Akash%20getting%20a%20ticket.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20central%20leadership%20is%20upset%20with%20Akash%20over%20his%202019%20attack%20on%20a%20civic%20body%20official%20in%20Indore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fakash-vijayvargiya-kailash-bjp-mla-arrested%5C%22%3Ewith%20a%20cricket%20bat%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F24161635%2F762449-kailash-vijayvargiya.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F24161635%2F762449-kailash-vijayvargiya.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F24161635%2F762449-kailash-vijayvargiya-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F24161635%2F762449-kailash-vijayvargiya-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-429757%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKailash%20Vijayvargiya.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kulaste%20is%20a%20six-term%20MP%2C%20Rakesh%20Singh%20and%20Ganesh%20Singh%20have%20won%20for%20four%20terms%2C%20Tomar%20is%20into%20his%20third%20term%2C%20and%20Riti%20Pathak%20into%20her%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20said%20that%20the%20party%20was%20hopeful%20that%20fielding%20several%20experienced%20leaders%20on%20the%20electoral%20battlefield%20will%20assuage%20the%20fatigue%20factor%20against%20Chouhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20been%20grappling%20with%