20pebbles%20had%20been%20washed%20away%20from%20under%20the%20tracks.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EAs%20the%20train%20was%20approaching%2C%20Mursalim%20took%20off%20his%20red%20T-shirt%20and%20started%20waving%20it%2C%20alerting%20the%20loco%20pilot%2C%20who%20pulled%20the%20emergency%20brakes.%20The%20damaged%20portion%20was%20repaired%20by%20the%20railway%20staff%20and%20the%20train%20then%20left%20for%20its%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chief%20public%20relations%20officer%20(PRO)%20of%20the%20Northeast%20Frontier%20Railway%20had%20initially%20denied%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20act%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20damage%20was%20noticed%20by%20railway%20staff.%20He%20later%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20acknowledged%20and%20saluted%20his%20%E2%80%9Capproach%20towards%20society%20being%20a%20teenager%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26172952%2Fimage1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22886%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26172952%2Fimage1.jpeg%20886w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26172952%2Fimage1-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26172952%2Fimage1-150x150.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-676986%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22886%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECourtesy%3A%20Mali%2C%20%40Malicartoonist%20on%20X%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20Northeast%20Frontier%20Railway%20issued%20a%20press%20release%20commending%20his%20act%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdefined%20bravery.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20one%20location%20where%20soil%20and%20the%20pebbles%20were%20washed%20away%20by%20the%20rain%2C%20the%20boy%20named%20Mursalin%20Seikh%2C%20son%20of%20a%20migrant%20labour%20of%20the%20nearby%20village%20was%20also%20present%20in%20the%20yard%20with%20the%20railway%20staff.%20On%20noticing%20a%20rain%20damage%20portion%20under%20the%20tracks%2C%20the%20boy%20acted%20sensibly%20and%20alerted%20the%20loco%20pilot%20of%20an%20approaching%20passenger%20train%20by%20waving%20his%20red%20shirt%20along%20with%20other%20on-duty%20railway%20staff%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sabyasachi%20De%2C%20chief%20PRO%2C%20the%20Northeast%20Frontier%20Railway.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20locals%20of%20Mursalim%E2%80%99s%C2%A0village%2C%20located%20in%20the%20Harishchandrapur-II%20block%20of%20Malda%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20even%20passengers%20who%20were%20on%20the%20train%20contradicted%20the%20railway%20official%E2%80%99s%20claim.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Railways%20is%20being%20economical%20with%20the%20truth.%20There%20were%20no%20railway%20workers%20there.%20That%20child%2C%20with%20a%20red%20handkerchief%20tied%20around%20his%20waist%2C%20halted%20the%20train%20all%20by%20himself%2C%20and%20there%20were%20seven%20local%20people%20with%20him.%20If%20they%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20there%2C%20it%20could%20have%20been%20a%20massive%20disaster%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Raghav%20Sen%2C%20who%20was%20a%20passenger%20on%20the%20train.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Khagen%20Murmu%2C%20the%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Malda%20North%2C%20visited%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20home%20with%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20senior%20railway%20official%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20presented%20him%20with%20a%20cash%20award%20of%20Rs%201%2C500.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20meagre%20sum%20sparked%20widespread%20criticism%20from%20various%20quarters.%20Local%20Trinamool%20leader%20Krishnendu%20Narayan%20Choudhury%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20utterly%20heartless%20government!%20I%20am%20contemplating%20taking%20legal%20action%20against%20the%20railways%20regarding%20this%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20defensive%20Murmu%20said%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CThey%20want%20to%20politicise%20everything.%20A%20railway%20official%20has%20already%20promptly%20approved%20the%20award.%20We%20will%20explore%20further%20actions%20later.%20They%20have%20no%20genuine%20concerns%3B%20they%20are%20merely%20engaging%20in%20opposition%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20typically%20active%20social%20media%20accounts%20of%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20have%20opted%20to%20downplay%20the%20incident.%20While%20the%20Northeast%20Frontier%20Railway%20shared%20clippings%20of%20reports%20related%20to%20their%20press%20release%20on%20Facebook%20and%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20neither%20the%20rail%20ministry%20nor%20its%20minister%20has%20shared%20or%20reposted%20it%20as%20of%20the%20time%20of%20filing%20this%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHailing%20from%20Puratan%20Koliyari%20village%20in%20Harishchadrapur%2C%20Malda%2C%20Mursalim%20is%20a%20seventh-grade%20student%20at%20Wahedpur%20Junior%20High%20School.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20that%20waving%20a%20red%20cloth%20would%20alert%20the%20driver%20to%20stop.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20used%20my%20T-shirt.%20Now%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20feeling%20a%20bit%20overwhelmed%20by%20all%20the%20attention%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26173024%2Fimage3.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F