he%20barrage%20of%20dehumanising%20slurs%20hurled%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bidhuri-danish-ali-lok-sabha-hate-speech%5C%22%3EBJP%20MP%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Kunwar%20Danish%20Ali%2C%20a%20Muslim%20member%20of%20parliament%20from%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20new%20parliament%20%E2%80%93%20where%20not%20so%20long%20ago%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20had%20lectured%20the%20opposition%20on%20the%20significance%20of%20decency%20of%20language%20and%20the%20need%20for%20good%20conduct%20to%20win%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20his%20colleague%20called%20a%20Muslim%20MP%2C%20a%20pimp%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekatua%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(an%20Islamophobic%20slur%20that%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98chopped%20penis%E2%80%99)%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eharamkhor%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20a%20terrorist.%20As%20the%20camera%20tilted%20up%2C%20senior%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20seated%20right%20behind%20Bidhuri%20were%20spotted%20giggling%20at%20their%20colleague%E2%80%99s%20ugly%20eloquence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fp95qMPaqJUM%3Fsi%3DXbTNxYu1QRhpWbHG%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20days%2C%20my%20cynically%20witty%20Muslim%20friends%20keep%20coming%20up%20with%20self-deprecating%20metaphors%20to%20describe%20this%20atrocious%20state%20we%20find%20ourselves%20in%20today.%20After%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20went%20viral%2C%20we%20had%20our%20small%20rant%20session%20in%20which%20some%20of%20us%20expressed%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20astonishment%20and%20others%2C%20the%20total%20lack%20of%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20seems%20as%20if%20a%20boulder%20has%20been%20tied%20to%20our%20backs%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20constantly%20eating%20into%20our%20spines%3B%20as%20if%20someone%20is%20aggressively%20stomping%20on%20our%20ribs%20while%20we%20gasp%20for%20breath%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20friend%20made%20his%20opening%20submission.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20seems%20like%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20turned%20into%20a%20trash%20can%2C%20in%20which%20anyone%20can%20throw%20up%20their%20filth%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20contributed.%20%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20reduced%20to%20a%20toilet%20pot%20that%20nobody%20even%20bothers%20to%20flush%20after%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20was%20quickly%20and%20crudely%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20remember%20how%20differently%20and%20angrily%20we%E2%80%99d%20have%20reacted%20to%20this%20incendiary%20outburst%20some%20years%20ago.%20Today%2C%20we%20are%20tired%20%E2%80%93%20our%20senses%20have%20been%20numbed%20or%20rather%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20sheer%20pervasiveness%20of%20the%20anti-Muslim%20hatred%20in%20India.%20On%20another%20occasion%2C%20two%20Muslim%20seniors%20%E2%80%93%20in%20an%20equally%20cynical%2C%20though%20more%20serious%20and%20civil%20mid-night%20introspection%20session%20%E2%80%93%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20robbed%20our%20ability%20to%20dream.%20We%20feel%20stripped%20today.%20They%20want%20us%20to%20feel%20as%20if%20there%20is%20nothing%20good%20about%20us%20and%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20achievers.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-opium-of-nationalism%5C%22%3EThe%20Opium%20of%20Nationalism%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20believe%20that%20this%20melancholic%20rant%20has%20sadly%20become%20a%20ritualistic%20feature%20of%20Muslim%20life%20in%20India.%20We%20really%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20react%20to%20the%20endless%2C%20ever-increasing%20list%20of%20accusations.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20being%20unresponsive%20to%20such%20attacks%20even%20after%20a%20decade%20diminishes%20our%20own%20humanity.%20There%20is%20a%20strong%20need%20to%20rethink%20who%20we%20are.%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20perpetually%20marinate%20in%20these%20stories%20where%20we%20exist%20to%20be%20battered%20and%20mourned%20as%20victims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20liberal%20friends%20painstakingly%20explain%20how%20everything%20is%20just%20a%20trap%20to%20solicit%20a%20strong%20reaction%20that%20can%20polarise%20society%20or%20why%20Islamophobia%20is%20just%20the%20means%20and%20not%20the%20end.%20Even%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20trap%2C%20how%20can%20we%20make%20peace%20with%20being%20defeatists%20who%20are%20ever%20ready%20to%20be%20trampled%20upon%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20meeting%20last%20week%2C%20a%20prominent%20progressive%20speaker%20pondered%20on%20the%20mistakes%20of%20secularists%20that%20led%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20rise.%20He%20lucidly%20explained%20why%20the%20right-wing%20feels%20so%20aggrieved%20today%20because%20of%20the%20approach%20of%20secular%20people.%20This%20supposed%20grievance%20of%20the%20right-wing%20with%20those%20who%20believe%20in%20secularism%20didn%E2%80%99t%20explain%20why%20Muslims%20are%20targeted.%20Every%20time%20secularists%20fall%20for%20these%20mischievous%20rationalisations%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20Muslims%20who%20lose%20the%20most.%20Whenever%20we%20find%20some%20logic%20in%20totally%20illogical%20and%20fake%20outrage%20campaigns%2C%20instead%20of%20outrightly%20rejecting%20them%2C%20they%20gain%20momentum.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20other%20speakers%20made%20some%20important%20points%2C%20nobody%20bothered%20to%20ask%20if%20there%20has%20ever%20been%20a%20serious%20attempt%20whatsoever%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Indian%20politics%20to%20ensure%20the%20inclusion%2C%20protection%2C%20and%20representation%20of%20Muslims%20which%20may%20have%20stalled%20the%20pace%20of%20the%20present%20onslaught.%20Moreover%2C%20previous%20governments%20did%20little%20to%20protect%20religious%20minorities%20from%20persecution%20through%20legal%20protection%20%E2%80%93%20despite%20no%20dearth%20of%20targeted%20communal%20violence%20against%20minorities%20throughout%20the%20history%20of%20independent%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20instance%20when%20a%20leader%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20party%20has%20participated%20in%20the%20dehumanisation%20of%20Muslims.%20Like%20those%20in%20the%20past%2C%20Bidhuri%20too%20is%20likely%20to%20get%20away%20with%20it.%20For%20many%20years%2C%20Muslims%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20marched%20in%20support%20of%20rapists%20and%20even%20garlanded%20murderers%20when%20their%20victims%20were%20Muslim.%20That%20Bidhuri%20represents%20Delhi%20in%20the%20parliament%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20make%20his%20vile%20utterances%20more%20astonishing.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20baiting%20and%20bashing%20of%20Muslims%20has%20become%20an%20intrinsic%20part%20of%20Indian%20society%20and%20politics%20cutting%20across%20geographical%20boundaries.%20This%20humiliation%20also%20blurs%20class%20lines%20and%20there%20is%20hardly%20any%20escape%3B%20it%20even%20affects%20those%20who%20leave%20no%20opportunity%20to%20publicly%20claim%20that%20they%20have%20renounced%20their%20Muslim%20identity%20completely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bidhuri-has-exposed-the-real-face-of-the-bjp-beyond-pr-charm-offensives-studied-silences%5C%22%3ERamesh%20Bidhuri%20Has%20Exposed%20the%20Real%20Face%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20Beyond%20PR%20Charm%20Offensives%2C%20Studied%20Silences%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConsider%20the%20below-mentioned%20examples%20from%20New%20Delhi%20alone%20to%20get%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20scale%20of%20this%20attack%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20February%202020%20riots%20in%20New%20Delhi%20that%20resulted%20in%20the%20killing%20over%2050%20people%2C%20most%20of%20them%20Muslims%2C%20we%20witnessed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fif-something-is-said-with-a-smile-then-there-is-no-criminality-delhi-hc-on-hate-speech%5C%22%3EUnion%20minister%20leading%20the%20crowd%20to%20chant%20the%20infamous%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fif-something-is-said-with-a-smile-then-there-is-no-criminality-delhi-hc-on-hate-speech%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egoli%20maro%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esaalon%20ko%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fif-something-is-said-with-a-smile-then-there-is-no-criminality-delhi-hc-on-hate-speech%5C%22%3E%20slogan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20were%20told%20that%20since%20he%20delivered%20this%20hate%20speech%20with%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fif-something-is-said-with-a-smile-then-there-is-no-criminality-delhi-hc-on-hate-speech%5C%22%3Esmile%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20was%20not%20hate%20speech.%20Another%20senior%20MP%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhindu-mahapanchayat-held-without-permission-in-gurugram-calls-for-boycott-of-muslims%5C%22%3Ecalled%20for%20the%20total%20boycott%20of%20Muslims%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20remaining%20unpunished%20although%20%E2%80%93%20even%20though%20he%20did%20not%20speak%20these%20words%20with%20a%20smile.%20At%20the%20same%20event%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Sunder%20Nagri%2C%20a%20BJP%20MLA%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20accused%20of%20entering%20Delhi%20with%202.5%20lakh%20people.%20We%20were%20trying%20to%20make%20them%20understand%2C%20but%20the%20police%20charged%20us%20for%20killing%20%E2%80%98jihadis%E2%80%99.%20We%20will%20kill%20%E2%80%98jihadis%E2%80%99.%20We%20will%20always%20kill%20them.%E2%80%9D%20Just%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20we%20witnessed%20an%20angry%2C%20pro-BJP%20mob%20shouting%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2021%2F8%2F10%2Findia-anti-muslim-slogans-hindu-groups-new-delhi%5C%22%3EJab%20Mulle%20kaate%20jayenge%2C%20tab%20Ram%20Ram%20chillayenge%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3Eat%20a%20BJP%20leader%E2%80%99s%20event%20just%20a%20few%20hundred%20metres%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20residence.%20We%20also%20witnessed%20staged%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjahangirpuri-demolition-driver-muslims-target-residents%5C%22%3Eviolence%20at%20Jahangirpuri%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20subsequent%20retribution%20via%20bulldozers%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20clearing%20encroachments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F15111607%2FMOSHED-2022-6-15-11-15-59.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F15111607%2FMOSHED-2022-6-15-11-15-59.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F15111607%2FMOSHED-2022-6-15-11-15-59-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F15111607%2FMOSHED-2022-6-15-11-15-59-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-601616%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20bulldozer%20demolishes%20Javed%20Mohammad%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20Prayagraj.%20Photo%3A%20Reuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20also%20not%20the%