t%20school%20who%20is%20taunted%2C%20mocked%2C%20and%20assaulted%20by%20his%20classmates%2C%20and%20in%20the%20end%2C%20is%20punished%20by%20the%20teachers.%20It%E2%80%99s%20always%20the%20Muslim%20victim%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20BSP%20MP%2C%20who%20is%20held%20responsible%20for%20the%20provocation.%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20already%20started%20a%20dirty%20blame%20game%20against%20Ali.%20Propaganda%20handles%20claim%20that%20Ali%20refused%20to%20raise%20the%20slogan%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat%20Mata%20ki%20Jai%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(Glory%20to%20Mother%20India)%20on%20a%20certain%20occasion.%20Some%20went%20even%20one%20step%20ahead%20and%20called%20it%20a%20reaction%20to%20a%20Tamil%20politician%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-attacking-udhayanidhi-stalin-over-sanatana-dharma-remarks%5C%22%3Eremarks%20against%20Sanatana%20Dharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20in%20which%20neither%20Ali%20nor%20any%20Muslim%20had%20a%20role%20to%20play.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20how%20the%20BJP%20machinery%20obfuscates%20facts%2C%20and%20rationalises%20its%20unjustifiable%20treatment%20of%20Muslims.%20Recall%20how%20Assam%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20reacted%20to%20former%20US%20President%20Barack%20Obama%E2%80%99s%20comments%20on%20Indian%20minorities.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhussain-obama-himanta-biswa-sarma%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20%3C%2Fspan%3EHussain%3Cspan%3E%20Obama%20in%20India%20itself.%20We%20should%20prioritise%20taking%20care%20of%20them%20before%20considering%20going%20to%20Washington.%20The%20Assam%20police%20will%20act%20according%20to%20our%20own%20priorities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuslims%20are%20not%20the%20only%20community%20facing%20persecution.%20There%20are%20cases%20of%20hate%20crimes%20against%20a%20Dalit%20or%20an%20Adivasi%20person%2C%20a%20Christian%20pastor%20is%20attacked%20or%20a%20church%20is%20vandalised.%20Sikhs%20are%20increasingly%20complaining%20about%20being%20targeted%20by%20right-wing%20forces%20under%20the%20pretext%20of%20the%20Khalistan%20bogey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20pride%20with%20which%20Muslims%20are%20violated%20is%20absolutely%20unparalleled%20today.%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20recent%20outreach%20to%20Dalits%2C%20in%20which%20he%20talked%20about%20atonement%20even%20if%20it%20involves%20eating%20cow%20meat%2C%20still%20leaves%20space%20for%20cow%20vigilantes%20like%20Monu%20Manesar%20to%20do%20what%20they%20do%20%E2%80%93%20but%20only%20against%20Muslims.%20Contrast%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmp-man-urinate-tribal-youth-viral-video%5C%22%3EShivraj%20Singh%20Chauhan%20washing%20the%20feet%20of%20a%20tribal%20man%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20urinated%20on%20by%20a%20BJP%20worker%2C%20with%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findore-bangle-seller-jail-assault%5C%22%3E%20unjust%20imprisonment%20of%20Tasleem%20Ali%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20bangle%20seller%20who%20was%20assaulted%20by%20a%20mob%20and%20later%20incarcerated.%20The%20bottom%20line%20is%20that%20with%20Muslims%2C%20the%20historical%20aggressor%20in%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20vision%2C%20the%20basic%20concepts%20of%20human%20decency%20vanish%2C%20the%20lines%20between%20lawful%20and%20unlawful%20are%20erased%2C%20and%20immorality%20becomes%20moral.%20This%20is%20why%20Zubair%20can%20be%20jailed%20for%20calling%20Bajrang%20Muni%2C%20the%20man%20who%20publicly%20called%20for%20the%20rape%20of%20Muslim%20women%2C%20a%20hate-monger.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFatima%20Khan%2C%20a%20young%20Muslim%20journalist%20in%20Delhi%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20keep%20saying%20%E2%80%98nothing%20even%20shocks%20us%20anymore%E2%80%99%20and%20yet%20there%E2%80%99s%20something%20this%20country%20and%20its%20leaders%20do%20every%20now%20and%20then%20that%20comes%20as%20a%20gut%20punch.%E2%80%9D%20While%20some%20of%20us%20used%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Cshocking%E2%80%9D%20and%20others%20used%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Cunsurprising%E2%80%9D%20to%20try%20and%20aptly%20describe%20this%20explicit%20expression%20of%20disgust%20for%20Muslims%2C%20I%20think%20that%20in%20reality%2C%20Indian%20Muslims%20have%20fallen%20short%20of%20accurate%20vocabulary%20to%20describe%20this%20everyday%20humiliation.%20Perhaps%2C%20we%20oscillate%20between%20a%20sense%20of%20astonishment%20and%20expectation%20because%20our%20reality%20is%20quite%20unpleasant%20%E2%80%93%20and%20just%20as%20any%20other%20group%20of%20humans%2C%20we%20can%20never%20make%20peace%20with%20being%20dehumanised.%20Our%20real%20quest%20is%20to%20find%20the%20language%20in%20which%20we%20can%20forcefully%20articulate%20and%20protest%20our%20dehumanisation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695732049000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F27162618%2FIMG_2018.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhat-it-means-indian-muslim-today%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri's%20slurs%20against%20Danish%20Ali%20went%20viral%2C%20some%20of%20us%20Muslims%20expressed%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20astonishment%20and%20others%2C%20the%20total%20lack%20of%20it.%20Indian%20Muslims%20have%20fallen%20short%20of%20accurate%20vocabulary%20to%20describe%20the%20everyday%20humiliations%20we%20face.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhat-it-means-indian-muslim-today%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Punjab%3A%20India-Canada%20Standoff%20Sparks%20Visa%20Fears%20Among%20Students%2C%20Overseas%20Consultants%2