ave%20been%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Canadian%20citizen%20and%20Khalistani%20activist%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndian%20government%E2%80%99s%20travel%20advisory%20leads%20to%20uncertainty%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20strongly%20rejected%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20claims%20terming%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Cabsurd%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cpolitically%20motivated%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%20development%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20issued%20an%20advisory%2C%20asking%20its%20citizens%20to%20avoid%20travelling%20to%20parts%20of%20Canada%2C%20leading%20to%20confusion%20among%20those%20running%20IELTS%20coaching%20centres%2C%20students%2C%20and%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20India-Canada%20standoff%20may%20not%20be%20a%20subject%20of%20immediate%20concern%20to%20people%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%20it%2C%20however%2C%20has%20been%20a%20routine%20conversation%20from%20the%20paddy%20fields%20in%20the%20villages%20to%20markets%20in%20the%20cities%20of%20Punjab.%20There%20is%20a%20sense%20of%20anxiety%20prevailing%20across%20several%20sections%20in%20Punjab%20if%20the%20crisis%20could%20affect%20those%20wanting%20to%20move%20to%20Canada%20for%20work%20and%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Touchstone%20Educationals%2C%20CANAM%2C%20Skybird%2C%20Times%20Academy%2C%20and%20many%20other%20famous%20IELTS%20coaching%20centres%20located%20at%20Jalandhar%E2%80%99s%20inter-state%20bus%20terminal%2C%20it%2C%20at%20least%2C%20appears%20that%20it%20has%20been%20business%20as%20usual.%20Even%20today%2C%20the%20lane%20opposite%20the%20bus%20stand%20remains%20flooded%20with%20students%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20with%20students%20from%20rural%20areas%20thronging%20the%20area%20to%20join%20one%20of%20the%20IELTS%20coaching%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%