0has%20shaped%20the%20lives%20of%20our%20siblings%20and%20friends.%20For%20us%2C%20it%20is%20a%20sure%20shot%20way%20of%20excelling%20in%20life%20and%20earning%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sukhjot%20Singh%20and%20Avneet%20Kaur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20here%20that%20the%20September%202023%20intake%20in%20Canada%20was%20already%20over%20and%20students%20have%20reached%20Canada.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20students%2C%20who%20are%20currently%20undertaking%20IELTS%20coaching%2C%20will%20be%20joining%20their%20colleges%20during%20the%20January%202024%20intake.%20Admissions%20in%20Canada%20are%20held%20in%20January%2C%20May%2C%20and%20September%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnxiety%20among%20students%20and%20parents%2C%20say%20education%20consultancies%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJalandhar-based%20education-cum-visa%20consultants%20Sandeep%20Singh%20and%20Parmeshwar%2C%20who%20run%20Golden%20Pillars%20Immigration%20and%20Consultants%2C%20said%20that%20there%20is%20uncertainty%20around%20what%20and%20how%20things%20will%20unfold.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20time%20being%2C%20we%20have%20put%20the%20files%20on%20hold.%20Not%20just%20the%20study%20visas%2C%20we%20are%20also%20not%20taking%20applications%20for%20tourist%20visas%20and%20skilled%20category%20visas%20for%20Canada.%20The%20number%20of%20inquiries%20from%20the%20applicants%20has%20increased%20in%20the%20past%20week.%20People%20are%20in%20dilemma%20and%20so%20are%20we%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20that%20recently%20when%20a%20woman%20came%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20tourist%20visa%2C%20they%20had%20told%20her%20to%20wait%20for%20some%20time%20instead%20of%20getting%20her%20file%20stuck%20in%20the%20process.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20IELTS%20coaching%20classes%20and%20tests%20are%20going%20on%20as%20usual.%20Students%20are%20concerned%20too%2C%20but%20they%20have%20three%20months%20to%20go%20till%20they%20apply%20for%20the%20January%202024%20intake.%20We%20are%20hopeful%20that%20this%20standoff%20wears%20off%2C%20and%20the%20situation%20will%20improve%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parmeshwar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20consultant%2C%20Lovedeep%20Sing%20from%20North%20Nation%20Consultancy%20at%20Dasuya%2C%20Hoshiarpur%20district%2C%20who%20has%20a%20tie-up%20with%20Oceanic%20Worldwide%20Services%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEver%20since%20the%20India-Canada%20standoff%20has%20begun%2C%20we%20have%20been%20getting%20regular%20inquiries%20about%20whether%20it%20will%20affect%20the%20student%20visa%20services%20too.%20There%20are%20all%20kinds%20of%20rumors%20in%20the%20market%20and%20not%20just%20the%20students%20but%20their%20parents%20are%20confused%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20education%20consultant%20also%20said%20that%20the%20India-Canada%20standoff%20has%20put%20the%20future%20of%20around%20five%20lakh%20students%20across%20India%20at%20stake.%20%E2%80%9CAround%20five%20lakh%20student%20visa%20applications%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20applied.%20Even%20last%20year%2C%20the%20total%20number%20of%20study%20visa%20applications%20from%20India%20were%202.65%20lakh%20out%20of%20which%201.32%20lakh%20were%20from%20Punjab%20alone.%20That%20shows%20the%20volume%20of%20students%20moving%20to%20Canada%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELovedeep%20said%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20been%20just%20a%20week%20and%20things%20will%20become%20clearer%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20hopeful%20that%20this%20will%20be%20sorted%20out%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ravi%20Sharad%2C%20who%20is%20the%20director%20of%20Times%20Academy%2C%20Jalandhar%2C%20said%20things%20are%20%E2%80%9Cnormal%E2%80%9D%20and%20students%20are%20preparing%20for%20the%20January%202024%20intake.%20His%20academy%20is%20famous%20among%20students%20for%20IELTS%2C%20TOEFL%20(Test%20of%20English%20as%20a%20Proficiency%20Language)%20and%20PTE%20(Pearson%20Test%20of%20English)%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLargely%2C%20the%20students%20are%20not%20very%20aware%20of%20the%20details%20of%20the%20ongoing%20row%20between%20India%20and%20Canada.%20Their%20focus%20is%20to%20clear%20the%20IELTS%20test%20and%20reach%20Canada.%20We%20are%20running%20IELTS%20coaching%20classes%20in%20three%20shifts%20in%20a%20day%20and%20there%20is%20no%20impact%20on%20our%20centers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAman%2C%20an%20employee%20from%20Jain%20Overseas%2C%20Jalandhar%2C%20which%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20most%20sought-after%20names%20for%20student%20visa%20applications%2C%20said%20that%20though%20the%20number%20of%20queries%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20India-Canada%20standoff%20has%20increased%20but%20it%20has%20not%20impacted%20the%20flow%20of%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20we%20are%20also%20keeping%20the%20students%20updated.%20As%20and%20when%20any%20development%20takes%20place%2C%20we%20will%20update%20them%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStudents%20hope%20for%20early%20resolution%20of%20India-Canada%20standoff%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IELTS%20exam%20is%20held%20twice%20a%20month%20on%20Saturdays.%20On%20September%2023%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20scene%20was%20no%20different.%20Like%20earlier%2C%20leading%20hotels%2C%20banquet%20halls%2C%20and%20marriage%20halls%20were%20booked%20as%20test%20centres%2C%20and%20students%20came%20in%20large%20numbers%20to%20appear%20for%20both%20the%20Academic%20IELTS%2C%20mandatory%20for%20student%20visas%2C%20and%20General%20IELTS%20for%20work%20permits%20and%20Permanent%20Residency%20(PR).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20swanky%20marriage%20palace%2C%20where%20over%20500%20students%20had%20gathered%20for%20the%20IELTS%20exam%20on%20September%2023%2C%20a%20student%20Navpreet%20Kaur%2C%20who%20came%20to%20appear%20for%20the%20exam%20from%20Nawanshahr%20district%2C%20said%20that%20right%20now%20her%20only%20concern%20is%20to%20get%20a%20good%20score%20in%20the%20IELTS%20test%20and%20join%20a%20good%20college%20in%20Canada%20during%20the%20January%202024%20intake.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26171237%2FIMG_2883-1-1-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26171237%2FIMG_2883-1-1-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26171237%2FIMG_2883-1-1-1-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26171237%2FIMG_2883-1-1-1-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-676982%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EStaff%20preparing%20for%20the%20IELTS%20exam%20at%20a%20marriage%20palace%20situated%20on%20GT%20Road%20in%20Jalandhar%20on%20September%2023.%20Photo%3A%20Kusum%20Arora.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20aware%20of%20the%20India-Canada%20tensions%2C%20but%20it%20is%20my%20earnest%20prayers%20that%20things%20normalise%20soon.%20Initially%2C%20when%20the%20Indian%20government%20banned%20visas%20for%20Indians%20in%20Canada%2C%20we%20expected%20a%20similar%20reaction%20from%20Canada%20too.%20We%20are%20glad%20that%20despite%20this%20tension%2C%20Canada%20avoided%20any%20such%20action.%20Indian%20government%20should%20sort%20this%20matter%2C%20our%20future%20is%20at%20stake%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESukhjit%20Kaur%20from%20Kapurthala%20district%20also%20said%20that%20they%20were%20alarmed%20over%20the%20rumours%20following%20the%20India-Canada%20standoff.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20past%20one%20week%20was%20quite%20difficult%20for%20us.%20I%20was%20preparing%20for%20my%20IELTS%20test%20and%20suddenly%20this%20news%20came.%20We%20just%20pray%20that%20things%20become%20normal%20between%20both%20countries.%20There%20are%20hardly%20any%20jobs%20and%20future%20here%20in%20India.%20We%20should%20not%20be%20robbed%20of%20our%20only%20chance%20of%20excelling%20in%20life%20by%20going%20to%20Canada%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20all%20her%20friends%20and%20cousins%20who%20went%20to%20Canada%20got%20settled%20within%20five%20to%20six%20years%20of%20time%20which%20was%20not%20the%20case%20in%20India%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInternational%20students%20in%20Canada%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20CBC%20report%2C%20Canada%20hosted%20more%20than%20eight%20lakh%20international%20students%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20figures.%20By%20December%202023%2C%20Canada%20is%20set%20to%20have%20around%20nine%20lakh%20international%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%202023-2025%20Immigration%20Plan%2C%20Canada%20has%20set%20targets%20to%20invite%20456%2C000%20permanent%20residents%20in%202023%2C%20485%2C000%20in%202024%2C%20and%20500%2C000%20in%20the%20year%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20another%20five%20lakh%20students%20from%20all%20over%20India%20are%20all%20set%20to%20leave%20for%20Canada%20till%20January%202024%20out%20of%20which%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20students%20are%20from%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CBC%2C%20the%20Canadian%20federal%20government%20released%20the%20%E2%80%98International%20Education%20Strategy%E2%80%99%20plan%20in%202014.%20There%20were%20239%2C%20131%20international%20students%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%202014%20plan%2C%20the%20government%20said%20it%20aimed%20to%20more%20than%20double%20that%20number%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade%2C%20as%20well%20as%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20students%20who%20would%20become%20permanent%20residents%20after%20graduation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20the%20IRCC%2C%20that%20goal%20was%20smashed%20in%20just%20four%20years%20with%20721%2C%20205%20international%20students%20in%20Canada%20in%202018%20alone!%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695730505000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26170412%2FThe-Wire-20.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fpunjab-india-canada-standoff-sparks-visa-fears-among-students-overseas-consultants%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20estimates%2C%20around%202.65%20lakh%20Indian%20students%20applied%20for%20Canadian%20visas%20last%20year%2C%20of%20whom%201.32%20lakh%20were%20from%20Punjab%20alone.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fpunjab-india-canada-standoff-sparks-visa-fears-among-students-overseas-consultants%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ambani's%20children%20will%20get%20no%20salary%2C%20only%20fee%20for%20attending%20board%20meetings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695728499000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F28%2Ffull%2F1693190385-4805.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fambani-s-children-will-get-no-salary-only-fee-for-attending-board-meetings-123092600817_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22His%20three%20children%20-%20twins%20Akash%20and%20Isha%20(both%2031)%20and%20Anant%20(28%20years)%20-%20will%20get%20only%20a%20sitting%20fee%20and%20a%20commission%20on%20the%20profit%20earned%20by%20the%20firm%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fambani-s-children-will-get-no-salary-only-fee-for-attending-board-meetings-123092600817_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.am