C%20Monalisa%20Mohanty%20(53)%2C%20his%20outfit%20has%20gained%20an%20annual%20turnover%20of%20about%20Rs%2015%20lakh%2C%20a%20feat%20which%20they%20managed%20to%20achieve%20in%20about%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F240644%2Findia-orchid-how-to-grow-business-flower-cultivation-import-industrialist-horticulture-department-telangana-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorchid%20cultivation%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20an%20easy%20feat%2C%20Sujan%20shares%20what%20qualities%20are%20required%20to%20make%20this%20a%20fruitful%20vocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20should%20have%20patience%20and%20perseverance%20to%20take%20up%20this%20task.%20One%20has%20to%20wait%20for%20two%20years%20for%20a%20suitable%20and%20proper%20yield%20at%20first.%20An%20acre%20of%20land%20may%20only%20produce%2060%2C000%20flowers%2C%20to%20begin%20with%2C%20but%20wait%20and%20watch%20in%20wonder%20how%20that%20number%20slowly%20shoots%20up%20to%20almost%20two%20lakhs%20soon.%20My%20training%20in%20the%20army%20has%20helped%20me%20immensely%20with%20this%20profession.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20only%20reason%20why%20I%20am%20now%20able%20to%20reap%20the%20benefits%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20wife%20of%20an%20army%20man%2C%20I%20have%20been%20ingrained%20with%20these%20traits%20as%20well.%20I%20have%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20a%20robust%20support%20system%20both%20in%20his%20personal%20and%20professional%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Monalisa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20always%20smooth%20sailing%20for%20Sujan%20before%20he%20decided%20on%20orchid%20cultivation%2C%20a%20venture%20which%20is%20totally%20alien%20to%20him.%20But%20with%20pure%20dedication%20and%20determination%2C%20his%20idea%20took%20root%20and%20then%20there%20was%20no%20turning%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20cla