%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EMargaret%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20small%20agricultural%20town%20in%20California.%20Before%20starting%20Thattu%2C%20she%20worked%20in%20the%20corporate%20sector%20for%2013%20years%20in%20several%20marketing%2C%20finance%2C%20and%20analytics%20companies.%20Being%20a%20foodie%2C%20she%20honed%20her%20culinary%20skills%20at%20a%20Korean%20restaurant%20where%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20prep%20cook.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20working%20here%2C%20I%20learnt%20how%20to%20prepare%20menus%20and%20set%20up%20a%20restaurant%20business.%20By%20this%20time%2C%20I%20had%20developed%20a%20fondness%20for%20the%20cuisine%20of%20Kerala.%20I%20wanted%20to%20start%20my%20own%20food%20business%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20in%202019%2C%20Margaret%20quit%20her%20job%20and%20started%20a%20street%20food%20stall%20to%20offer%20authentic%20Kerala%20dishes.%20By%20then%2C%20Vinod%20had%20also%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20joined%20his%20wife%20in%20running%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMargaret%20recalls%20how%20the%20American%20customers%20were%20baffled%20at%20first%20when%20she%20started%20selling%20%3Cem%3Eappams%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20often%20asked%20what%20I%20was%20making%20by%20the%20interested%20customers.%20%3Cem%3EAppams%3C%2Fem%3E%20look%20like%20pancakes%20but%20are%20cooked%20on%20only%20one%20side.%20It%20piqued%20their%20interests%20as%20they%20watched%20me%20cook%20it%20and%20wondered%20how%20they%20were%20supposed%20to%20eat%20it.%20I%20would%20tell%20them%20that%20this%20particular%20pancake%20had%20to%20be%20dipped%20in%20a%20curry%20to%20be%20eaten%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20jokingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FThattu-3-1695302832.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202019%2