dent%20in%20Class%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%2090%20young%20girls%20have%20been%20saved%20from%20early%20marriages%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20of%20South%20Tripura%20district%20%E2%80%94%20Saju%20Vaheed.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20to%20understand%20more%20about%20the%20initiative%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20battle%20against%20child%20marriages%20in%20Tripura%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBeti%20Bachao%2C%20Beti%20Padhao%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20scheme%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20was%20started%20in%202020%20by%20the%20then%20collector%20Debapriya%20Bardhan%20to%20educate%20girls%20on%20adolescence%20and%20reproductive%20health.%20But%20the%20initiative%20turned%20dormant%20as%20schools%20shut%20amid%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F257746%2Fias-hero-karnataka-ceo-zilla-parishad-prevents-child-marriage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Saju%20Vaheed%20%E2%80%94%20a%202015%20batch%20IAS%20officer%20from%20Kerala%20%E2%80%94%20took%20over%20and%20joined%20as%20the%20Collector%20of%20South%20Tripura%20district%20and%20revived%20the%20initiative%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Saju%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20reviving%20this%20project%2C%20I%20got%20to%20know%20that%20many%20female%20students%20of%20Classes%208%2C%209%2C%20and%2010%20were%20dropping%20out%20of%20school.%20The%20education%20department%20informed%20me%20that%20it%20was%20because%20of%20child%20marriages.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20the%20past%20year%2C%2090%20young%20girls%20have%20been%20saved%20from%20early%20marriages%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20of%20South%20Tripura%20district%20%E2%80%94%20Saju%20Vaheed.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330395%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%2090%20young%20girls%20have%20been%20saved%20from%20early%20marriages%2C%20thanks%20to%20IAS%20officer%20Saju%20Vaheed.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20in%20mid-2022%2C%20we%20conducted%20a%20survey%20and%20found%20out%20that%20215%20such%20girls%20got%20married%20in%202020%20and%20the%20number%20was%20209%20in%202021.%20This%20comprised%20over%2050%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20dropout%20rate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20that%20they%20observed%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20girls%20were%20getting%20married%20when%20they%20were%20between%20Classes%206%20to%209.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20means%20that%20girls%20were%20getting%20married%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20were%20entering%20puberty%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Family%20Health%20Survey-5%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%2040.1%20percent%20of%20women%20aged%2020%E2%80%9324%20years%20were%20married%20before%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years%20in%20Tripura%20%E2%80%94%20the%20third%20highest%20after%20West%20Bengal%20(41.6%20percent)%20and%20Bihar%20(40.8%20percent).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20noticed%20that%20a%20high%20percentage%20of%20underage%20girls%20are%20getting%20married%20in%20Tripura.%20Another%20issue%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20detect%20ongoing%20child%20marriages%20because%20they%20often%20involve%20local%20cooperation.%20Typically%2C%20we%20only%20find%20out%20about%20the%20marriage%20through%20the%20girl%E2%80%99s%20boyfriend%2C%20and%20sometimes%20we%E2%80%99re%20notified%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20making%20it%20very%20difficult%20to%20prevent%20the%20marriage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%2C%20departments%20like%20health%20and%20social%20welfare%20would%20only%20get%20to%20know%20about%20these%20marriages%20when%20these%20young%20girls%20got%20pregnant%20and%20reached%20out%20to%20avail%20government%20schemes.%20Even%20though%20the%20departments%20knew%20it%20was%20illegal%20for%20these%20young%20girls%20to%20be%20married%2C%20they%20found%20themselves%20helpless%20when%20they%20found%20out%20about%20the%20girls%E2%80%99%20early%20pregnancies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saju%20Vaheed%20brought%20together%20all%20the%20departments%20to%20utilise%20Balika%20Manch%20for%20child%20marriage%20prevention.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330398%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaju%20Vaheed%20brought%20together%20all%20the%20departments%20to%20utilise%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20child%20marriage%20prevention.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EConsidering%20it%20his%20duty%20as%20DM%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F62502%2Fchild-marriage-education-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevent%20child%20marriages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20brought%20together%20all%20the%20departments%20and%20decided%20to%20utilise%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20child%20marriage%20prevention%20in%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20three-tiered%20approach%20to%20secure%20the%20future%20of%20young%20girls%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20informs%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20club%20of%20school-going%20girls%20from%20Class%206%20to%2012.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20female%20teacher%20is%20appointed%20as%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20club.%20In%20addition%2C%20a%20female%20student%20is%20appointed%20as%20the%20convenor%20who%20keeps%20track%20of%20the%20female%20students%E2%80%99%20attendance%20in%20their%20classes.%20If%20a%20girl%20is%20absent%20for%20more%20than%20a%20week%2C%20she%20reports%20about%20it%20to%20the%20chairman.%20On%20learning%20this%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%20%3C%2Fem%3Erepresentatives%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Evisit%20the%20absentee%E2%80%99s%20house%20to%20enquire%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saju.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20learn%20that%20the%20family%20is%20forcing%20the%20girl%20to%20get%20married%2C%20they%20try%20to%20convince%20the%20family%20to%20get%20her%20back%20to%20school%20citing%20legal%20complications%20of%20the%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20the%20administration%20has%20formed%20WhatsApp%20groups%20of%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20representatives%2C%20women%20school%20management%20committees%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Childline%2C%20child%20welfare%20committees%2C%20and%20district-level%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20WhatsApp%20group%2C%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20representatives%20inform%20the%20group%20members%20about%20the%20case.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20cases%20where%20the%20parents%20are%20not%20convinced%2C%20then%20administrative%20support%20is%20sought.%20This%20is%20when%20our%20second%20layer%20of%20officials%20comes%20into%20the%20picture.%20It%20comprises%20a%20one-stop%20centre%20(where%20young%20girls%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20experts%20for%20counselling)%2C%20a%20district%20child%20protection%20unit%2C%20counsellors%2C%20psychologists%2C%20and%20legal%20practitioners%20who%20reach%20out%20to%20families%20to%20convince%20them.%20Most%20of%20the%20cases%20get%20resolved%20in%20the%20second%20layer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20Tripura%2C%2040.1%20percent%20of%20women%20aged%2020%E2%80%9324%20years%20were%20married%20before%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330400%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20Tripura%2C%2040.1%20percent%20of%20women%20aged%2020%E2%80%9324%20years%20are%20married%20before%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20the%20families%20start%20questioning%20our%20rights%20to%20prevent%20the%20marriage%2C%20we%20activate%20our%20third%20layer.%20My%20sub-divisional%20magistrate%20rushes%20to%20the%20spot%20and%20tells%20the%20parents%20that%20the%20administration%20shall%20file%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20family%20as%20child%20marriage%20is%20a%20punishable%20offence.%20But%20even%20then%2C%20if%20families%20go%20ahead%2C%20we%20send%20police%20officers%20to%20their%20homes%20and%20register%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20family.%20We%20then%20get%20an%20affidavit%20signed%20by%20the%20parents%20stating%20that%20they%E2%80%99ll%20not%20marry%20off%20their%20daughters%20until%20they%20are%2018%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20collector.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20timely%20intervention%2C%20Saju%20has%20been%20able%20to%20prevent%2090%20planned%20child%20marriages%20in%20the%20district%20in%20the%20past%20year%20with%20the%20help%20of%20158%20school%20clubs%20across%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20work%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20if%20we%20are%20able%20to%20continue%20this%20way%20for%20another%20year%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20eradicate%20child%20marriages%20in%20our%20district.%20Seeing%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20work%2C%20the%20state%20government%20aims%20to%20expand%20this%20initiative%20across%20Tripura.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20work%20is%20deeply%20satisfying%20to%20me%20because%20when%20these%20girls%20talk%20to%20me%2C%20I%20realise%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20not%20just%20preventing%20marriages%3B%20we%E2%80%99re%20saving%20lives.%20These%20young%20girls%20now%20have%20a%20platform%20to%20voice%20their%20concerns.%20While%20I%E2%80%99m%20involved%20in%20various%20other%20development%20projects%2C%20this%20one%20is%20particularly%20dear%20to%20me.%20I%20believe%20it%20will%20ensure%20a%20better%20future%20for%20generations%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saju.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Saju%20Vaheed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695218864000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tripura%20is%20notorious%20for%20child%20marriages%20with%20four%20in%2010%20girls%20getting%20married%20before%20turning%2018.%20In%20a%20novel%20approach%2C%20South%20Tripura%20District%20Magistrate%20Saju%20Vaheed%20revived%20%E2%80%98Balika%20Manch%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20school%20club%20cum%20platform%20to%20prevent%20young%20girls%20from%20dropping%20out%20of%20school%20and%20getting%20married.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330387%2Fias-officer-district-magistrate-saju-vaheed-balika-manch-prevent-child-marriage-south-tripura%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Startup%20Will%20Help%20You%20Find%20Less%20Crowded%20Fuel%20Stations%2C%20For%20CNG%20%26amp%3B%20EVs%20Too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20got%20his%20licence%20at%2018%2C%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%20tried%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306067%2Fcollege-dropout-launches-ev-startup-builds-made-in-india-luxury-electric-suv-pravaig%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edriving%20a%20car%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20every%20other%20person.%20However%2C%20he%20would%20often%20end%20up%20getting%20into%20accidents%2C%20and%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20other%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20stop%20driving.%20This%20made%20him%20a%20regular%20user%20of%20cab%20services%20like%20Ola%20and%20Uber.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20decision%20to%20stay%20off%20the%20roads%20led%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20startup%20idea%20which%20aimed%20to%20decongest%20fuel%20stations%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Vaibhav%2C%20an%20engineer%20from%20BITS%20Pilani%2C%20was%20doing%20an%20internship%20in%20Greater%20Noida.%20During%20the%20half-hour%20commute%20between%20his%20home%20and%20office%2C%20he%20used%20to%20strike%20up%20conversations%20with%20cab%20drivers.%20They%20mainly%20drove%20CNG%20vehicles%20and%20this%20is%20where%20he%20learnt%20about%20their%20biggest%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20drivers%20complained%20of%20one%20single%20problem%20%E2%80%93%20the%20line%20at%20the%20fuel%20station%20was%20very%20long.%20Out%20of%20the%2010%20hours%20they%20spent%20on%20the%20road%2C%20an%20hour%20was%20wasted%20at%20these%20fuel%20stations%20daily.%20The%20cab%20drivers%20told%20me%20that%20they%20lost%2010%20percent%20of%20their%20daily%20earnings%20idling%20away%20in%20the%20queue%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaibhav%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWouldn%E2%80%99t%20it%20be%20wonderful%20if%20the%20cab%20driver%20could%20know%20which%20fuel%20station%20had%20a%20lesser%20waiting%20time%3F%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20%E2%80%98Nawgati%E2%80%99%20came%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20of%2020%20then%2C%20and%20in%20his%20third-year%20of%20engineering%2C%20Vaibhav%20thought%20that%20this%20problem%20must%20have%20been%20solved%20by%20someone.%20To%20his%20surprise%2C%20when%20he%20learnt%20that%20there%20was%20no%20solution%2C%20he%20started%20working%20on%20one%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20Aalaap%20Nair%20and%20Aryan%20Sisodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20researched%20various%20pain%20points%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20customers%20and%20fuel%20stations.%20They%20then%20spoke%20to%20fuel%20providers%20and%20examined%20their%20in-house%20challenges%20and%20difficulties.%20After%20this%2C%20they%20built%20the%20technology%2C%20a%20queue%20management%20platform%2C%20which%20would%20help%20both%20fuel%20stations%20and%20customers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20fuel%20companies%20improve%20efficiency%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nawgati%20founders%20Aryan%20Sisodia%2C%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%20and%20Aalaap%20Nair%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330322%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENawgati%20founders%20%E2%80%93%20Aryan%20Sisodia%2C%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%20and%20Aalaap%20Nair.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20came%20up%20with%20two%20solutions%2C%20an%20app%20for%20consumers%2C%20and%20its%20flagship%20product%2C%20Aaveg%2C%20a%20B2B%20platform%2C%20for%20fuel%20companies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20improve%20compliance%2C%20achieve%20operational%20efficiency%2C%20monitor%20real-time%20congestion%2C%20and%20direct%20customers%20to%20less%20crowded%20stations%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAaveg%20is%20a%20single%20point%20of%20reference%20for%20fuel%20station%20owners%20to%20have%20complete%20oversight%20of%20transit%2C%20waiting%20and%20serving%20time%2C%20attendants%20deployed%2C%20and%20under%20or%20over-utilisation%20of%20resources.%20We%20help%20fuel%20companies%20and%2For%20dealers%20with%20congestion%20management%2C%20compliance%20monitoring%2C%20and%20automating%20forecourt%20operations%2C%20which%20allows%20them%20to%20scale%20up%20or%20scale%20down%20operations%20at%20any%20outlet%20and%20make%20decisions%20backed%20by%20data%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Aryan%2C%20co-founder%20and%20CTO%20at%20Nawgati.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Aaveg%E2%80%99%20which%20is%20Sanskrit%20for%20impulse%2C%20is%20built%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296093%2Fcouple-converts-tempo-traveller-into-caravan-to-travel-van-life-youtube%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplug-and-play%3C%2Fa%3E%20framework%20and%20aims%20to%20provide%20fuel%20companies%20%E2%80%98data%20within%20an%20impulse%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20vertical%20SaaS%20(software%20as%20a%20service)%20platform%20that%20captures%20real-time%20data%2C%20based%20on%20the%20edge%20devices%20we%20deploy.%20The%20edge%20devices%2C%20in%20simple%20terms%2C%20are%20a%20set%20of%20hardwares%20that%20controls%20data%20flow%20between%20two%20networks%20at%20fuel%20stations.%20Through%20these%20devices%2C%20we%20get%20access%20to%20CCTVs%20and%20dispensers%20at%20the%20stations%2C%20which%20gives%20us%20insights%20into%20the%20congestion%2C%20waiting%20time%2C%20utilisation%20of%20each%20dispenser%2C%20and%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Aryan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20data%20and%20metrics%20help%20companies%20increase%20sales%2C%20reduce%20recurring%20costs%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founders.%20They%20get%20access%20to%20the%20vehicles%20fuelling%20at%20their%20station%2C%20how%20much%20time%20each%20vehicle%20is%20waiting%2C%20how%20much%20time%20is%20spent%20on%20fuelling%20every%20vehicle%2C%20which%20dispensers%20are%20being%20used%20more%2C%20what%20are%20the%20inefficiencies%2C%20amongst%20other%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENawgati%20works%20on%20a%20subscription-based%20model%20and%20charges%20fuel%20stations%20on%20a%20monthly%20basis%2C%20starting%20from%20Rs%205000.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20technology%2C%20that%20is%20saving%20money%20for%20fuel%20companies%2C%20was%20built%20at%20BITS%20Pilani%20in%202019%2C%20through%20the%20college%E2%80%99s%20incubation%20program%2C%20Pilani%20Innovation%20%26amp%3B%20Entrepreneurship%20Development%20Society%20(PIEDS).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20building%20the%20technology%2C%20we%20embarked%20on%20trial%20runs%20that%20led%20us%20to%20a%20pilot%20project%20with%20Indraprastha%20Gas%20Ltd%20(IGL)%20in%202021.%20We%20received%20a%20lot%20of%20valuable%20insights%20regarding%20the%20challenges%20encountered%20by%20the%20teams%20at%20CNG%20stations.%20We%20then%20made%20some%20changes%20to%20enhance%20Aaveg%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Aryan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20pilot%2C%20IGL%20signed%20an%20annual%20contract%20with%20Nawgati.%20Today%2C%20Aaveg%20is%20live%20at%20IGL%2C%20Indian%20Oil%20outlets%20in%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20Mahanagar%20Gas%20(MGL)%20outlets%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20GAIL%20Gas%2C%20Torrent%20Gas%2C%20JioBP%2C%20HP%20Gas%20among%20several%20other%20fuel%20companies%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20plan%20to%20onboard%2015%2C000%20fueling%20outlets%20within%20two%20years.%20The%20startup%20has%20filed%20a%20patent%20for%20this%20technology%2C%20which%20helps%20fuel%20pumps%20manage%20congestion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20Nawgati%20helps%20consumers%2C%20especially%20cab%20drivers%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nawgati%20app%20helps%20consumers%20find%20nearest%20fuel%20stations%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-170x300.jpg%20170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-500x883.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-768x1356.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-870x1536.jpg%20870w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-150x265.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330324%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221907%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Nawgati%20app%20helps%20consumers%20find%20the%20nearest%20fuel%20stations.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20solution%20was%20built%20with%20cab%20drivers%20in%20mind%2C%20to%20help%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304454%2Ftwo-friends-climate-tech-startup-climes-helps-neutralise-carbon-footprint%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esave%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20this%2C%20the%20company%20has%20developed%20an%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNawgati%20fueling%20app%20is%20the%20largest%20fuel%20discovery%20application%20in%20the%20country.%20You%20can%20use%20the%20application%20to%20navigate%20to%20a%20CNG%2Fpetrol%2Fdiesel%20station%20on%20your%20route%2C%20or%20find%20one%20closest%20to%20you.%20We%20have%20more%20than%20a%20million%20downloads%20on%20the%20app%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vaibhav%2C%20co-founder%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%20of%20Nawgati.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%204-year-old%20app%20is%20currently%20free%2C%20but%20the%20founders%20have%20plans%20to%20roll%20out%20a%20freemium%20model%20soon%2C%20where%20they%20would%20offer%20basic%20features%20for%20free%2C%20but%20charge%20for%20the%20premium%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20had%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20Season%202%20and%20signed%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%2067%20lakhs%20for%203%20percent%20equity.%20This%20gave%20a%20boost%20to%20Nawgati%20and%20led%20to%20more%20dealers%20reaching%20out%20to%20them.%20The%20startup%20is%20also%20backed%20by%20the%20department%20of%20science%20and%20technology%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20revolutionising%20the%20fuel%20station%20experience%2C%20benefiting%20both%20fuel%20providers%20and%20consumers%20alike.%20Any%20new%20CNG%20station%20is%20now%20listed%20on%20our%20app%20too.%20This%20helps%20fuel%20stations%20get%20more%20sales.%20We%20have%2075000%20fuel%20stations%20listed%20on%20the%20app%20today.%20We%20are%20fuel%20agnostic%2C%20and%20also%20list%20EV%20charging%20stations%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vaibhav.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERun%20by%20two%2025-year-olds%20and%20one%2024-year-old%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326200%2Fecosoul-home-india-boston-sustainable-plastic-free-kitchenware-cutlery-sugarcane-palm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%20wants%20to%20become%20synonymous%20with%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20Nawgati%20to%20be%20the%20doctor%20for%20any%20fuel%20related%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vaibhav.%20Now%2C%20when%20Vaibav%20hops%20onto%20a%20cab%2C%20he%20leads%20the%20driver%20to%20the%20nearest%20fuel%20station%20with%20the%20least%20waiting%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%3A%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695218288000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330313%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nawgati%2C%20founded%20by%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%2C%20Aryan%20Sisodia%20and%20Aalaap%20Nair%2C%20wants%20to%20change%20the%20fuel%20station%20experience%20in%20India.%20Its%20B2B%20platform%20'Aaveg'%20offers%20congestion%20monitoring%20through%20technology%20for%20fuel%20stations%20while%20the%20app%20offers%20easy%20navigation%20for%20customers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330313%2Fnawgati-fuelling-management-app-innovative-startup-shark-tank-india-bits-pilani%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Royal%20Physician%20and%20Freedom%20Fighter%20%26amp%3B%20The%20Story%20Behind%20India%E2%80%99s%20Oldest%20Ganeshotsav%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20that%20time%20of%20the%20year%20when%20houses%20across%20the%20country%20are%20adorned%20with%20flowers%20and%20festive%20lights%20to%20welcome%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295735%2Feasy-eco-friendly-home-decor-ideas-for-ganesh-chaturthi-on-instagram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Ganapati%20%3Cem%3EBappa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fa%3E%20But%20do%20you%20know%20the%20origin%20story%20of%20how%20this%20iconic%20festival%20came%20into%20existence%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20this%2C%20we%20need%20to%20go%20back%20about%20131%20years.%20During%20a%20time%20when%20India%20was%20actively%20resisting%20British%20colonial%20rule%20and%20striving%20for%20independence%2C%20Krishnajipant%20Khasgiwale%20used%20the%20festival%20to%20demonstrate%20India%E2%80%99s%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201892%2C%20Pune%20resident%20Krishnajipant%20visited%20the%20Maratha-ruled%20Gwalior.%20There%2C%20he%20witnessed%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261898%2Findias-oldest-ganeshotsav-was-set-up-by-a-freedom-fighter-in-1892%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20public%20celebration%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20brought%20it%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20his%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20Shrimant%20Bhausaheb%20Rangari%20and%20Balasaheb%20Natu%20%E2%80%94%20back%20home%20in%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShrimant%20Bhausaheb%20Rangari%2C%20also%20a%20famous%20royal%20physician%20and%20a%20freedom%20fighter%2C%20saw%20potential%20in%20this%20festival%20to%20unite%20countrymen.%20So%20he%20installed%20the%20first%20%3Cem%3Esaarvajanik%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20public%20Ganesha%20idol%20in%20his%20home%20or%20%3Cem%3Ewada%3C%2Fem%3E%20located%20in%20an%20area%20called%20Shalukar%20Bol.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20idol%20was%20unique%20as%20it%20depicted%20the%20deity%20killing%20a%20demon.%20Made%20of%20wood%20and%20bran%2C%20the%20imagery%20was%20far%20from%20the%20usual%20calm%20and%20composed%20demeanour%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261867%2Fhow-to-carve-clay-ganesh-idol-chathurthi-sustainable-hack-eco-friendly%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eof%20Lord%20Ganesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20this%20was%20symbolic%20of%20India%20as%20a%20nation%20fighting%20for%20its%20freedom%20against%20the%20colonialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20gained%20more%20attention%20when%20freedom%20fighter%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20praised%20his%20efforts%20in%20an%20article%20in%20the%20iconic%20newspaper%20%3Cem%3EKesari%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Over%20a%20century%20later%2C%20the%20original%20idol%20made%20of%20paper%20pulp%20is%20still%20worshipped%20at%20Bhausaheb%20Rangari%E2%80%99s%20wada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDid%20you%20find%20the%20story%20interesting%3F%20Watch%20this%20short%20video%20to%20find%20out%20more%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%20%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FAu35GJHjHWE%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695218070000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22http%3A%2F%2Fimg.youtube.com%2Fvi%2FAu35GJHjHWE%2F0.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330388%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20royal%20physician%20and%20freedom%20fighter%2C%20Shrimant%20Bhausaheb%20Rangari%20installed%20a%20unique%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Ganesha%20in%20India's%20first%20public%20%E2%80%98Ganeshotsav%E2%