ents%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20his%20assistance%20now%2C%20this%20government%20officer%20is%20a%20strong%20believer%20in%20%3Cem%3Ekarma%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Today%2C%20he%20supports%20six%20students%20in%20their%20education.%20%E2%80%9CGod%20has%20blessed%20me%3B%20I%20have%20to%20pass%20on%20the%20help%20to%20those%20who%20need%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oecd-ilibrary.org%2Fsites%2F61d5c87b-en%2Findex.html%3FitemId%3D%2Fcontent%2Fcomponent%2F61d5c87b-en%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EOECD%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695101867000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330237%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nellayapan%20B%2C%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20(OSD)%20to%20the%20Nagaland%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20grew%20up%20in%20crushing%20poverty%20in%20a%20one-room%20house%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Kanniyakumari.%20Exemplifying%20the%20power%20of%20education%2C%20his%20inspiring%20story%20has%20won%20the%20Internet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330237%2Fnellayapan-b-kanniyakumari-osd-to-nagaland-chief-minister-inspiring-story-went-viral-on-twitter%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%E2%80%99s%20Behind%20The%20Auto%20Strike%3F%20The%20Decline%20Of%20A%20'Good%20Job'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Falling%20real%20wages%20and%20high%20corporate%20profits%20have%20fomented%20militancy%20on%20the%20picket%20lines%20at%20Ford%2